context:
{
  "id": "line:0b9159a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Emily"
}

{
  "id": "line:015a533",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "It was the grave of Emily Grant—[p/]such a shame that she died so young."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f3f19",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "I briefly paid my respects."
}

{
  "id": "line:00000d9",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "It was the grave that Eris was attending to earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0962936",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "The name on the stone said “Emily Grant”,[p/] and her lifetime appears to be awfully short."
}

{
  "id": "line:08be1b7",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "She must have only been twelve years old when she died."
}

{
  "id": "line:083be08",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Grave"
}

{
  "id": "line:05578c7",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "It was a grave for an individual that I didn't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:060b029",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "Out of respect,[p/] it'd be best to leave it undisturbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0766bae",
  "node": "Cemetery_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f433f0",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Trial"
}

{
  "id": "line:0395ffc",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: That was my first time watching a court trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0048d7b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: You were truly remarkable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d77b86",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Thank you.[p/] Were you in the gallery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0857029",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I’ve always enjoyed watching physical battles [p/]in the theatre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0e114",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: But I see now that battles of wits can be just as entertaining to watch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f41705",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: “Entertaining”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c8766",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Yeah,[p/] I know what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfcdd8",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: You see the odds are stacked against him,[p/] but then he suddenly pulls out this crazy deduction that takes the whole trial back."
}

{
  "id": "line:094d90d",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I’ve...[p/] never really thought of it like that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc07f5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: But I’m sure it’s far more entertaining to be the one [i]making[/i] the deductions."
}

{
  "id": "line:014c50c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m...[p/] not really sure what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:074f1ff",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I practice law so that I can help those persecuted by the justice system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae490b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I don’t really do it to \"entertain\" myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0503923",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: But is that really true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8dd63",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Don’t you find the experience even the least bit entertaining, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0393da3",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Um...[p/] I wouldn’t really put it that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce568",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: You’re far too modest.[p/] You save people from the clutches of death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0436176",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: To your clients,[p/] you might as well be a knight in shining armor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc58e2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07191d9",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: I know you're looking for it,[p/] but apparently those new operating systems don't like it when I peek at your real name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0307bd3",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: I'm all for a bit of fun,[p/] but that's not worth blue-screening people."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d0e59",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc132a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: Don't worry about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d28ed",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Illusion Magic"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3bc83",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Earlier,[p/] you said that you were studying [b]illusion[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de7cc4",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I am.[p/] Did you want to ask me about the prosecution’s theory?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098e2f5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Yes, actually.[p/] How did you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039622d",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Disguising an undead with an illusion is definitely possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a95ea",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: As Lady Steelwind said,[p/] [b]Illusory Disguise[/b] would be the best spell to use for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5d9a5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What if someone created a freestanding illusion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031f7cd",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: We know that Wallace didn’t animate and disguise the professor’s corpse."
}

{
  "id": "line:017e23f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: So,[p/] what if the illusion wasn’t disguising [i]anything[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0057144",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Maybe someone created a freestanding illusion of Bellwether walking around?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061e56e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: For something like that,[p/] one would probably use [b]Major Illusion[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:068d32c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Major Illusion"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fcc53",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:023d693",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc17ff",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I don't think [b]Major Illusion[/b] is what we’re looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf9b4",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you remember what Jan said?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a845a5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I was cleaning a mess in the hallways."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecdd2c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Bellwether knocked over a vase...[p/] And there were shards and dirt everywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4ec2d",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: If the “Bellwether” that Jan saw was a Major Illusion,[p/] then she couldn’t have knocked over that vase."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f68adc",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Illusions created by that spell don’t have any mass."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e07a6",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I see.[p/] How perceptive of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4508e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Aren’t there any other [b]illusion[/b] spells that have mass?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0b334",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: No.[p/] All known [b]illusion[/b] spells in Wyverngarde can only recreate visual and auditory sensations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f60e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: None of those spells can create something that someone can touch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc7b6",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: So that means that someone disguised[p/] [i]something[/i] to make it look like Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd4bd2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:052a414",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Why the look of suspicion, Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086d8a0",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/][s/] I wasn’t-!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0121750",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Calm yourself.[p/] I was only joking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a45747",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I don’t blame you for considering every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:004d9d5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: In fact,[p/] I’m flattered you think I’m capable of pulling off such an elaborate ruse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b81c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c51a3",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Anyways,[p/] this [i]does[/i] tell us one important thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0487a51",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: What’s that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa5298",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: The “Bellwether” that Jan saw had a physical mass to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b3a5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: It wasn’t a freestanding illusion.[p/] It was someone disguised as her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26450",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Gravestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3410",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Hm...[p/] It’s quite a shame, isn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d32539",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Eris looked pensively towards the gravestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:06537ee",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "The name on the stone said “Emily Grant”,[p/] and her lifetime appeared to have been awfully short."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca1027",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: S-[p/]Sorry for interrupting you...[p/] Was she someone you knew?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce2cd",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I’m actually here on Wallace’s behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f80ba",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wallace knew her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c639c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Wallace joined the academy as part of a program run by Headmaster Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e765f7",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: At the time,[p/] the headmaster was reaching out to mages among the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b91110",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: He had started a program to admit them to the academy through a scholarship program."
}

{
  "id": "line:0156710",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Both Emily and Wallace were among those mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:020cd68",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wow...[p/] That must have been an amazing opportunity for them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05667c1",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: The truth is,[p/] neither of them actually cared about learning magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:014133c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: The real problem was that Emily had a deadly illness."
}

{
  "id": "line:084b4ac",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: She and Wallace were poor orphans,[p/] and they obviously didn’t have the resources to treat it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b8fa6",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: But if they enrolled in the academy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:036837c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: The academy would be obligated to give her medical treatment."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0b83",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: The Imperial Academy teaches the best mages in the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:088d85f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: They thought that curing her illness would be an easy task for the academy’s healers."
}

{
  "id": "line:003094f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: ...But they were mistaken, I’m afraid."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d86b5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: I’m sure you know this by now,[p/] but healing spells can only treat wounds.[p/] They can’t cure illnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e91b3e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Emily’s condition only got worse over the years,[p/] and eventually,[p/] she succumbed to her illness."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c165a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Wallace was furious.[p/] He didn’t understand why the kingdom was outlawing magic that could save lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f1d6",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...And that’s why he decided to learn it himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f0105",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Yes.[p/] The headmaster was inspired by Wallace’s resolve."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe07c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: He gave him access to the academy's forbidden tomes of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0738af7",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: And with the headmaster's guidance,[p/] Wallace learned the spells that he knows today."
}

{
  "id": "line:000976f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: So, that’s why..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e2d51",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: It was supposed to stay a secret between him and the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8189",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: ...But I’m sure you know how that turned out."
}

{
  "id": "line:07983fb",
  "node": "Cemetery_Talk",
  "text": "Player: BACK"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa645a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Runestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9564",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Seriously?[p/] You're showing me the badge now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d1194",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Badge\"?[p/] It's an Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:019b7f3",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: We're really threading the line, aren't we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb43f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Are you going to make a habit of showing this thing to everyone you meet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0278b74",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I just think it's neat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f77f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76dc1",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I wasn't quite sure what to make of you at first,[p/] but you are truly remarkable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0313279",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks...[p/] I think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0749271",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I quite enjoyed watching you battle Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c861bf",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I only hope the climax lives up to my expectations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0143ac2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d3d03",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: That's a fancy-looking sword, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0660b37",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Is it from the Eastern Kingdoms?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbaf8f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/]Yes, actually."
}

{
  "id": "line:090440b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: How did you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0802529",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I've encountered a few weapons from there before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0482876",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: They have a unique style that's easy to recognize."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5ce26",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a6ecd",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Lady Steelwind is really something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0217a38",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah.[p/] I feel like she's always one step ahead of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deaa55",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: But she [i]does[/i] have a habit of relenting when she realizes she's wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4dd9a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I think you deserve a worthier adversary."
}

{
  "id": "line:07218d2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I mean...[p/] She can be a pain sometimes,[p/] but I'm glad that she pursues justice even if it means she loses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670ede",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "It was strange...[p/] I would've never seen myself holding such high respect for a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d4617",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Anyways,[p/] I wonder what would drive a noble like her into becoming a lowly prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ffe63",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I'd love to know the story behind that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa2faa",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Eris"
}

{
  "id": "line:08957d5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We know that Wallace was accepted through Redmond's program..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ee94b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: But what about you, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae364b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Are you trying to ask me if I'm a noble bastard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ae46e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry, I didn't mean-"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1bf0d",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: No need to apologize."
}

{
  "id": "line:09be314",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Although,[p/] the answer to that question is a bit...[p/] complicated."
}

{
  "id": "line:026690e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: My family is quite wealthy, but I wouldn't consider them a part of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd25c",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] Her family must've been part of a guild or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c701a7",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I would say it's more like several circles."
}

{
  "id": "line:06afcb8",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherine"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bdb66",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Catherine Bellwether wasn't the best person."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef808",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: She constantly used her authority to belittle and torment people."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a1403",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I'm sure the world is better off without her in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16a9e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/]That's extremely blunt,[p/] Eris..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1d6d5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "But I couldn't exactly disagree with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8f444",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I have no interest in indulging those in power who are unworthy of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b97f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Wallace"
}

{
  "id": "line:057db98",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: It's strange, really."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab4d2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: If it weren't for his disposition,[p/] Wallace would be quite the person to fear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8f5cd",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06430ed",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: It's clear to the three of [i]us[/i] that he didn't commit the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e346ec",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: But think about how easily he [i]could[/i] have done what he was accused of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0807245",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: He could instantly kill anyone using [b]Necrotic Blight[/b],[p/] and he could even raise them as undead using [b]Animate Corpse[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05604db",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Wallace would never do something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:086b362",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I agree."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce334",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: But one can often be surprised by what someone can do if they are pushed far enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:05809c2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: It really makes me wonder how idiotic the people who bully him are."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bba04",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "I'd rather not think about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:085b7ca",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Player: Theodore"
}

{
  "id": "line:0daf8c2",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were with the headmaster in his office earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2a915",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you two acquaintances?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26e27",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: In a way, yes.[p/] You could say that I’m a patron of his."
}

{
  "id": "line:0978d10",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I’m interested in why he would go so far as to include the commonfolk in the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:029c7d5",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: His generosity can clearly be a vice sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2492e",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Enrolling commonfolk mages into the academy was already a controversial move."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c65c26",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: But teaching one of them [b]necromancy[/b] illegally..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d7d50",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Even [i]if[/i] Wallace is acquitted,[p/] I don't see things getting easier for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a159ef",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fa229",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fdd33",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Really, now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94263",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I can't tell you [i]everything[/i] you need to get through this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0152870",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Eris: What would be the fun in that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c4d0f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6d61d",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion...?[p/] What are we doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05ac9",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m...[p/] not sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0400f9a",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "For some reason,[p/] I felt drawn to this place."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cd37f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "I was supposed to make my way back to the Academy,[p/] but I suddenly found myself here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe955",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "It was strange,[p/] but I couldn't even remember how we'd arrived here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515f52",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wait...[p/][s/] Is that Eris?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3345",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "Celeste pointed further into the cemetery.[p/] Eris was standing there in front of a gravestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0929145",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "She was placing flowers on it and appeared to be chanting a short prayer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b70895",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Well...[p/] We found her."
}

{
  "id": "line:045febd",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: We...[p/] should probably talk to her later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a610e8",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: It would be rude to disturb her now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7705",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "As we were about to leave,[p/] Eris suddenly turned to face us."
}

{
  "id": "line:058316f",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "She was far away,[p/] but she'd clearly noticed us and was beckoning us over."
}

{
  "id": "line:004310b",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: Oh, hello there.[p/] Were you two looking for me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054dbd8",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: S-[p/]Sorry.[p/] We [i]were[/i] looking for you,[p/] but we understand if you’d rather talk later..."
}

{
  "id": "line:043d952",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: No.[p/] I was just finishing up here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aaf09",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: Did you have something you wanted to talk to me about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a61a92",
  "node": "Cemetery_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Well...[p/] We wanted to ask you some questions about the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec08e5",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh, Tyrion![p/] I almost forgot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b853a3",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Let me show you one of the new spells I learned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0396d3f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...[b]REPERIO ARCANUM[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0776af7",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0204c2e",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/][s/]What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c354b2",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: [i]That[/i] is the incantation for the [b]Detect Magic[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f8da6",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: [b]Detect Magic[/b]...?[p/] Wait...[p/][s/] Does that mean—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2981e",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Yep![p/][s/] I can see magical traces while we're EXAMINING crime scenes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e33c2e",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Painting"
}

{
  "id": "line:0355fe4",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of some sort of musician."
}

{
  "id": "line:0295ae3",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's some text written below it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09953a4",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Doctor Nicolas Goussu:[p/] Inventor of the Arcane Engine.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d453ba",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"His work revolutionized trade and travel across the seas.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:01a0488",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"He was well known for not discriminating between the commonfolk and the nobility,[p/] judging his assistants based purely on their merit.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:06b49d5",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"When he wasn't conducting research within the Imperial Academy,[p/] he was known to compose symphonies in his free time.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:039b7cb",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "It sounded like he was a man of many talents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfdd45",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc886b",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a chalk outline where the professor's body was."
}

{
  "id": "line:017fa27",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It appears that most of this blood came from her abdomen."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ee685",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that where the fatal wound was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:089ce74",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:089996f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: There’s a lot of blood in this puddle...[p/] but there’s no trail leading to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a375cf",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: And there aren't any magical traces anywhere else in the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fdce2",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt the murderer used magic to clean it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0847b",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Does that mean that the murderer attacked her in this room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3c918",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: Maybe...[p/] But it’s hard to say for certain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0780503",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d229",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: The lecture hall has a window."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2ab6",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I feel like I'd just stare outside all day if I had to sit in this place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0394c45",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: How long do they have to sit here, anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd9fdb",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Lectures here last for an hour at a minimum."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d809c",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: An [i]hour[/i]?![p/] No wonder all the nobles are such psychopaths!"
}

{
  "id": "line:034f31f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Present company excluded, I hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9c2a0",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] You're not that bad, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd397e",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...How have you learned so many spells if you're so distractible?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cd4cc",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't know.[p/] I just look at the spell formula and...[p/] do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2dfd0",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f6b25",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is that not normal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00e9b",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Books"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cbae7",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh![p/] They have books here too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd45d9",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: These appear to be textbooks about alchemy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0195137",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Aw...[p/] Lame."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2324",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Students"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9d361",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: This must be where the students sit during lectures."
}

{
  "id": "line:0693662",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I can't imagine sitting in one place all day."
}

{
  "id": "line:01db4f1",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you never attended a school before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:071ab02",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you seriously think a dump like Kornhaven has standardized education?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c0c5f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I learned from books that I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0832d2f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "She glanced at Steelwind before finishing that thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e79a4",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I learned from books that I [i]appropriated[/i] from some traveling merchants."
}

{
  "id": "line:04453c6",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: What about you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098536d",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I attended a public school when I was younger,[p/] but Ms. Tymora handled most of my education herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bdf2a",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc884",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Detect Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c4c1d",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "There was a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626f75",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "According to Steelwind,[p/] that was the primary piece of evidence implicating Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:014ddd4",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9905c",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: What’s wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096e67c",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] in Bellwether's blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c8316",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: [b]Necromancy[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b4faf",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Isn’t [b]necromancy[/b] the type of magic that creates zombies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bbb7d",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: She’s not just going to get up and walk away, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0746d67",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: ...We’re honestly not sure.[p/] The Inquisition is on edge about that as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9efe9",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: But how does that implicate Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067c008",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Oh,[p/] he didn't tell you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbda46",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: Wallace Nightgrave is a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea9119",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: We believe that he drained her life force using a spell called [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ccb0a",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Spells like that tend to interfere with the [b]divination[/b] spell we use to identify the cause of death."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7508",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: However,[p/] there were no visible wounds.[p/] Only a [b]necromancy[/b] spell could have killed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:056d7fa",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have a copy of the Autopsy Report?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070721f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Of course,[p/] but it's incomplete because of the aforementioned reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc79cf",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: This whole ordeal has put everyone on edge."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3f40",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: This is the first case of necrotic homicide we've had in nearly a century."
}

{
  "id": "line:011a0ab",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "I couldn't believe it...[p/] I'd only read about [b]necromancy[/b] in fantasy novels."
}

{
  "id": "line:0707d3d",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "I never imagined that I'd end up defending a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b764b",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: But if what you're saying is true,[p/] weren’t there plenty of other mages who could use [b]necromancy[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a26d",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: This [i]is[/i] an academy for mages, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6a680",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: No.[p/] The knowledge required to learn [b]necromancy[/b] is heavily controlled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2cf89",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Mr. Nightgrave already violated several laws simply by learning these spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0721e15",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: I'm baffled as to how he even got access to that knowledge in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebf8a3",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Right...[p/] [b]Necromancy[/b] sounded like some dark magic—[p/]even by the nobility's standards."
}

{
  "id": "line:050a4f9",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "I'd be terrified to know why [i]anyone[/i] would want to learn that type of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb112",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "ARIA: The fact that he was the only known student who knew these spells makes him our only suspect. [h=\"But it’s still too convenient...|Something else is happening...\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4f87f",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0354c6e",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "I seldom caught thoughts from Steelwind,[p/] and they usually only appeared when someone brought up her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:031a172",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "She was usually very composed,[p/] and I still didn't see a hint of that uneasiness in her posture."
}

{
  "id": "line:0392a9b",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "Normally,[p/] I could only see thoughts when the target was stressed or excited..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7683",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "[i]Something[/i] about this case must've been rattling her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aca09",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Is there something you’re not telling us, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0094f73",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b884a8",
  "node": "Classroom_Examine",
  "text": "The Eye couldn't catch any more thoughts from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0316b38",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Questions for us"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c18a5b",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Ms. McCoy.[p/] It’s my understanding that you were adopted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4e3cf",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Would you happen to know who your biological parents are?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4333a",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste tensed and shifted uncomfortably."
}

{
  "id": "line:0721359",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...That's kind of personal, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5c1b",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: You agreed to answer my questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9546c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I [i]did[/i],[p/] but I didn’t think you meant—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08719e9",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: I-[p/][s/]It’s fine, Tyrion.[p/] It's for Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4155",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "She took a breath.[p/] This had always been a sore subject for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:074b827",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: I don’t know who my birth parents are.[p/] I’ve never tried looking for them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7a1a9",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3e1a6",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: If I recall correctly,[p/] your [b]Spell Compendium[/b] only contained one spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bd99d",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: How did you learn [b]Mage Blade[/b] in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0909fea",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: I bought a scroll from a merchant a few years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea27d8",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It had [b]Mage Blade's[/b] spell formula on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abcee0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: But surely someone taught you how to cast it."
}

{
  "id": "line:046f929",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: No, I'm self-taught."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b3b66",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Steelwind's eyes narrowed.[p/] She was being unusually interrogative about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e9dc",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...You can't teach yourself magic, Ms. McCoy.[p/] That's not possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d416f3",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Well,[p/] [i]I[/i] did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca6500",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...Are you sure you're not mistaken?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f570c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hey![p/] I've got a system, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb1683",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I even learned a few new spells today."
}

{
  "id": "line:024bc55",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I’m sorry...[p/] “spells”?[p/] As in plural?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f76a",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah![p/] [i]I'd[/i] like to think I'm pretty good at this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0327399",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: ...How long did it take you to learn these spells?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a38d3",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: A few hours, I think."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b35e8",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ... [h=\"She taught herself multiple spell formulas|within a few hours?!\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1a96",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c20101",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I think that’s all I need to ask for now.[p/] Thank you, Ms. McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c67e0f",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Um...[p/] Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d8886",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Steelwind looked like she was deep in thought.[p/] Why was she so interested in Celeste's magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7ed77",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Murder"
}

{
  "id": "line:078ee4a",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you know what happened here, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069d407",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Well,[p/] the City Watch received a call from the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:050164f",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: They reported an attack on campus grounds and put the entire building on lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb996d",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: The city watch set up a perimeter around the building while they waited for the system to deactivate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0574311",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: They had to wait?[p/] Why didn't the academy just deactivate the system manually?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0578f13",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I’m not sure about the specifics,[p/] but supposedly,[p/] the lockdown can’t be shut down once triggered.[p/] It's a safety mechanism."
}

{
  "id": "line:0594a64",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: You’ll have to ask one of the academy’s admins if you want to know more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0097b1d",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: From what I've heard,[p/] you two were also present during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb042c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Did either of you see anything suspicious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb74e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: No,[p/] but we actually met the professor that morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbecd2",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: She was obviously still alive then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0880f68",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I see...[p/] That [i]does[/i] match with the accounts from our other witnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:02116d9",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: She must have gone to her meeting with the headmaster afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:09972d0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: She had a meeting with the headmaster?[p/] How long did this go on for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a10188",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: From 12:00 PM to 1:00 PM—[p/]about an hour before her death."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f02c3",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "If the headmaster met with Bellwether,[p/] he might've known where she went after the meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:021a7a2",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Would you happen to have a map of the academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033d0df",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I do.[p/] I'll transfer it to your Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46db5",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: There’s only one direct path from the headmaster’s office to this lecture hall."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b92684",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Why would she even enter the lecture hall in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2142c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Did she die here,[p/] or was she murdered somewhere else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d673d8",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Rancid Smell"
}

{
  "id": "line:0802779",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/] That smell is driving me crazy."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3bd0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: What [i]is[/i] that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9fc0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: There was a bit of an accident during an alchemy lecture a few days ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0032348",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: The instructor misread the directions for an experiment."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1e83",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: As a result,[p/] he accidentally produced this rancid-smelling vapor."
}

{
  "id": "line:069ff53",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Vapor...?[p/] It’s not toxic, is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d4053",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I wouldn’t be standing here if it were."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3a17",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...It’s just extremely unpleasant to the senses."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a1922",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: They temporarily closed this lecture hall until they could get rid of the smell."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bf42e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: House Steelwind actually...[p/] [i]used[/i] a similar concoction during the Great Luminite War."
}

{
  "id": "line:022eb53",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: See?[p/] This is why I stick to [b]transmutation[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:026cbe2",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Ms. McCoy.[p/] Alchemy is a [i]branch[/i] of [b]transmutation[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a1188",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e03572",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I could've been making potions this entire time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efb618",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "How was the body discovered?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ac53",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: How was the body discovered?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0899f78",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Two members of the kitchen staff spotted her body inside this classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca9bd5",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: They reported the situation to the campus admin while they attempted to save her life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df60d4",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: But it was too late.[p/] The professor had already passed away long before any healers arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29fbd",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Those two staff members...[p/] Who were they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f29b1",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Valentina and Valerie Ianus.[p/] They’re sisters."
}

{
  "id": "line:09caced",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: How are they holding up?[p/] I imagine they'd be rattled after discovering the body of their coworker."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e090",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: From what Orym said,[p/] they were extremely tense during questioning,[p/] but I suppose that's to be expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:09900c9",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: He told me that they couldn't sit still."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9374b",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: He found it difficult to take their statements because of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3325",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They \"couldn't sit still\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb72f3",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Well,[p/] he's always making excuses for his incompetence."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e3021",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Why is Wallace a Suspect?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c27e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: We’ve already told the Inquisition this,[p/] but Wallace was with us the entire time.[p/] He has a perfect alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:02722f0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Strong, maybe,[p/] but his alibi is far from perfect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d37fc1",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Ms. McCoy herself told us that.[p/] There was a small time period when she wasn't with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfc7c5",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:097bfdb",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right...[p/] It was after we came to check on you when you knocked over that shelf."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a277",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: We got separated,[p/] and I kind of got...[p/] lost in the fiction section."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b71f3",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: She found an early release copy of [i]Deaths at Daggerfall[/i].[p/] She binge-read it for over an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0480740",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't just rat me out to him![p/][s/] He's my boss!"
}

{
  "id": "line:017ef53",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Nonsense.[p/] They're well-written books.[p/] No one would fault you for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:056271b",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "I mean—[p/]I [i]might[/i] fault her for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b5c99",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] You read them too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08104d9",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f76fa",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What did you think about the ending of \"The Uncrowned\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02db2ba",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00df645",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I found the cliffhanger to be needlessly unsatisfying."
}

{
  "id": "line:00522aa",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: They're stringing the readers along to sell more copies of the sequel."
}

{
  "id": "line:076877c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, come on![p/][s/] Anticipation just makes each new book that much more fulfilling."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a35a6",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f13a",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I eat brunch with the author occasionally.[p/] The fame has clearly gotten to her head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0417230",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: She's clearly just dragging her feet to raise profits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0441ac6",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You eat brunch with Altheris Duskweaver?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0090f3e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "I cleared my throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc61e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Everyone![p/] We are [i]all[/i] supposed to be working right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:019d1df",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You're such a killjoy sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9c5b0",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] He's right.[p/] I don't know what got into me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f746e",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Well,[p/] after this case is over,[p/] I'm tagging along for brunch with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74a27",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e37a8c",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] you tried to convict me for murdering my dad."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b5b3f",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You owe me, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a69ef6",
  "node": "Classroom_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I suppose you have a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e8c5f",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Ah,[p/] an Attorney's Runestone.[p/] I have one of these myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff1032",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're useful, aren't they?[p/] The note-taking and picture functions save so much time during these investigations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e47799",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: They're really a marvel of artificery.[p/] You'll see a lot of these among the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:052f632",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would nobles need to store evidence?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048746d",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:063238e",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: They have other uses, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0206f11",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I wasn't expecting to meet you here, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:094c37e",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: The Imperial Academy isn't exactly open to outsiders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7aed8",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We originally came here to do some research,[p/] but I never expected to get wrapped up in another homicide..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbbcff",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...What kind of research were you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033785c",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't bother asking.[p/] He won't tell you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e5bfb",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I'm glad to see you under less...[p/] dire circumstances, Ms. McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b328c3",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Are you accompanying Mr. Cuthbert on his investigation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e176f6",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] I'm working as Tyrion's bodyguard now."
}

{
  "id": "line:08eb6a7",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I see.[p/] Well, you certainly have the credentials for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ebde6",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Although,[p/] I'm surprised he's able to afford your services."
}

{
  "id": "line:022794c",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What's [i]that[/i] supposed to mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f01a5",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I meant no offense,[p/] but work like this [i]does[/i] appear to be below Ms. McCoy's pay grade."
}

{
  "id": "line:02741ea",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] I was surprised, too.[p/] Ruby pays me a lot to protect this guy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba00c3",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Ah,[p/] Ruby Tymora is paying you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a155b",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...I suppose that makes more sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0b340",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Orym"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a5cd2",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was surprised to see [i]you[/i] conducting the investigation, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9ade2",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why don't you leave things to Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e60214",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Please.[p/] I can barely trust that oaf to make me coffee."
}

{
  "id": "line:0884b6d",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: After last time,[p/] I feel much more confident overseeing the investigation myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2584f",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "The Inquisition didn't seem to be helping her at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:067f767",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "They were just standing guard while [i]she[/i] did all of the work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccac00",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: Foul"
}

{
  "id": "line:071505c",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] This rancid smell is really horrible."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3b1f",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: Yes.[p/] I don't blame you for finding it distracting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9713b",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: All because of a mistake during an alchemy experiment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0127879",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I was surprised too.[p/] It's not like the headmaster to make a mistake like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01066c8",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, the headmaster teaches alchemy here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0493b21",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherine|Blood|Blood2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb0013",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: As a mage from a noble house,[p/] you must have gone to school here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcae3d",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know Catherine Bellwether while you were here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01363ee",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I unfortunately did.[p/] I constantly clashed with her over her treatment of the commoners here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb299f",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: One of my biggest regrets is failing to remove her from her position before I graduated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0948229",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: But she was a friend of House Frega.[p/] There wasn't much I could do against that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acaeb1",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "It sounded like [i]many[/i] people didn't get along with the professor..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c6bee",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I would say more,[p/] but it's all in the past,[p/] and I'm not one to speak ill of the dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d523f",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: SteelOrd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0694dc1",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you giving us access to the crime scene,[p/] but not the Inquisition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca92a3",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: They work under you, don't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b69b5",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...I simply trust you two.[p/] Are you trying to imply that I shouldn't?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c4baa",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d331",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: Four"
}

{
  "id": "line:054c3e4",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind...[p/] Is it possible that this case involves a Pillar Family other than yours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec9d58",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08425aa",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Her eyes twitched ever so slightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:08aea57",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: ...As I said before,[p/] you'll do better than that if you want to bluff me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b48b9c",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Player: Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4fad6",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023c459",
  "node": "Aria_Present",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry.[p/] But I'm afraid I can't say much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c89960",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "KNIGHT: Hey![p/][s/] Stop right there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ec68a",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "As we tried to enter the classroom,[p/] one of the Inquisition knights stepped between us and the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d2179",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "He tried to make himself look bigger,[p/] but I could see him falter when he recognized Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:006c099",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m a defense attorney.[p/] We have a right to investigate the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e16c1",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "KNIGHT: ...Yeah?[p/] From what I’ve heard,[p/] the kid doesn’t [i]have[/i] an attorney yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ccc17",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I still needed to talk to Wallace about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db02d7",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "I doubted Wallace had another attorney in mind,[p/] but I would have less jurisdiction until he made it official."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a6ca2",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: It’s quite all right.[p/] Let them in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73d3d",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "KNIGHT: L-[p/][s/]Lady Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:085ce00",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: What have I told you about calling me that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04be381",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: While you work under me,[p/] you will address me as \"[i]Prosecutor[/i] Steelwind\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2c1fb",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "KNIGHT: Y-[p/][s/]yes, L—[p/][s/] [i]Prosecutor[/i][p/][s/] Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0983bd4",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/] What’s that smell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3b694",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "As we entered the classroom,[p/] a sour and rancid odor blew over us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d20fa9",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "My eyes began to tear up.[p/] I had to take a handkerchief from my pocket to cover my nose."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f155d",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: Don’t worry.[p/] You eventually get used to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:093d805",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: What are you even doing here, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092bfc0",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: I’m here to coordinate the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d5212",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "I looked around the room.[p/] There wasn't a single Inquisition knight to be found.[p/] It was only her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ada96c",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Was she investigating the crime scene by herself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0936100",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Due to the circumstances,[p/] I’ve decided to handle this case personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210f10",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Since we’ve got you here,[p/] could we ask you some questions about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef1b3e",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Can I assume that you're planning to defend this case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a985f",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Aria: That would make you my opponent.[p/] What do I have to gain from helping you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bffc2",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc851e",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: However,[p/] I [i]would[/i] be willing to answer your questions..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0133383",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Aria: But only if you answer some of mine as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e00ea8",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...[p/] Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed2ab2",
  "node": "Classroom_Check",
  "text": "Did she want to ask us about Wallace's alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c150c7",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "It was time for the trial,[p/] and my heart was thundering against my chest like a drum."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ec7c8",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Luckily,[p/] I'd been reading about some meditative techniques after what happened last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05decdd",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "I just needed to take deep breaths and relax."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b6bf1",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "I breathed in.[p/] I breathed out.[p/] I breathed in—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02576c8",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hi, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f266b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "TYRION: Gah![p/][s/] Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02de7b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "TYRION: D-[p/][s/]Don’t sneak up on me like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0964275",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Are your nerves acting up again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46906",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Come on.[p/] It’s not as if this is your first time defending someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0266b68",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "TYRION: No,[p/] it's just my [i]second[/i] time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe29a",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/] It’s too bad Ruby couldn’t make it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16917",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’d [i]say[/i] that you should calm down for Wallace’s sake,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2e59c",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "WALLACE: There are so many people here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0821083",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "WALLACE: A-[p/][s/]And they're all looking at me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:044c4a3",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "WALLACE: Their eyes are prying into me like a pack of flesh-eating maggots!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f8633",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Ew."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b989af",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "I needed to calm down...[p/] I was just making Wallace more nervous."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d975c",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0810d4f",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "TYRION: ...D-[p/][s/]Don’t worry, Wallace![p/] Our investigation revealed a lot of weaknesses in the prosecution’s case."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a8daf",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "TYRION: We have a strong case for your acquittal."
}

{
  "id": "line:075104d",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "WALLACE: O-[p/]Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f71252",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Actually,[p/] that [i]was[/i] true.[p/] I really had nothing to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7e9b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "CELESTE: See?[p/] You can be confident when you want to be."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a73989",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is now in session for the trial of Wallace Nightgrave."
}

{
  "id": "line:007516a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution is ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0906358",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "TYRION: The defense is also ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78a4f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: Very well.[p/] Prosecutor Steelwind,[p/] could you please list the charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fab4c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Nightgrave is a second-year student at the Wyverngarde Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0128919",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "AriaC: He is charged with first-degree murder,[p/] negligent misuse of the Arcane Arts,[p/] and illegal practice of advanced [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dac0d6",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: [b]\"N-[p/][s/]Necromancy\"[/b]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a191a2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: Do you mean to tell me that the defendant is a necromancer?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0199894",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Gallery: I can’t believe it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0faf42f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Gallery: A [i]necromancer[/i]?[p/] In [i]this[/i] day and age?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d41f0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Gallery: How could the kingdom allow this to happen?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:025ec76",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "TYRION: Your Honor![p/][s/] I would like to remind the court that they are obligated to judge my client objectively."
}

{
  "id": "line:0470637",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: O-[p/][s/]Of course...![p/] But one can easily see it from the list of charges."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf6a4",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "JUDGE: [b]Necromancy[/b] plays a large role in the charges."
}

{
  "id": "line:047560a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Indeed.[p/] The crime occurred within the academy this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c50b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: The victim is Catherine Bellwether:[p/] a professor at the school."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e14fe2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Although there were no witnesses to the crime,[p/] traces of [b]necromancy[/b] were detected on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a427f7",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Furthermore,[p/] the autopsy report shows that the body has no physical wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:078d2e7",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: [b]Necromancy[/b] is the only type of magic that can harm an individual without physically wounding them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af6efe",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Additionally,[p/] an alchemist report shows no signs of poison or disease."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c5458",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: One could only conclude that a necromancer had committed the crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d6f78",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Judge: I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec4055",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: As many of you know,[p/] the practice of advanced [b]necromancy[/b] is outlawed in the Kingdom of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d07b64",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Aside from the defendant,[p/] no other students had learned advanced necrotic magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:09efe8d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: As such,[p/] the defendant was the only mage in that building capable of committing the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa569b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: I see.[p/] That is certainly compelling evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b122c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "AriaC: To properly present our case,[p/] the prosecution would like to call Commander Orym White to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727613",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Commander White,[p/] please testify to the court about the Inquisition’s findings."
}

{
  "id": "line:07eedc1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "ORYM: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0922633",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Orym: It started when the city watch got a call from the Imperial Academy.[p/] Someone was attacked,[p/] and the whole building was put on lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c580f8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Orym: We set up a perimeter around the area and waited for the lockdown system to deactivate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0781a64",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Orym: When we finally got into the building,[p/] the prosecutor personally inspected the body and detected traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca3e74",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Orym: There were no cuts or bruises on the body either.[p/] The entire body was clean."
}

{
  "id": "line:046de16",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Orym: With those two pieces of evidence,[p/] we concluded that it could only be the necromancer kid that did it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6b353",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "The Inquisition’s testimony was just as I'd expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0541a87",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "I'd already found and identified the holes in Steelwind’s case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0951370",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "All I had to do was find that hole in the commander’s testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:04adc62",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] You may begin your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e3c65",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: It started when the city watch got a call from the Imperial Academy.[p/] Someone was attacked,[p/] and the whole building was put in lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b95b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: What time did this call come in?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009a830",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: A little after 3:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:084d9c5",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: It was a few minutes after the murder was discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0664a05",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I remember that was around the time the lockdown occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:045a3ac",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "The lockdown couldn't be ended manually,[p/] so they must have been forced to wait for an hour until it was lifted."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c240c",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: How secure was this perimeter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdbe6b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: Is it possible that someone slipped past you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0418f8e",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: The Inquisition was working in conjunction with the City Watch [i]and[/i] the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:07233a5",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: With that many soldiers at the scene,[p/] it’s very unlikely that [i]anyone[/i] escaped unnoticed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dad250",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "That made sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fbd6d",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "For better or for worse,[p/] the kingdom must have acted quickly to protect a building filled with the children of every noble family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc3d65",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: Why did the prosecutor inspect the body instead of the Inquisition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:047a353",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "ORYM: ...Well—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9559",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: How I chose to lead the investigation is irrelevant to the proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:019ca11",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Or would you like to insinuate that [i]I’m[/i] not as competent as Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b1114",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not a question of your competency, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfe7f4",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just find your actions to be bizarre,[p/] given how you usually work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0088bc2",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "JUDGE: While the court admits that the prosecutor’s actions are unorthodox,[p/] we find the presence of a necromancer to be an unorthodox situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f554b1",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Judge: I see no reason to question the prosecutor's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d776ed",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: Thank you, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:022a3e0",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: How carefully was the body checked?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0877261",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: Perhaps the prosecution missed something like a small puncture wound."
}

{
  "id": "line:0357336",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: The coroner couldn’t find even the smallest cut,[p/] bruise,[p/] or fracture on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:005278b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: Furthermore,[p/] the alchemist’s report showed no signs of poison or disease."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bae01",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: The [b]necromancy[/b] spell had obfuscated the postmortem divination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0002821",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: I spared no expense to verify the cause of death through other means."
}

{
  "id": "line:0374350",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "That made sense.[p/] If someone had used [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on the body,[p/] it would have healed even the most minor of injuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f33b83",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "So,[p/] how do I prove that someone healed the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096737f",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: And the prosecution believes that my client used [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015eb91",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "ORYM: Yep.[p/] It’s the only way that the crime scene makes any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5198b",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "JUDGE: “[b]Necrotic Blight[/b]”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5c6ce",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "JUDGE: I’m afraid I’ve never heard of this spell before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e77a92",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: [b]Necrotic Blight[/b] is a spell that drains the life force from its target."
}

{
  "id": "line:0272572",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: When used on a living human,[p/] it makes their bodily functions cease."
}

{
  "id": "line:025cb6d",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "AriaC: Their body dies soon after."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ad7b7",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "JUDGE: I-[p/]I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:042da80",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Gallery: What a horrible spell!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac982f",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Gallery: That commoner should have never been allowed to learn something like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9829d",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Gallery: I'd thought there would be more protection against [i]children[/i] learning this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:000426e",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Wallace's Spell Compendium really wasn't doing him any favours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a41b71",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "...There really is a large stigma against necromancers, isn't there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f268c5",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Player: Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f1b41",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "CELESTE: We already collected a lot of evidence after investigating the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bdcff",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "CELESTE: We already know that the Inquisition’s theory contradicts one of the clues that we found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0829b20",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "TYRION: Right.[p/] All I have to do is present that contradiction to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb48bc",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Player: Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce941",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] It's clear that the witness's testimony is contradictory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0390972",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this piece of evidence proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d52b7c",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Judge: I fail to see how that proves anything, Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:042509f",
  "node": "Cross_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e7b4",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Commander White.[p/] It appears that you’ve neglected to mention one key detail of the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac426e",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "ORYM: Yeah?[p/] And what’s that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a15d6c",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: During your testimony,[p/] you said that the entire body was clean."
}

{
  "id": "line:06235e5",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: I [i]will[/i] admit that there weren’t any wounds on the body..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ded7a4",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: However,[p/][s/] the body was certainly not clean!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09101b2",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0407c20",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: At the scene of the crime,[p/] there was a large pool of blood located where the body was."
}

{
  "id": "line:000760a",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: This blood had to have come from the victim’s body,[p/][s/] and it was certainly not clean like the commander testified!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd964a",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "JUDGE: I’m sorry, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but I fail to see the significance of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a4c3e",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: I’d like to remind the court of the prosecution’s case against my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ef821",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: They are accusing him of murdering the victim using [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]:[p/] a spell which would [i]not[/i] have physically wounded the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd20b5",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: So why was there any blood at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00949ed",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Let’s not get ahead of ourselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607a25",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: The fact still stands.[p/] There were no wounds on the body,[p/] nor were there any reports of poison or disease on the autopsy."
}

{
  "id": "line:00723d9",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: There are clearly magical elements in this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1dc85",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: But Catherine Bellwether [i]was[/i] bleeding profusely at some point!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a41ac7",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: How else would there be a bloodstain on the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a49f",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you have an explanation for that, Ms. Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f545a7",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: ...No.[p/] I'll admit that the prosecution doesn't have an explanation for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:035103c",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: And while I do find the circumstances questionable,[p/] all other evidence clearly points to the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5b142",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "AriaC: So tell me, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] if the victim wasn’t killed with [b]necromancy[/b],[p/] why was there a trace of it on the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048bc81",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m glad you asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf44f",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: I’d like to present a spell that could have left a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0680855",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Mend Wounds"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e886f",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Necrotic Blight"
}

{
  "id": "line:095099b",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0894a8c",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Judge: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:044df64",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5a0f",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Celeste: We're supposed to prove that the trace [i]wasn't[/i] left by [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba3210",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Your honor,[p/] it appears that the defense is admitting defeat."
}

{
  "id": "line:008861e",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: [b]Necrotic Blight[/b] is the only spell that would have left that trace."
}

{
  "id": "line:05422df",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/]Wait...[p/][s/] That was a mistake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d03dd",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I meant to present a [i]different[/i] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0046962",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Judge: Um...[p/] What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08544ad",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]This[/i] is what left the trace of [b]necromancy[/b] at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0484dcd",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: I fail to see how [i]that[/i] could leave a trace of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:094c9bb",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/]Oh,[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a5b97",
  "node": "OrymObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]However[/i],[p/][s/] [i]that's[/i] not the spell I was speaking of!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0426475",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: [b]Mend Wounds[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af01e5",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Correct me if I’m wrong,[p/] but isn’t that a healing spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef365f",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s correct, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0814a4c",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Spells from the school of [b]necromancy[/b] can control the forces of death [i]and[/i] life!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6fabb",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: [b]Mend Wounds[/b] is, in fact, a [b]necromancy[/b] spell!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e91ed7",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Really, now?[p/] I wasn't aware of this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eea11b",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]Now[/i] I’d like the court to consider the following..."
}

{
  "id": "line:074b925",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: What would happen if Bellwether was wounded,[p/] and someone attempted to heal her using [b]Mend Wounds[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0be9b",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: All of her wounds would disappear from her body!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0172df5",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: I see...[p/] That [i]does[/i] make sense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa44a2",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Do you think I'm that incompetent, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043c3ca",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Frankly,[p/] I'm a little insulted."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c9f5d",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: The Inquisition is well aware of what happens when a mage attempts to save a victim using [b]Mend Wounds[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0502b33",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: The healers that arrived at the scene already confirmed that the victim was long dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4e1e",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: None of them attempted to heal her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0395517",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well,[p/] what if someone tried to heal her and didn't report it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ad75",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Please.[p/] None of the healers would have anything to gain by doing so."
}

{
  "id": "line:049ce09",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: In fact,[p/] as a necromancer,[p/] the defendant could have easily carried out the described scenario."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa9bd",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: He could have cast [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on the victim after murdering her to confound the investigation!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b73193",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "At the end of the day,[p/] the burden of proof was on us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0276329",
  "node": "OrymObj_2",
  "text": "But if I could prove someone else healed the body,[p/] I would sever the only thread linking Wallace to the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8b6e6",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "Whoever this healer was...[p/] Valentina definitely knew her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4c610",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Your Honor.[p/] I will admit that I don’t have any evidence to support my theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f49a96",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: However,[p/] I [i]do[/i] believe that we can bring it to light."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5270d",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: There may have been [i]two[/i] people that witnessed someone cast magic on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e37648",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Valentina and Valerie Ianus:[p/][s/] the sisters who discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4cbc",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...This is nonsense.[p/] We’ve already questioned those two witnesses extensively."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d7323",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: If they [i]had[/i] witnessed something like that,[p/] it would have come up in their testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ed61a",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: If that’s true,[p/] then the courts have nothing to lose by hearing their testimonies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607bec",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Very well.[p/] If you’re so confident,[p/] let’s hear her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eab4a5",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: It seems the prosecution has no objections."
}

{
  "id": "line:0834ccd",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: If this line of questioning leads nowhere, however,[p/] I see no reason to further prolong this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ba9b",
  "node": "OrymObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Of course, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eebdf0",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...! [h=\"Oh, crap!|It’s that guy from before!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6be09",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ... [h=\"What?!|He's the necromancer’s lawyer?!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78db3",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "She just arrived at the stand,[p/] and she was already stressed out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abeac3",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "That would work in my favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b6d9",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0149167",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: U-[p/]Um...[p/] My name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f85445",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] there’s no need to be so nervous."
}

{
  "id": "line:02db16e",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: We merely want to hear about what you saw on the day of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0156c",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: R-[p/]Right.[p/] I-[p/]it’s just that guy over there.[p/] He..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0766e45",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Are you talking about Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0686ade",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Did this man harass you, witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78382",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/]Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd8a9",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/][s/] Yeah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a88fe",
  "node": "OrymObj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: He [i]super[/i] harassed me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb144a",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "JUDGE: Mr. Cuthbert, I would expect someone of your profession to behave more professionally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a19737",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "I could hear Celeste snickering under her breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe7fc3",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "TYRION: You're enjoying this far too much..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea1ffd",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "TYRION: A-[p/]Anyways,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the court, Ms. Ianus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0932a03",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ... [h=\"Just calm down.|He can’t prove anything.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b014b",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...My name is Valentina Ianus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f64aff",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I'm the head chef at the Wyverngarde Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f4430",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "Judge: Really?[p/] And at such a young age."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc843b",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: As I recall,[p/] you were one of the witnesses who discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26024",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Apparently,[p/] the defense finds your involvement suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:033f7c9",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2ad2",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Rest assured, Ms. Ianus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66c69",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: In this courtroom,[p/] you will be protected from Mr. Cuthbert’s “harassment”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0434b78",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "TYRION: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f857db",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Now,[p/] please testify to the court on what happened that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffedcf",
  "node": "OrymObj_5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/]Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e347de",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "Valentina: I was walking with my sister in the west wing when we noticed something in a nearby classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5669a",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "Valentina: We looked over to see what it was.[p/][s/] That's when we saw Ms. Bellwether bleeding on the ground!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f95290",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "Valentina: My sister tried her best to help her,[p/] but the professor had already lost a lot of blood..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67097",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "Valentina: While my sister did that,[p/] I used an emergency communication device to call for help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df902e",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "Valentina: But it was too late.[p/] By the time her bleeding stopped,[p/] she’d already lost too much blood..."
}

{
  "id": "line:052970e",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hm...[p/] If your theory is true,[p/] that means she just lied in her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c1fc1",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "CELESTE: She’s holding something back."
}

{
  "id": "line:09de345",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "TYRION: She definitely saw more than she’s letting on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f2e3",
  "node": "ValTest",
  "text": "I just needed to prove that somehow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b0577",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: Where were you two coming from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fdcc2",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: We came from the kitchen."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e57cb",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: We were taking a break after the lunch rush."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2fb8",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "The cafeteria was on the west side of the academy,[p/] so that made sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dda38b",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "AriaC: What did you see in the classroom, Ms. Ianus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043c3bd",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you notice anything else strange in the lecture hall?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d25ed8",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Well, there [i]was[/i] that terrible smell."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3ee2",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: It was awful.[p/] I almost couldn’t see because of how much I was tearing up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abd70e",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "It makes sense...[p/] Aside from Bellwether,[p/] that smell was the most notable thing in that room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0765bee",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "It would've been hard to notice anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0684b81",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "She tried to...[p/] “help her”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36f9c",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus.[p/] How exactly did your sister try to help Ms. Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f79bf",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What? [h=\"Agh!|I slipped up!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a39cd",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0252d8f",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: My sister used first aid to try to stop the bleeding."
}

{
  "id": "line:077f2f9",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: I...[p/] see.[p/] Could you please add that detail to your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8c07",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah...[p/] Sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e24fe",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "Valentina: She used first aid and applied pressure to her wound to stop the bleeding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b508cc",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: Your sister knows how to use a first aid kit?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0355992",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/]Yeah,[p/] it was covered in our training when we first started working there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0279c",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: With all the nobles around,[p/] I guess the headmaster wanted to make sure we were prepared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de30f2",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: A device?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0766811",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "AriaC: It’s a communication device for use in an emergency."
}

{
  "id": "line:09af8cf",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: I see.[p/] So who [i]did[/i] you contact?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0787d3c",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I wasn’t sure, honestly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0957775",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I could hear a lot of people talking on the other end."
}

{
  "id": "line:0609c7e",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "AriaC: That particular device broadcasts to the headmaster’s office and the City Watch Barracks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0372d19",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "AriaC: I imagine that’s why the headmaster was able to activate the lockdown so quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f089d6",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b4587",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: I see.[p/] That must have been a difficult experience for both of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff676e",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: It was especially hard on my sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2c70",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I think she blames herself for not being able to save her."
}

{
  "id": "line:026306c",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "She seemed sincere when she said that."
}

{
  "id": "line:056543e",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "I didn't catch any dissonant thoughts through the Eye either."
}

{
  "id": "line:072a8ab",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "CELESTE: Honestly,[p/] her testimony makes a lot of sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:070eca0",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "CELESTE: It’s hard to figure out which parts she might be lying about."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b18f8",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "TYRION: There has to be a contradiction here somewhere..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05416c1",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "CELESTE: Your theory is that Valentina saw someone use [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cebef",
  "node": "Cross_Val",
  "text": "CELESTE: You should focus on the statements that describe how they both interacted with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f232",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Witness.[p/] What is the meaning of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025f04b",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What?[p/][s/] Why are you looking at me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c666dc",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Maybe [i]I[/i] can elaborate, Ms. Ianus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0447b2e",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "TYRION: You weren’t present in the gallery earlier,[p/] were you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a0617",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: N-[p/][s/]No.[p/] I was waiting in the lobby."
}

{
  "id": "line:055abe4",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Lady Steelwind told me to wait there."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fb525",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "I considered myself lucky.[p/] This wouldn't have been nearly as easy if Valentina had seen my cross-examination of Oyrm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb3163",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "TYRION: You see, Ms. Ianus...[p/] One key element of the case is that the body [i]didn’t[/i] have any wounds on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d92b74",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/]Yeah?[p/] So?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff7298",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]So[/i], that begs the following question..."
}

{
  "id": "line:040358d",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "TYRION: How did Valerie apply first aid when there shouldn’t have been [i]any[/i] wounds on the body?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8caee",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: What?! [h=\"Ah! No...|Did I screw up?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:059e19b",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I-[p/][s/]I... [h=\"But I saw that wound on her!|What happened?!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7c76d",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "JUDGE: There’s clearly something amiss here."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b3a90",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "JUDGE: But I’m afraid I don’t fully understand the implications of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f2ed4",
  "node": "ValObj",
  "text": "JUDGE: Are you accusing the witness of committing perjury, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06700cb",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "When someone lied,[p/] they kept it as close to the truth as possible while changing minute details."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c591b",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "In her thoughts,[p/] Valentina said that she was sure she [i]saw[p/] a wound on Bellwether..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382a14",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "She also mentioned that [i]Valerie[/i] was the one who tried to save the professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701251",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "I knew that someone had cast healing magic on the body.[p/] That was why the wounds had disappeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc0d5d",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "If the wounds disappeared after the twins discovered the body,[p/] that could only mean one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fefd22",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: The witness [i]was[/i] lying, Your Honor...[p/] But not about everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0219ebb",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: Valerie Ianus [i]did[/i] try to save the victim's life by addressing her wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:097fed3",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: But she didn’t use first aid...[p/][s/] She used magic!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7c53",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...?! [h=\"How did he|figure it out?!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0441c2c",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but your theory is completely flawed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba409a",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: ...How so, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c10db",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Well,[p/] it’s quite simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:0263a77",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: We’ve already verified that neither of the sisters is a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d29e4",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0636716",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/]Wait...[p/] How can you be so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ae261",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: During the investigation,[p/] we had both the Ianus sisters attune to a [b]Spell Compendium[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0501ffc",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: It’s standard procedure for the Inquisition when interviewing witnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae8542",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/]Then that means..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03aac32",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Neither of the Ianus sisters could attune to a [b]Compendium[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:070c63c",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "VALENTINA: H-[p/][s/]Ha![p/][s/] T-[p/][s/]That’s right![p/][s/] The Inquisition checked us both!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac0ea8",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "VALENTINA: We're [i]not[/i] mages! [h=\"That was close...\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:071ec4f",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "Was I wrong about Valerie being a mage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01599a2",
  "node": "ValObj_1",
  "text": "No...[p/] That couldn’t be right."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fb249",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...?! [h=\"How did he|figure it out?!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2fb0c",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "Her thoughts said, “How did he figure it out?!”.[p/] That meant that I [i]was[/i] on the right track."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d04f8",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "Valerie [i]had[/i] to be the mage I was looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:056e1a5",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Celeste.[p/] Is it possible for a mage to hold a [b]Spell Compendium[/b] and avoid attuning to it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01457a5",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: No...[p/] It just needs to be on their person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9ddbc",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...When I was arrested,[p/] the Inquisition also made me attune to one of their [b]Spell Compendiums[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0170b04",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: They were really careful to make sure that I did the attunement correctly."
}

{
  "id": "line:093518b",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s no way a mage could avoid it with them watching you."
}

{
  "id": "line:008dc31",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "Right...[p/] Commander White may have been negligent sometimes,[p/] but even [i]he[/i] wasn’t that careless."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dbd1a",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Now,[p/] if you’re done,[p/] I do believe that you’ve exhausted all your options."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6db2c",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/][s/]wait![p/][s/] I’m still not done cross-examining this witness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:014adf3",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What could you possibly hope to glean from her testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000041d",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "Valentina was stressed out enough to see her thoughts."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c4fe2",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "...But I couldn't exactly say that I was planning to read her mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7f510",
  "node": "ValObj_2",
  "text": "And at this point,[p/] I felt that I was already testing the judge's patience."
}

{
  "id": "line:0045190",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: T-[p/][s/]There’s one key element of her testimony that the court is overlooking!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e6808",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: I have a right as an attorney to complete my cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e9eb",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor.[p/] The defense is clearly trying to buy time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b6b4a",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: ...I might be compelled to agree with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a449",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: However,[p/] I'll also admit that [i]some[/i] elements of the witness’s testimony are quite peculiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:094f6eb",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: I will allow the defense to continue their cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0840328",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "That was close."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b248b4",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: ...But know that this is your last chance, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcce77",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: If you produce nothing substantial with your questioning,[p/] I [i]will[/i] pass my verdict."
}

{
  "id": "line:07de88d",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: O-[p/]Of course, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c19e",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "Alright...[p/] It was all or nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:039422b",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "If I couldn't find anything by reading her mind,[p/] this whole case was finished."
}

{
  "id": "line:0108e5d",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Witness.[p/] Please give your testimony, once more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6898",
  "node": "ValObj_3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: U-[p/]Um... [p/]Okay... [h=\"How long does he plan|to keep me up here?!\" e=\"fa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf223",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Valentina: Like I said,[p/] my sister and I saw Ms. Bellwether bleeding on the ground.[p/] We rushed over to her. [h=\"I was definitely surprised|when I saw her like that.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a6ccb",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Valentina: N-[p/][s/]Now that you mention it...[p/] I don’t know if I saw any wounds on her.[p/] But I definitely saw blood! [h=\"I can’t go back on that now...|I just need to play dumb.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0229072",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Valentina: My sister tried to save her![p/][s/] But she didn’t use any magic! [h=\"Ugh, Valerie...|You’re too kind-hearted...\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0006008",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Valentina: We're not mages![p/][s/] Both of us held that book the knights gave us! [h=\"I was caught off guard when they asked us.|They almost found us out.\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0091251",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Valentina: The commander was watching us the whole time![p/][s/] He can confirm it! [h=\"It’s a good thing that we’re twins...|Or else that trick wouldn’t have worked.\" e=\"hf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f829",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "CELESTE: What are we going to do...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cabd15",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "CELESTE: They have pretty hard proof that Valerie isn’t a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:083a72e",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "TYRION: Valerie [i]is[/i] the mage we’re looking for.[p/] I’m sure of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0219e96",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm just not sure why they felt the need to lie to the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d1127",
  "node": "Val2Test",
  "text": "And more importantly,[p/] [i]how[/i] did they trick the Inquisition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09334a9",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "That matched the details of her previous testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f87d5c",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "There was nothing suspicious there,[p/] but I had no reason to doubt this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0387bf0",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It sounds like you're just backtracking on your previous testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:088902f",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: I-[p/][s/]I'm not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ade43",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: I guess I just assumed she was wounded because of all the blood!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3d01a",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: How was [i]I[/i] supposed to know she didn't have any wounds?![p/][s/] There was so much blood!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69031",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Her thoughts implied that she was lying,[p/] but her logic was sound."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365aa1",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "I should look at the thoughts that appeared during her other statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:0530fcc",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Valerie wasn't the one who closed her wounds,[p/] how did she try to \"help\" her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c0264",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: I-[p/]I don't know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2e58",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: She might have been looking for an open wound to apply first aid to."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0dff",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if we assume that you're telling the truth,[p/] there wouldn't be any wounds to find."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0420",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client would have already closed them to confound the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c901cf",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm telling you![p/][s/] I don't know!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a498f0",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "She's pleading ignorance of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bf52f",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "They \"almost\" found them out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4965",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can I assume that this \"book\" was an unattuned [b]Spell Compendium[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a0f5f",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes.[p/] The Inquisition has several of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84dd3",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: It's standard procedure to have witnesses attune to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f5482",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But doesn't the kingdom require that mages register?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03be908",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why don't you just cross-reference those records with the witnesses’ names?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a4127",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: For whatever reason,[p/] many mages among the commonfolk avoid registering with the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b84674",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: As a result,[p/] many of them choose to hide their abilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa414",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:035fce6",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "It was a \"good thing that they're twins\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039947b",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did you pull some kind of trick to [i]deceive[/i] the Inquisition while attuning, Ms. Ianus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac0da",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: O-[p/]Of course not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0376044",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: W-[p/][s/]We know that lying to the Inquisition would get us in trouble!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008d8c3",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: Why would [i]either[/i] of us take a risk like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0747c3b",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Living as an unregistered mage is a serious crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0606fa0",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Valerie [i]was[/i] a mage,[p/] then you would have been charged with fraud right then and there."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c798f",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Valentina: Y-[p/]Yeah![p/][s/] But we already proved that we're not mages!"
}

{
  "id": "line:025b609",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "The Eye seems to differ,[p/] but I'd need something else to convince the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0543e47",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "I needed to think through this.[p/] This wasn’t like a normal cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0530a49",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Nearly all of her thoughts were suspicious and contrary to her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:025f184",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "What I needed to do was find the thought that gave me a thread to pull on."
}

{
  "id": "line:072b1f9",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "In this case,[p/] I would need to find the thought that implied how the twins tricked the commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da33bc",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Once I found that,[p/] I could INTERPRET it without the need for evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:067e256",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The witness's testimony contradicts what she truly thinks!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6a67",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] that just sounds like speculation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8621a",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ll have to trust me, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845208",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have an instinct for this sort of thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0e30",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Your “instincts” do not make for concrete evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8f65a",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "AriaC: I can't believe I have to explain this to you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0262424",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c1e00",
  "node": "Cross_Val2",
  "text": "I couldn't exactly say that I could see her thoughts..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5a966",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus.[p/] Your thoughts betray you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fc7c2",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccdfae",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "I found the thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae6d5",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "They must have done something to trick Orym,[p/] but what...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09928da",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "It must have happened when he was interrogating them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0226416",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "ARIA: Orym collected their statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e3ac9",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: How are they holding up?[p/] I imagine they'd be rattled after discovering a body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d049bb",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "ARIA: From what he said,[p/] they were extremely tense,[p/] but I suppose that's to be expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b3a2e",
  "node": "Val2Obj",
  "text": "ARIA: He told me that they couldn't sit still.[p/] He found it difficult to take their statements because of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0809288",
  "node": "Val2Obj_1",
  "text": "They couldn't sit still...[p/] That implied they were moving somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:090934b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_1",
  "text": "She also thought it was a good thing that they were twins..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcc626",
  "node": "Val2Obj_1",
  "text": "This means that their so-called “trick” wouldn’t have worked otherwise..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01baf88",
  "node": "Val2Obj_2",
  "text": "Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:03329a0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_2",
  "text": "No...[p/] There had to be a way that the twins tricked Commander White."
}

{
  "id": "line:005b21c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_2",
  "text": "Steelwind said that the two of them \"couldn't sit still\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9e5f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_2",
  "text": "Were they really just antsy,[p/] or were they tricking the commander somehow?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0818a91",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "Of course![p/][s/] They switched places!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34bc6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "Valentina attuned to the first [b]Spell Compendium[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02acc2d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "Then she pretended to be Valerie to attune to the second one!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e34ae6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "They even wear the same uniform.[p/] No wonder Commander White couldn’t tell the difference between them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8eae6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus.[p/] There’s something I want to confirm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e757e0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: During the investigation,[p/] both you and Valerie attuned to a [b]Spell Compendium[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75d66",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah.[p/][s/] That knight [i]watched[/i] us do it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1a17",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: And how did he have you do this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d34a1e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you both attune to those [b]Compendiums[/b] at the same time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d406b1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Or did you attune one after another?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bd6bf",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fe45a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: I fail to see how that makes any difference, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b520c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: Yes.[p/] I agree."
}

{
  "id": "line:0782f61",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: The [b]Spell Compendiums[/b] would work regardless of what order they went in."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d068c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: You may not be aware of this, Your Honor,[p/] but Valentina and Valerie Ianus are identical twins."
}

{
  "id": "line:0137056",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which [i]means[/i] that their physical appearances are nearly identical to each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea2d9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: They also work in the same kitchen,[p/] which means that they must have been wearing the same uniform during questioning."
}

{
  "id": "line:061b6de",
  "node": "Val2Obj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: If Commander White didn’t have them attune at the same time,[p/][s/] what would stop the twins from switching places with each other?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e91100",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: This is clearly nothing but baseless conjecture."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79c8c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Orym wouldn’t fail at such a basic task."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c588ca",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Really, Prosecutor Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00350b5",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you find it hard to believe that [i]Commander White[/i] would fail at a task like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b91fa",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Even so,[p/] the gift of magic is inherited through bloodlines."
}

{
  "id": "line:083f48c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: For a pair of genetically identical twins,[p/] it would be impossible for one twin to be a mage while the other is not."
}

{
  "id": "line:027d01a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Has that been proven, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a55efc",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because as far as I'm concerned,[p/] [i]that[/i] is baseless conjecture!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e21eae",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]Wait a minute![p/][s/] This is crazy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6d95",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: We [i]didn’t[/i] trick the Inquisition!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f46d0a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I keep telling you![p/][s/] My sister and I aren't mages!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c32ce",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Then prove it, Ms. Ianus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b40c7",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Bring in your sister,[p/] and we’ll have you attune to [i]two[/i] [b]Spell Compendiums[/b] at the same time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2affd",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068b3a9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: Order in the court!"
}

{
  "id": "line:069839e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: It’s clear that we won’t get anywhere unless we test the defense’s theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:045aa93",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: Bailiff![p/][s/] Escort Valerie Ianus to the stand,[p/] and bring two unattuned [b]Spell Compendiums[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb57f7",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "VALERIE: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068d31a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "CELESTE: They’ve both had their hands on those Compendiums for the last ten minutes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcbe7f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s no way they can fake it in front of this many people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0386fe1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "Alright...[p/] It was the moment of truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e58248",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "I could only hope that my theory was correct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5debb",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: No...![p/][s/] Did he seriously—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e5d64",
  "node": "Val2Obj_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: W-[p/][s/] What is it, Prosecutor Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c06560",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: What I [i]see[/i] is the commander seeking new employment in the near future..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afe822",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] It appears that the defense was correct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0086327",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Valentina Ianus isn’t a mage,[p/] but Valerie Ianus is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0438cbe",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: What’s more,[p/] Valerie Ianus’s [b]Compendium[/b] contains the [b]Mend Wounds[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e955d0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Which makes the defense’s theory entirely plausible."
}

{
  "id": "line:038fa7f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: P-[p/][s/]Please...[p/][s/] Just allow me to explain..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f8a9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: We should allow you to explain [i]what[/i] exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a189f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: You're an unregistered mage,[p/] and you and your sister have made a mess of the investigation and this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0561594",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: How would you know what it’s like, [i]Lady[/i] Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e39dc",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ff9d2",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: Do you think we don't know who you are?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3a32",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: You’re not like us.[p/] You don’t [i]have[/i] to hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d11acc",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: But it's okay...[p/] This whole situation has gotten out of hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:041f8e4",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: I didn’t think hiding it would cause so much trouble,[p/] and I won’t let someone go to prison because of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0053eb8",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Even if he [i]is[/i] a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:040ac81",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: ...Please let me testify about what I saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dedd13",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: I’ll tell all of you what really happened that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d3e3",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "JUDGE: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a095f8",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] I believe we may all benefit from hearing Ms. Ianus's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d345c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "JUDGE: Very well,[p/] but understand that there will be repercussions for your actions, witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0129e62",
  "node": "Val2Obj_5",
  "text": "VALERIE: I know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eabc2",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "Valerie: My sister and I were walking in the hallway from the kitchen to the west exit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075bf8",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "Valerie: That's when I suddenly spotted the professor lying in a pool of blood in a nearby classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:018185e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "Valerie: Valentina used a communication device to call for help while I tried to save her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5cfbf",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "Valerie: I saw that she was bleeding,[p/] so I cast [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on her to close her wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:084f85e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "Valerie: But it was too late.[p/] I closed the hole in her chest,[p/] but she was already dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0a11f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "JUDGE: ...There was a hole in her chest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c21a44",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "TYRION: Your Honor.[p/] As you can clearly see from the witness’ testimony,[p/] the trace of [b]necromancy[/b] was left by the witness,[p/] not my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:048bc0b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "TYRION: What’s more,[p/] it’s clear that there was a [i]physical[/i] wound on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d71f9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "JUDGE: I-[p/][s/]I see...[p/] Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f48f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "His words trailed off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0592df0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "He clearly didn’t want to pass a verdict with no clear culprit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38f2b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "But he had no choice.[p/] The case against Wallace was predicated on Bellwether being killed by [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e7f7",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "With Valerie’s testimony,[p/] the prosecution didn't have a shred of evidence implicating him."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e91ef",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "JUDGE: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Very well.[p/] The court sees no reason to prolong this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f417c5",
  "node": "Val2Obj_6",
  "text": "JUDGE: With these new developments,[p/] the court has no choice but to find Wallace Nightgrave—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb728b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: I believe the court is ignoring one key detail of the witness’s testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0923a24",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "TYRION: ...And what would that be, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0512827",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: Let’s re-examine the witness’s testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5b0c1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: The communication device that Valentina Ianus used logs the time of day during each use."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c1dc5",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: From this log,[p/] we know that Valentina used this device at 3:04 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0097cc1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: This was an hour after the time of death."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ba3b3",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "TYRION: Where are you going with this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f676fc",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] There was a witness who saw the victim before the body was found:[p/] Jan Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0438f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_7",
  "text": "AriaC: He,[p/] along with another witness,[p/] spotted Bellwether walking in the hallways before the body was found."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c203d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "JAN: I was cleaning the halls."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e701a7",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "JAN: Bellwether knocked over a vase...[p/] There were shards and dirt everywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c68980",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "TYRION: Wait...[p/] You [s/][i]saw[/i] the professor before the twins arrived?"
}

{
  "id": "line:051ce11",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "JAN: Yeah.[p/] Like I said,[p/] she broke the vase right in this hallway..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0533104",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "JAN: It was probably 20-30 minutes before the twins found the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d49c0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: “20-30 minutes” before the body was found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9b765",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: Do you see the discrepancy, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13d71",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "Wait...[p/][s/] That couldn't be right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0432abf",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "Bellwether died more than an [i]hour[/i] before the body was found..."
}

{
  "id": "line:035004b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "So how did Jan see her half an hour [i]after[/i] her death?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0997780",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: I wonder, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bfb4b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: How could one make a dead body move and walk around?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d5988",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "TYRION: No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:040c7e2",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: We didn't just arrest the defendant based on those traces of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0542",
  "node": "Val2Obj_8",
  "text": "AriaC: We arrested him because only [i]one[/i] person in that school could have animated her corpse!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0860c42",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "Gallery: An undead?![p/][s/] Created [i]within[/i] the Imperial Academy?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc72d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "Gallery: How reprehensible!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05932d5",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s ridiculous![p/][s/] She had a hole in her chest when the twins found her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4fd10",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "TYRION: Jan Hughes would have noticed that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066acc9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "AriaC: [b]Animate Corpse[/b] stops the flow of blood.[p/] So she wouldn’t have tracked blood anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c94bb",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant is also proficient with [b]illusion[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0236a88",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "AriaC: He could have easily used an [b]illusion[/b] spell to hide the undead Bellwether’s wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f599be",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "TYRION: But another party could have easily used [b]illusion[/b] magic to disguise themselves as the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f6dd1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "AriaC: If that were true,[p/] how did they move the body to the classroom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000004d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0236200",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: Ms. Steelwind.[p/] If your theory is true,[p/] it would mean that the murder occurred elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:061ab36",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: Would the Inquisition happen to know where?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbfa99",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Regrettably,[p/] we do not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec52fe",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then the prosecution's case against my client is still faulty!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07954ab",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't convict my client without more evidence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2a22",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: I must agree with Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1d6b4",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: With these new developments,[p/] the court sees it fit to suspend the trial for the time being."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9bce",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: We will give the Inquisition time to investigate these unknowns."
}

{
  "id": "line:0567052",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court proceedings for this case will resume tomorrow morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee6b0e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_9",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is adjourned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075fde",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hey...[p/] Are you feeling okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0705e27",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "A body was seen moving around an hour after death..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da9e37",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "It clearly wasn't Bellwether..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3446f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "Or at the very least,[p/] she wasn't alive when Jan ran into her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626129",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "So, what was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022da53",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07847cb",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": ":Steelwind was right about one thing:[p/] there was [b]illusion[/b] magic involved..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d39d9",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "But which spell was it?[p/] Could it have been [b]Illusory Disguise[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7b0a6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89f22",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "TYRION: Ah...![p/] What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:005448b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: You’ve been pacing around the lobby since the trial ended."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa81df",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry...[p/] I was just thinking about Steelwind's theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baab7e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: It’s a little creepy when you think about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0961182",
  "node": "Val2Obj_10",
  "text": "CELESTE: Do you really think someone turned the professor into an undead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06db593",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: I don’t think so.[p/] The prosecution’s case is hinged on one key point:[p/] that Wallace was the only high-level necromancer nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b270de",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: We have to assume that he’s the only person capable of using that type of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:05179ec",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: But then how was she walking around...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07996c6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: I don’t know...[p/] It doesn’t make any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef8b81",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s a given that Wallace didn’t animate the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3971e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter what they did,[p/] someone had to have used an [b]illusion[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0efc2",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: Aren’t there spells that can create freestanding illusions?[p/] Not just disguises?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0026040",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: I honestly don’t know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9715",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: We’d need to talk to someone who knows about that type of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d4972",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: Didn’t Eris say that she was studying [b]illusion[/b] magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65565",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: She might be able to give us a lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da858f",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Is that really a good idea?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d542d8",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056d7c1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: What if [i]she’s[/i] the one who created the illusion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbaba0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df4d5d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "I was detecting fear from her again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba2496",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "TYRION: Celeste,[p/] are you [i]afraid[/i] of Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000bdba",
  "node": "Val2Obj_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] N-[p/][s/]No...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5790",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "TYRION: I saw it this morning, too.[p/] You always get really anxious whenever she’s around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9a34",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: O-[p/][s/]Oh.[p/] I didn't mean to be so obvious about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07eac63",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b6905",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Sorry,[p/] it’s not based on anything real,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e949e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] How do I explain this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001b8a0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: You already know that I was working as a mercenary before this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0044ba0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: When you do that kind of work,[p/] you build up an instinct to sense danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:029ba67",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: You kind of [i]have[/i] to if you want to stay alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab22bd",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "TYRION: Sorry...[p/] I never knew."
}

{
  "id": "line:0985fe4",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion.[p/] I’ve fought literal monsters and barely escaped with my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:097bd2a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: But when I’m near Eris,[p/] none of those creatures come even close."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ffacb",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: I get this feeling.[p/] It's like I’m in front of a predator that I couldn’t ever hope to beat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fabbc1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Every instinct I have tells me to run whenever she’s close by."
}

{
  "id": "line:078e020",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "TYRION: Really...?[p/] But she doesn’t seem that dangerous—[p/]just a little mischievous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6ffb8",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: I-[p/]I know...[p/] I think maybe I’m just anxious or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:065e916",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: [i]I[/i] should know better than anyone not to judge people by how they look."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9d6a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6e3cc",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: S-[p/]Sorry,[p/] forget I said anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:068b036",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: If you think we should talk to her,[p/] then we should do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0683fed",
  "node": "Val2Obj_12",
  "text": "Celeste’s instincts had never steered me wrong before."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d104d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "She had always been reliable,[p/] and if Eris was making [i]her[/i] feel this way,[p/] that must've meant something."
}

{
  "id": "line:092d933",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "But that’s all the more reason for us to talk to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7b4c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "TYRION: But aside from that,[p/] there was also something else that the prosecutor said."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d54c4",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "TYRION: There was another witness who saw Bellwether walking around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccef0a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right...[p/] Jan probably isn’t the most reliable witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:087db99",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was probably only half-awake when he saw her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d977b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...But do you think Steelwind will tell us who that witness was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0217009",
  "node": "Val2Obj_13",
  "text": "TYRION: We still have that deal with her.[p/] We won’t lose anything by asking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18e39",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] that's still bothering me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d86348",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7a8b",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Why was she so interested in who my biological parents are? [h=\"It's none of|her business...\" e=\"sa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00486d1",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "That [i]was[/i] strange...[p/] She traded information about the investigation for it too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be114a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe she thinks you're her long-lost sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:017651e",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] I never even thought of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0424c8d",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:033dc40",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Wouldn't that mean I'm the daughter of Lucio Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc14c",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: I think my dad would've thrown a fit if he ever heard that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754b26",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]are[/i] pretty good at fighting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5d119",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] That actually makes a lot of sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0187461",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: I guess I like Aria,[p/] and I've always wished I had a sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0388fdd",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: ...But I don't want to think about this now."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aa315",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe you can ask her when you're at that brunch you strongarmed her into."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa9c4a",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh,[p/] I almost forgot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28db0",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe I'm going to meet Altheris Duskweaver!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d7544",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] we still had a long investigation ahead of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:03385d6",
  "node": "Val2Obj_14",
  "text": "And we'd need to start by talking to Steelwind about that witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f59c1",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Val,[p/] you're back!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d83a56",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Where's the produce for tonight's dinner?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c7d3",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: The grocers all said someone already collected the deliveries."
}

{
  "id": "line:0769d27",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: Do you think someone stole them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ad6d",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: I bet word about the trial has gotten out already."
}

{
  "id": "line:0577e5d",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: They're definitely not going to sell to us anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df1ee8",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:079acc5",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Ugh...[p/] That dumb attorney just had to go and ruin everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5a1f4",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: I don't know...[p/] I was watching the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0413fd9",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: Do you really think that boy killed Catherine?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034c996",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Of course, he did![p/][s/] He's a [i]necromancer[/i] for crying out loud!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7006",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: If what they said was true,[p/] I'm one, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc22ec",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: You know that's not the same thing.[p/] You only use healing magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6d1ab",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Come on,[p/] help me prep some of the leftover meat.[p/] I bet we can still make some soup out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:091803f",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: I hate this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f634f0",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Yeah,[p/] I know.[p/] The students are totally going to complain about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8b5d2",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: No,[p/] I [i]hate[/i] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e83f8",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valentina: Sure.[p/] Whatever, Val..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c50dc",
  "node": "StartInves1",
  "text": "Valerie: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093078c",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Court is now resumed for the trial of Wallace Nightgrave."
}

{
  "id": "line:018eee9",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: During yesterday's trial,[p/] it was revealed that the trace of [b]necromancy[/b] might not have been left by the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f4c7",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: It may have been left by a witness who cast [b]necromancy[/b] in an attempt to [i]heal[/i] the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0573f33",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: However,[p/] the victim was seen by witnesses well after her time of death."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a64d2",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: That could only be explained if someone had used [b]necromancy[/b] to animate the victim’s body,[p/] which begged the following question."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4eb6e",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: [i]If[/i] the victim had been raised as an undead and ordered to walk to Lecture Hall 2-B,[p/] where did the murder actually take place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5c88",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Does the prosecution have an answer for this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b2ac7",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "AriaC: Based on the testimonies of several witnesses,[p/] it is very likely that the murder took place in the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ac713",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Interesting...[p/] What led you to this conclusion, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f79c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "AriaC: First,[p/] I’d like to remind the court [i]where[/i] the victim was sighted before the body was found."
}

{
  "id": "line:05455c3",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "AriaC: It began when the victim had a meeting with the headmaster near the center of the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de3dba",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Theodore: Our meeting was scheduled for 12:00 PM.[p/] According to my schedule for that day,[p/] our meeting lasted for an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:04935b3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: This brings us to the statement of the next witness:[p/] a student at the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acc665",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: This student saw the victim walking in the hallways."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c621",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Miriam: I saw her coming out of the headmaster’s office."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c95e3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Miriam: She was heading towards the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:020d964",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Which means that our first witness saw Bellwether leave the headmaster’s office."
}

{
  "id": "line:068abf0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: Presumably,[p/] this would have happened [i]after[/i] her meeting there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0def261",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]That[/i] would time this encounter at around 1:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:09db858",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The other event is the discovery of the body,[p/] which was when Valentina Ianus contacted security."
}

{
  "id": "line:05caa99",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Valerie: I suddenly spotted the professor lying in a pool of blood in the classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:01af7b6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: As we’ve already established,[p/] this event occurred at 3:04 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8db20",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: But the significance of this time is in what occurred [i]before[/i] the body was discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9ae2d",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "AriaC: The second witness,[p/] a member of the cleaning staff,[p/] spotted the victim in the west-wing hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ec1ad",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Jan: Bellwether knocked over a vase...[p/] And there were shards and dirt everywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:041be32",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Jan: It was probably 20-30 minutes before the twins found the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab4933",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: This means that this encounter must have happened no later than 2:30 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0191c0a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: And [i]this[/i] implies that the victim was near the library between 1:00 PM and 2:30 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac58c0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: According to the defendant’s statements,[p/] he was in the Library during this time period."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4bf71",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Furthermore,[p/] the time of death was at 2:01 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a9768",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: This means that Mr. Hughes saw the victim’s animated body."
}

{
  "id": "line:020d5c9",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: I see.[p/] What do you have to say in your defense, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09be979",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "TYRION: The prosecution’s argument is definitely well thought-out, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c046",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "TYRION: ...However,[p/] it is entirely predicated on the testimonies of all the witnesses involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eefe1",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Steelwind’s deduction had to have a hole somewhere..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c6e3a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "And since our conversation yesterday,[p/] I’d had a feeling that Miriam was hiding something..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd198b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "If I wanted to get to the truth,[p/] I would need to drag that out of her through a cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3379",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Your Honor.[p/] To test the validity of these claims,[p/] the defense would like both of these witnesses to testify."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df503d",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The defense calls Miriam Frega to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a772c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: F-[p/][s/]Frega?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a678c5",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "At the mention of her name,[p/] the judge’s face turned a bit pale."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c54fcf",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "He fidgeted with his gavel,[p/] looking towards the bailiff and then towards Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0281a43",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I had a feeling it would come to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fde531",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: D-[p/][s/]Do you have any objections, Ms. Steelwind...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0407d00",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "AriaC: I do not, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a0b45",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d93c0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Judge: Bailiff.[p/] Please escort...[p/] [i]Lady[/i] Frega to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4ea5c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55b8c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: You little snakes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05009e1",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: How [i]dare[/i] you deceive me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:009fc0c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] It looks like she found out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0cb9f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "AriaC: I had the opportunity to debrief the witness beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfa643",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Ms. McCoy,[p/] I asked you to exercise discretion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a06b26",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "AriaC: I did not imply that you should impersonate a member of my family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdf733",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Y-[p/]Yeah...[p/] Sorry about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa19a6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I gave you [i]all[/i] of the tea that I imported from the Eastern Kingdoms!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d9105",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I demand that you return it to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eba324",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: No![p/][s/] You gave them to me![p/][s/] They’re [i]legally[/i] mine now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a32d3c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Anyways, Miriam,[p/] could you please testify to the court about your encounter with the victim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef1354",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...Fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0820ebc",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Miriam: I was working on a research project in my dorm room when I decided to take a break."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee6e53",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Miriam: I left my room and went on a walk.[p/] That’s when I saw Professor Bellwether exiting the Headmaster’s Office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caba54",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Miriam: She was walking in my direction.[p/] So I greeted her,[p/] and she responded in kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:009be5a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Miriam: After that,[p/] she headed towards the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd67f0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Miriam: A short time after that,[p/] I went back to my room and continued my work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad4c39",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: I see...[p/] So it was only a brief encounter."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b061f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "AriaC: However brief it was,[p/] the witness’s testimony verifies two things."
}

{
  "id": "line:00417e3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "AriaC: One is that Miriam saw the professor exiting the Headmaster’s Office."
}

{
  "id": "line:03da601",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "AriaC: The other is that she witnessed the victim head toward the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0946b2a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "AriaC: This gives us a rough timeline of where the victim was before her death."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9265",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: Hm...[p/] That [i]does[/i] seem consistent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4bee7",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Did Bellwether really enter the library after her meeting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be681b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "I felt like I would've seen her there if she did."
}

{
  "id": "line:012336c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] You may begin your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:055a7e6",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: Was this research project a part of your schoolwork?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0c0dd",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It was an independent study to develop a new [b]conjuration[/b] spell formula."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebc8fb",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: The project is being sponsored by the Crown Prince himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b2ec",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I wasn’t aware that he was involved in such a study."
}

{
  "id": "line:04db573",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Of course you wouldn't.[p/] Did you expect to know every aspect of his life, dear Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02431ae",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "...I sensed some hostility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6fd34",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: If you don’t keep an eye on him,[p/] House Frega might just steal him back from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:054b58f",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: Hmph...[p/] As if His Highness would align himself with your rapacious family again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0409b5b",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0700a2a",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Ha![p/] Our banking houses form the economic infrastructure of our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4336",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: But perhaps he’ll come to the Steelwinds if he needs to massacre a village of commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c15520",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "JUDGE: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/][s/] With all due respect,[p/] may we please focus on the matter at hand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fb709",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Of course, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:01edd34",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: And you’re sure that you saw her exit the Headmaster’s Office?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f17666",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes.[p/] I remember it clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:057063d",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "Miriam: I was surprised that she was still meeting with the headmaster at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03ce8",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "She must've been referring to her family's plot to replace him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c86870",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: Did you interact with the professor at all, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b80a72",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "Miriam: She was walking in my direction.[p/] So I greeted her, and she responded in kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa957a",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: Did anything seem off about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e5be8",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...No,[p/] but it was a very short encounter."
}

{
  "id": "line:09330c7",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It’s not as if we stopped to have a conversation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff0526",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: You said that you greeted her,[p/] and she responded."
}

{
  "id": "line:0597bdc",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did she say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7445b",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: W-[p/]Why is that important? [h=\"It's not important at all.|So why?\" e=\"af\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:040f062",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega,[p/] it’s possible that someone used [b]illusion[/b] magic that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4777c",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]Every[/i] detail about the victim’s interactions could be important."
}

{
  "id": "line:0253d24",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Well...[p/] I bid her good morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26383",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: She said,[p/] “Good morning” in response."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd72d6",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "Miriam: She was walking towards me.[p/] So I bid her good morning, and she responded in kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0544785",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: And you’re certain that nothing seemed off about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84f4d",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Y-[p/][s/]Yes.[p/] Like I said,[p/] it was a very short encounter. [h=\"I don't understand...|Why did she say that...?\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:02958c9",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It only happened over a few seconds."
}

{
  "id": "line:081c809",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness’s interactions are not what’s important here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5e77",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: What matters is that she [i]witnessed[/i] where the victim was coming from and where she went afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ddd0e",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you [i]see[/i] her enter the library?"
}

{
  "id": "line:017711e",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...I didn’t,[p/] but there’s not much else in that direction."
}

{
  "id": "line:07604c4",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: From the testimony of Jan Hughes,[p/] we know that she later came from the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c922fe",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "AriaC: Even if she didn’t enter the library,[p/] she was still in that area for more than an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10903",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: How long did you leave your dorm room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:089b0ff",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Only for a few minutes.[p/] I try not to let my breaks go for too long."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a460d9",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: And you didn’t see the professor again after your first encounter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8cfc6",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "MIRIAM: No.[p/] I did not."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a1bfe",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "CELESTE: Her testimony seems pretty straightforward,[p/] but she could still be lying..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08db8aa",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m honestly not sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce2b33",
  "node": "Cross_Miriam",
  "text": "TYRION: We’ll just have to focus on her statements about how Bellwether acted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb13e5",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega.[p/] If I recall correctly,[p/] you have a habit of getting absorbed in your work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8adc5",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: So much so,[p/] that you’ll even lose track of the time of day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f43996",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "MIRIAM: If [i]I[/i] recall correctly,[p/] you pulled that information out of me through your lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ced52",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Regardless,[p/] earlier in today’s proceedings,[p/] the prosecutor made the following argument:"
}

{
  "id": "line:0960cd2",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Our first witness saw Bellwether leave the meeting with the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0903e13",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]That[/i] would time this encounter around 1:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5e37",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega.[p/] If you had said “Good morning” to the professor,[p/] you would have been mistaken..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07da6a7",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Because that encounter could have only happened during the afternoon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed05f",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "AriaC: And your point is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d0d9a",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "AriaC: You said it yourself, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] The witness simply lost track of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b767bc",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: What the witness said isn’t what’s important here."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7d71",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: The significance is in [i]what[/i] the professor said in response."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d152b",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: She had just come out of a meeting that was scheduled for noon and ran for an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:05417ef",
  "node": "MiriamObj",
  "text": "TYRION: She would be well aware that it was no longer morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab8bed",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Wouldn’t she have corrected the witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04edf06",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Their encounter was extremely short,[p/] and the victim’s mind may have been preoccupied."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a8b61",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: She could have easily responded to the witness without thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a09953",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’m going to be honest.[p/] I kind of agree with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:08490b6",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: It’s not hard to believe that they were both confused about the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05538e9",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "It was definitely a stretch,[p/] but I still couldn't shake the feeling that Miriam was hiding something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f31f7a",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "Every time I asked her about how Bellwether acted that day,[p/] the Eye of Horus read a suspicious thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a227c3",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "There [i]had[/i] to be something there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0755426",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega.[p/] You haven’t been entirely truthful in your testimony, have you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b51b03",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "MIRIAM: T-[p/][s/]That’s absurd![p/][s/] What reason would I have to lie?! [h=\"It’s such a small detail!|Why does he even care?!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de7494",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Every[/i] detail about how she acted is important, Ms. Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb626c",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What [i]aren't[/i] you telling us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5b7d",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] you have no basis to accuse the witness of perjury."
}

{
  "id": "line:097847a",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Y-[p/][s/]Yes![p/][s/] You will stop this at once!"
}

{
  "id": "line:024384f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega,[p/][s/] you're [i]lying[/i] about how Bellwether responded to your greeting, aren’t you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:083a7da",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I-[p/][s/]I... [h=\"It doesn’t make a difference...|All she did was yell at me...\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c02e56",
  "node": "MiriamObj_2",
  "text": "“All she did was yell”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3ce2",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega.[p/] Is it possible that Bellwether’s response was less than friendly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076f3d4",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: W-[p/][s/]What do you care?![p/][s/] What difference does it make?! [h=\"This peasant!|Why is he being so persistent?!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67c4e",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: My job is to make sure [i]every[/i] part of your testimony is truthful!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24a91",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]Every[/i] detail matters,[p/][s/] no matter how seemingly insignificant!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2cc8a",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "JUDGE: Mr. Cuthbert![p/] You [i]will[/i] stop this,[p/][s/] or I will find you in contempt!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad244b",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: The professor yelled at you,[p/] didn’t she, Ms. Frega?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0efbb",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yeah?![p/][s/] So what if she did?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081644c",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5c6b1",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: E-[p/][s/]Er...[p/] I mean..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adc4c7",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...I'm sorry,[p/] but we all clearly heard what you just said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfb71f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: So,[p/] you [i]do[/i] admit that she yelled at you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00238a3",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Agh![p/][s/] You impertinent little-!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca364",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes![p/][s/] I admit it![p/][s/] The professor [i]didn’t[/i] greet me back that day!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf91d",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh.[p/] Good morning, professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5255",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "CATHERINE: Be quiet!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d878ca",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:046040f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: She yelled at me to “Be quiet!”"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e22cbc",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: But until then,[p/] we had always been nothing but courteous with each other..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f4c2c",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I don’t know what got into her that day,[p/] but something had put her in a foul mood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3f9b",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: B-[p/][s/]But that’s it![p/][s/] Everything else I said was the truth! [h=\"I [i]am[/i] telling the truth!|That's all she did!\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f37fdb",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I [i]did[/i] see her come out of the Headmaster’s Office and walk towards the library! [h=\"She walked past me!|[i]That[/i] part was true!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d2c0b",
  "node": "MiriamObj_3",
  "text": "So, she [i]wasn’t[/i] lying about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:018ec22",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: So,[p/] is that all, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083599e",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: ...What do you mean, “is that all”?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f1e93",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: You badgered this witness,[p/] all so you could prove...[p/] [i]what[/i] exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e78be",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: The witness committed perjury—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caaa65",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness changed a [i]small[/i] detail of her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:065e296",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: A detail that is inconsequential to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:083d9bc",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: It was clearly an act with no malicious intent."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2885",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "After seeing her thoughts,[p/] it was difficult to disagree with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acdf44",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "I was so sure that the Eye would give me a thread to pull on,[p/] but she was only lying to save face."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a2ada",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness saw the victim leave the Headmaster’s Office and head toward the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4899d",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "AriaC: Do you have any concrete evidence to refute [i]that[/i], Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c698dc",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: ...N[p/][s/]-No...[p/] I guess not."
}

{
  "id": "line:071cd5d",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "CELESTE: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] Is this really okay?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8bf63",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "CELESTE: At this rate,[p/][s/] this will be the only chance you have to cross-examine her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1babb",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: I don’t think she’s lying anymore,[p/] and I was really pushing my luck earlier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0799ba5",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: If I continue pressing her,[p/] the judge might [i]actually[/i] charge me with contempt..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f3506",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "But if Miriam wasn’t the one who was lying,[p/] then..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77422",
  "node": "MiriamObj_4",
  "text": "TYRION: The defense has no further questions for the witness, Ms. Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fef20",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "The prosecutor stayed silent for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:058b0c2",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "...She almost looked disappointed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c821e5",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Very well.[p/] Miriam,[p/] you are dismissed."
}

{
  "id": "line:041223f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2e9a2",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "Miriam shot me a look of disdain,[p/] but she left the room without protest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b557bd",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "The judge let out a sigh as the young noble was escorted out of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4ec23",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "It was as if he were expecting the young noble to literally explode at any moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4683e",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Now with that out of the way...[p/] What else do you have, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076bb2c",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "The only way to refute the prosecution’s theory was to cast doubt on one of the witnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:019c7c8",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "If it wasn’t Miriam,[p/] then..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e500f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind.[p/] To test your theory,[p/] we must question every witness who saw the victim that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c95e6f",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "TYRION: So,[p/] with that said,[p/] the defense would like to call Jan Hughes to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f72eb",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I hope you understand, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e05b7",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: Your entire case rests on the assumption that one of the witness accounts is incorrect."
}

{
  "id": "line:06276fd",
  "node": "MiriamObj_5",
  "text": "AriaC: If your cross-examination of Mr. Hughes leads nowhere,[p/] then I hope you’re ready to concede."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe41a",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "I didn't like the sound of it,[p/] but she was right."
}

{
  "id": "line:029eb0a",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "Unless I could find...[p/][s/] [i]something[/i] in Jan’s testimony,[p/] I wouldn't have a case at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:07648c8",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "AriaC: Bailiff,[p/] please bring in Mr. Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:097101e",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc420",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "JAN: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:082ce42",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness![p/][s/] Name and occupation!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8c8b8",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "JAN: A-[p/][s/]Ah,[p/][s/] right."
}

{
  "id": "line:011dfee",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "JAN: My name is Jan Hughes.[p/] I’m on the cleaning staff of the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d436b1",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Mr. Hughes,[p/] please testify to the court about your encounter with the professor that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e96d59",
  "node": "MiriamObj_6",
  "text": "JAN: ...Alright."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd9170",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "Jan: I saw the professor when I was cleaning the west-wing hallways.[p/] It was about 20-30 minutes before the body was discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:065a3f5",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "Jan: She walked by me,[p/] but she looked pretty out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44ad5",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "Jan: I heard she was undead when this happened...[p/] Pretty creepy if you ask me."
}

{
  "id": "line:037b7af",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "Jan: After that,[p/] she went into the empty classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5b7e9",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "TYRION: Well...[p/] That was[p/] straightforward."
}

{
  "id": "line:094c3e3",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "CELESTE: Come on, Jan![p/][s/] What are we supposed to do with that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:078fd02",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "JAN: I don’t know.[p/] [i]You[/i] guys are the lawyers."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aa8dc",
  "node": "MiriamObj_7",
  "text": "JAN: I’m just telling you what I saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7c0c2",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: How are you so sure that it was 30 minutes before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0818b27",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: I always check the time to make sure I’m on schedule."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce81ff",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: I was supposed to finish cleaning the halls by 3:00 pm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b48234",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": ":Right...[p/] The body was discovered at 3:04 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6c046",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "AriaC: What was the \"professor\" like, Mr. Hughes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e030c9",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: She walked by me...[p/] But she looked pretty out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f36fad",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: Did anything else look off about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac1d4",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: Yeah, probably.[p/] She [i]was[/i] an undead after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a848cc",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: That remains to be proven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a86eee",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: If you say so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94c78",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: Anyways,[p/] what was her demeanor like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033b504",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: She looked like she was in a bad mood."
}

{
  "id": "line:01724a8",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: Either that or she was tired,[p/] but I guess she was actually just dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ee5ea",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: I heard she was undead. Which is pretty creepy because she pushed me out of her way."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d8917",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: I heard she was undead. Which is pretty creepy because she knocked over a vase."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad1f93",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "Jan: I heard she was undead. Which is pretty creepy because she yelled at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8eca1",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you see anyone else enter that classroom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04553a3",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: I’m honestly not sure.[p/] I wasn't paying much attention to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0685986",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: I [i]did[/i] think it was weird that she went in there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e109b4",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "JAN: With the funky smell,[p/] I can't think of any reason why someone would go there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbea64",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "CELESTE: He’s not giving us a lot to work with..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c75ab2",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: He tends to leave out details unless we directly ask him about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ec448",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: I just need to ask him the right questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f863a5",
  "node": "Cross_Jan",
  "text": "TYRION: Maybe we can pull more information out of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7090a",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: I believe you’ve forgotten a few details about what the professor did."
}

{
  "id": "line:015207d",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: Yeah...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0def924",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "Jan: Sorry,[p/] it’s hard to remember these things sometimes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe58f3",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "Did she do anything to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b690b",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: Did she interact with you at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1c694",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: Oh...[p/] yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d04fd7",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: I didn’t notice her at first and I accidentally got in her way."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f9357",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: She shoved me to the side and kept walking forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f5e95",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "Did she touch anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e06e4",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: Did she touch anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc7c2",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: She knocked over a vase and shattered it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02020e1",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: It [i]might[/i] have been an accident,[p/] but she’s done stuff like that on purpose before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9dc6c",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "Did she make any sounds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e7f4d",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you hear her make any sounds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bcfb5",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: Oh...[p/] Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:018d1c5",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: After she knocked over the vase,[p/] she yelled at me to [s/]“Be Quiet!”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382ed2",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: ...But I didn’t even say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7a450",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: This detail could be extremely important."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701e00",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "TYRION: Please add it to your testimony, Mr. Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:041bc3b",
  "node": "JanPress",
  "text": "JAN: Whatever you say, man..."
}

{
  "id": "line:031a90a",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Mr. Hughes.[p/] You said that Bellwether yelled at you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4fcf8",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: What were her exact words?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b70e",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: Uh...[p/] I think she yelled at me to “Be Quiet!”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0716a6a",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "AriaC: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002979a",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: I thought it was weird.[p/] I didn’t even say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed2781",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: But I know better than to talk back to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:087fbfe",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s the thing, Mr. Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7cd23",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution’s theory is as follows:[p/] the professor was murdered in the library and was reanimated using [b]Animate Corpse[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b46c30",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: With a quick [b]illusion[/b] spell,[p/] no one would notice that she was undead."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b1f4",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: However,[p/][s/] if what you saw was [i]truly[/i] the undead Bellwether..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ebca1",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: ...How did she speak to you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0580d81",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: Huh...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c48269",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "AriaC: This...[p/][s/] can't be right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cabf9",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Mr. Hughes,[p/] undead can follow simple orders,[p/] but they don’t have the intelligence to speak."
}

{
  "id": "line:002042a",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Perhaps the witness was mistaken!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08981fb",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] I’m sure I heard her yell at me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0208cf7",
  "node": "JanObj",
  "text": "JAN: I remembered because what she said didn’t make any sense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022200b",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Exactly![p/][s/] He didn’t say anything,[p/] but she still yelled at him to “Be quiet!”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb58ff",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "...Wait a minute."
}

{
  "id": "line:0388f2a",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: I’m...[p/] afraid I don’t understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:059594a",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: We’ve already established that the victim was dead long before her encounter with Mr. Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5f50d",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: But...[p/] if what he saw wasn’t an undead,[p/][s/] what was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a52a2",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: It [i]had[/i] to be an undead!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0777293",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: What other explanation is there?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0abc983",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "It couldn’t have been a [b]Major Illusion[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7e45",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "Otherwise,[p/] it wouldn’t have been able to shove Jan out of the way or knock over the vase."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f044fa",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "Whatever it was,[p/] someone probably used an [b]Illusory Disguise[/b] to make it look like Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c93ef",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "Does that mean it [i]was[/i] a person?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02631b7",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "No...[p/] If it were a person,[p/] how did Bellwether’s body end up in the lecture hall?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02be10d",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "Bellwether wouldn’t have been able to turn herself invisible if she were dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1e7da",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "And whatever Jan saw,[p/] it needed to be something that could have transported Bellwether’s body unseen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0436c",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "It would have also needed to have a mass [i]and[/i] the ability to speak."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c30dd3",
  "node": "JanObj_2",
  "text": "Or at the very least,[p/] it needs to be something that can recreate Bellwether’s voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c56000",
  "node": "ConstPres",
  "text": "What could have done that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0302384",
  "node": "ConstPres",
  "text": "Construct"
}

{
  "id": "line:08cee88",
  "node": "ConstPres",
  "text": "No...[p/] That wasn't right."
}

{
  "id": "line:058d171",
  "node": "ConstPres",
  "text": "I remembered there was [i]something[/i] that could have recreated Bellwether's voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:04853d9",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7c633",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: What...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0daf265",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: Everyone,[p/] the witness didn’t actually [i]hear[/i] the dead victim speaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e754ef",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: What he [i]actually[/i] heard was Bellwether's voice being recreated using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ada7f",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: Are you trying to say that her voice was recreated using a spell...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3ba41",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: Not a spell, Steelwind.[p/] It was artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b9e77",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: And whoever the murderer is,[p/] they had the perfect piece of artificery available to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d3073",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: One programmed with Catherine Bellwether’s voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24dba",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "AriaC: You can’t possibly mean—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f844ce",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s right, Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0160ec6",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: What Mr. Hughes saw was an Arcane Construct!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc4b50",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: An “Arcane Construct”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0378ed6",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: It is a magically animated suit of armor, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e862f1",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: But we ruled out such a possibility, hadn’t we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bb3fc",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: Construct or not,[p/] no one could disguise themselves [i]and[/i] carry the body to the classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaaa56",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: A person wouldn’t have been able to do it,[p/] but Arcane Constructs are a different thing entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f447b",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Those suits of armor are extremely large,[p/] but more importantly,[p/][s/] they’re hollow!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d1170",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: That means that theoretically,[p/] someone could have placed the victim’s body inside it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:056ce17",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: The Arcane Construct wouldn’t [i]just[/i] transport the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfa93c",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: With an [b]Illusory Disguise[/b],[p/] it would also confuse and mislead anyone who saw it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3933",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: I commend your deduction, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I would have never considered that possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e3a79",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: It’s certainly plausible,[p/] but what does this prove exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ad0e7",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: It proves that the body wasn’t animated using [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd4c6",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: My client isn’t the murderer!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077ca14",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant is still capable of performing all of the acts that you described."
}

{
  "id": "line:0017496",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: His [b]Compendium[/b] contains [b]Illusory Disguise[/b] after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0774bf9",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: There were several students in the library that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e0a5",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]Any[/i] of them could have committed the murder!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13fe5",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: One [i]might[/i] come to that conclusion,[p/] if they didn’t have one crucial piece of evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0939e6e",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: I’d like to present a new piece of evidence to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94e9a",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "From under her table,[p/] Steelwind pulled out Miriam Frega's bloody rapier."
}

{
  "id": "line:016b9ed",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "JUDGE: A sword...?[p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]Is that...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03b50",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: Yes, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b19316",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]This[/i] is the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db02a8",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: This rapier was reported stolen by Miriam Frega weeks before the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:052fdb3",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: During the investigation,[p/] it was finally found in the [i]defendant’s[/i] locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c9813",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/][s/]Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0109eb8",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: He was clearly trying to use one of her possessions in a paltry attempt to frame her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0502b0b",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Why...[p/] he even stole her locker’s nameplate and placed it over his."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04dd2",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/][s/] That wasn't what really happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3c9d7",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "But honestly,[p/] it sounded more plausible than what [i]really[/i] took place..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa4635",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...We’re basically back to square one, aren’t we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dece8",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Anyone could have told that Construct to do all those things."
}

{
  "id": "line:015d246",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] Was that really true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a59c89",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "The Construct transported the professor’s body,[p/] and someone used an [b]illusion[/b] to make it look like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b496",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "They even used a pre-recorded voice to make the illusion more convincing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daaae1",
  "node": "ConstPresAfter_3",
  "text": "Could [i]anyone[/i] have done that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049ac03",
  "node": "RedPres",
  "text": "Theodore"
}

{
  "id": "line:068fd9a",
  "node": "RedPres",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Constructs will take orders from anyone,[p/] but not all of their functions are enabled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffdd18",
  "node": "RedPres",
  "text": "Who would have every function available to them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0020359",
  "node": "RedPresAfter",
  "text": "It was at that moment that several memories flooded back to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c8d00",
  "node": "RedPresAfter",
  "text": "JAN: Uh...[p/] I think she yelled at me to “Be quiet”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8407",
  "node": "RedPresAfter",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Until then,[p/] we had always been nothing but courteous with each other..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce05b9",
  "node": "RedPresAfter",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I don’t know what got into her that day,[p/] but something put her in a foul mood."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bf02c",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "Catherine: Be quiet!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a29e0",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "TYRION: S-[p/][s/]Sorry!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5e479",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "Catherine: BE QUIET!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9a7d",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "Eris giggled to herself.[p/] She was clearly amused by what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0410dd5",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "ERIS: The construct’s “voice” is an amalgam of pre-recorded phrases."
}

{
  "id": "line:064a660",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "ERIS: I’m not sure if you noticed,[p/] but it uses the voice of Professor Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cc02b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I knew there was something wrong with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e59163",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "ERIS: Unfortunately,[p/] you can’t make them say anything other than basic responses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0475385",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_1",
  "text": "ERIS: Only the headmaster can change those settings."
}

{
  "id": "line:036cfda",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: No...![p/][s/] Was it [i]him[/i] the entire time?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0b154",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: What is it, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057aca3",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Did you figure something out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052ac67",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] did."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c72b7",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "I didn't like where this was going,[p/] but with the way the pieces were laid out,[p/] there was only one explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:006a30b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind,[p/] earlier you said that my client could have orchestrated this entire ruse,[p/] but that’s simply not true."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5b6a",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: How so?[p/] Anyone could have ordered the Construct to carry the victim’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ed2b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Yes,[p/] but not everyone can [i]change[/i] what the Constructs are able to say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0f2fe",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Only one individual has the credentials for that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604d90",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Theodore Redmond:[p/] Headmaster of the Imperial Academy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:004fea0",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wait,[p/][s/] you’re not serious, are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7383c",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: You think the [i]headmaster[/i] did all this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf157e",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I...[p/] don’t want to believe it,[p/] but he’s the only person who [i]could[/i] have done it."
}

{
  "id": "line:026c9b4",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_2",
  "text": "AriaC: That’s completely ridiculous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9ff6",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Headmaster Redmond is 88 years old![p/][s/] He could [i]never[/i] do something like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c6777",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind,[p/] there’s one common element between each of the witnesses’ encounters with Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:038424a",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s what Bellwether said to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74b40",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: She yelled at both of them to “Be quiet!”..."
}

{
  "id": "line:011c417",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Miriam Frega was particularly surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9e7a",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: She had a good relationship with the professor,[p/] but when greeted by the professor,[p/] Bellwether just shouted at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650616",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Almost as if the professor was responding indiscriminately."
}

{
  "id": "line:08679ab",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: And recall her encounter with Jan Hughes."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e9259",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: The professor knocked over a vase and shouted at him to \"Be quiet!\" immediately after."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4ae8c",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: But he hadn’t said anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6012b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...She was responding to the sound of the vase breaking!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba6958",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Now,[p/] let me ask you this, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0292f59",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: Where did Bellwether come from [i]before[/i] she encountered Ms. Frega and Mr. Hughes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069385f",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Her meeting—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94688",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_3",
  "text": "TYRION: —With the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9121b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: It appears that the defense truly means to indict Theodore Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00b26",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "JUDGE: If so,[p/] we have no choice but to take a brief recess until he can be brought here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0616111",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "Theodore: There’s no need."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3db07",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: Fortunately for you,[p/] I was already in the gallery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8faae",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "The headmaster stood up from the gallery behind me and slowly made his way onto the witness stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dcc8b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "...Had he been here the entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0165133",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: Now,[p/] please correct me if I’m wrong, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0836a61",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: But are you trying to say that [i]I[/i] am the one who committed this crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb604e",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "TYRION: ...I’m sorry, Mr. Redmond,[p/] but no matter how I look at it,[p/] everything I’ve found points to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e59a6b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: No,[p/] there’s no need to apologize."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcafaa",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: In fact,[p/] I should commend you on the lengths that you’re going to defend dear Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9a02",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...The court appreciates your understanding, Mr. Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec6a5b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: ... [h=\"How can she speak so cordially?|After [i]all[/i] she's done!\" e=\"a\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78567",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_4",
  "text": "THEODORE: Now then...[p/] To clear the air,[p/] I suppose I should give [i]my[/i] testimony on what happened that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6cd7d",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "Theodore: That day,[p/] I had a meeting scheduled with the professor at noon."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cdaae",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "Theodore: She showed up at the expected time,[p/] and we discussed various administrative matters."
}

{
  "id": "line:033602b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "Theodore: Our meeting went on for an hour.[p/] After which, she left to prepare for her next class."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c84483",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "Theodore: Despite our many disagreements,[p/] we still knew how to be civil with one another."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e3306",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "Theodore: After all,[p/] I had no reason to bear a personal grudge against her."
}

{
  "id": "line:008cb8b",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "CELESTE: I...[p/] just can’t see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e50a",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "CELESTE: He seems like such a nice old man."
}

{
  "id": "line:08574ea",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "CELESTE: Is he [i]really[/i] the killer we’re looking for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3cd4c",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "TYRION: He has to be.[p/] No one else could have orchestrated this entire plot."
}

{
  "id": "line:007b50a",
  "node": "RedPresAfter_5",
  "text": "I just needed to find out how to prove it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0126698",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: What was this meeting for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d132f8",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: Oh,[p/] nothing of note."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f41a0e",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: We were merely discussing her daily operations and duties within the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7c42b",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: In an academy such as ours,[p/] it is beneficial to regularly communicate with the staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:064f211",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: So, she showed up at [i]exactly[/i] 12:00 PM?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cabdd1",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: More or less."
}

{
  "id": "line:047ba9e",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: Catherine Bellwether was many things,[p/] but she was never tardy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bec85",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "There weren’t any witnesses who saw her before the meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0172d16",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "So, I didn't have a way to disprove what he’s saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:06db46c",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "I needed to look elsewhere in his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:082eead",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "AriaC: How long did this meeting last, Headmaster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084a547",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "Theodore: Our meeting went on for an hour.[p/] After which, she left.[p/] Presumably to prepare for her next class."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e9aeb",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: So that means the professor left your office at 1:00 PM?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021f117",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: Yes.[p/] She was quite adamant about taking time to prepare her lesson plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:01056f4",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "Now that I thought about it,[p/] Miriam had no idea what the time was when she saw Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbeaf2",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "If the headmaster [i]was[/i] lying about when the meeting ended,[p/] there’d be no way to verify it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c29ac",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "Which would account for the “hour gap” that Steelwind mentioned."
}

{
  "id": "line:082eed0",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] Did the headmaster really do this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1e060",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: After hearing so much about her...[p/] I find that a little hard to believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bef443",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...I can see why you’d say that,[p/] but despite everything,[p/] I was still her superior."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c4dc",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: She always remained professional when speaking with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:027d3dd",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "Was that really true, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f224d4",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: Really?[p/] Even after the way she’s acted toward the students and faculty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fafc53",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: Make no mistake,[p/] I’ve heard many complaints regarding her actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0606cd4",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: And I’ve had many conversations with her to attempt to correct her behavior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8617d",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: At the end of the day,[p/] however,[p/] she [i]was[/i] a remarkable professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0439d30",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Regardless of her lack of people skills."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21142",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "CELESTE: His testimony pretty much matches what we know so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0969416",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m not entirely sure if he’s lying or not."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c9993",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "TYRION: At the very least,[p/] we know that he was involved in the professor’s murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0223725",
  "node": "Cross_Theo",
  "text": "First,[p/] I would need to make his motive clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0556353",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Redmond.[p/] Did you really hold no animosity toward Professor Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b98e2",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "THEODORE: Of course not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfa066",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "THEODORE: I [i]did[/i] have strong opinions about how she treated the students,[p/] but I always remained professional.[p/] We both did."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f2642",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "TYRION: Frankly,[p/] I find that hard to believe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0717e",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "TYRION: In fact,[p/] I think you might have had a [i]very[/i] good reason to murder the professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0439f3c",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Considering that she was going to take your job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6da74",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "THEODORE: S-[p/][s/]So you knew about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08e16",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "AriaC: I’m sorry,[p/] but I don’t follow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b989f8",
  "node": "TheoObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Just [i]how[/i] was the professor going to take the headmaster’s job?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a3a0",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: According to Miriam Frega,[p/] Catherine Bellwether was currying favor with the school board."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c63a",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: In fact,[p/] there was a plan to oust Mr. Redmond and appoint Bellwether as the new headmaster of the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0085db0",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0708638",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...B-[p/][s/]But in any case,[p/] I doubt that the headmaster had [i]any[/i] idea of this until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0123eb4",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I’d like to remind the court of the witness’s reaction just now."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5531",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: He said,[p/] “So you knew about that...”"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ff04d",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: His reaction was one of surprise,[p/] but he wasn’t surprised [i]by[/i] this information."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e00e1",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: He was surprised that I [i]knew[/i] this information!"
}

{
  "id": "line:072cd3c",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: T-[p/][s/]That’s-!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfc17e",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Please,[p/] dear Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e74dca",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I may be a frail old man,[p/] but I’m perfectly capable of defending myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84f55",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: If you have an explanation, Mr. Redmond,[p/] then by all means,[p/] I’d love to hear it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aef3c",
  "node": "TheoObj_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Gladly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0140865",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: It [i]is[/i] true that I knew about the Fregas’ plot beforehand,[p/] but I had only [i]just[/i] learned about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0dd6b",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: On the day of the murder,[p/] the professor told me about her plan.[p/] She was going to replace me as headmaster and replace the staff with her Arcane Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee1131",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: Now,[p/] you might say that this would have given me the perfect motive to murder the professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c20158",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: However,[p/] the supposed murder weapon was stolen from Lady Frega.[p/] This happened weeks before our meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffb9f2",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: I had no knowledge of their plan before she told me,[p/] and therefore,[p/] I wouldn’t have known to steal Lady Frega’s weapon in an attempt to frame her."
}

{
  "id": "line:054b0be",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: Are you satisfied now, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e12c84",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "AriaC: There is no way that the headmaster could have come up with this plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab8152",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hm...[p/] If he [i]really[/i] did do this,[p/] that means he stole the rapier too, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090fcf7",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Most likely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0758cb0",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: His alibi makes sense.[p/] He couldn’t have planned this whole thing unless he knew about Bellwether's plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c7d0c",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: That would mean he knew about this weeks ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0335b61",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: But how did he even find out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0882475",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: The best way to tell a convincing lie is to leave a lot of truths and only change one detail."
}

{
  "id": "line:008ad9b",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Maybe Bellwether [i]did[/i] tell him,[p/] but she actually told him weeks ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0122f81",
  "node": "TheoObj_3",
  "text": "But how would I [i]prove[/i] that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079925f",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: So, you only learned about it recently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037d367",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Doesn’t that seem a bit too convenient for you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a1337",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: It may appear that way.[p/] Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0449a39",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "Theodore: But..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b392",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: That must have infuriated you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0260ddd",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Your colleague betrayed you [i]and[/i] attempted to steal your job."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a5ade",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I’m only human. Of course I was taken aback."
}

{
  "id": "line:095e1f3",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I’ve been headmaster of the Imperial Academy for nearly sixty years."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bb5e8",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: To think that the professor [i]and[/i] the board would go around my back like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cbd8c",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "Theodore: Now, you might say that this would have given me the perfect motive to murder the professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ddb1c",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: With the professor dead,[p/] you won’t have to worry about losing your job."
}

{
  "id": "line:022305a",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: At least not for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c9198",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I suppose you’re correct,[p/] but there are others who benefit too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6bdc9",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: The faculty staff is now aware of the Fregas’ plot."
}

{
  "id": "line:093498c",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: With her plot delayed,[p/] they won’t need to worry about abruptly losing their jobs either."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b1ddc",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "...But what would happen if I proved that Redmond was the killer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff9413",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "He would be sent to prison [i]and[/i] the school board would just appoint someone else to carry out their plan..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0558e0a",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d96c2",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "No...[p/] I couldn't think about that now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72082",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "If I couldn't prove Redmond's guilt,[p/] the court would convict Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d85d73",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: As the headmaster,[p/] you’d probably have the tools available to get into her room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc224d",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Yes,[p/] I will admit that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c943",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: The academy has a master key that can be used to enter each of the students' dorms."
}

{
  "id": "line:092d0ff",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Then you had the perfect way to get into her room [i]and[/i] steal the rapier undetected."
}

{
  "id": "line:024092b",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I suppose I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee352",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: However,[p/] there’s one flaw with your logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:09742b2",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: It was my understanding that the school board wanted to keep this a secret until the very end."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bd160",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Why would Bellwether,[p/] of all people,[p/] tell you about her betrayal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c447a4",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I imagined she wanted to taunt me with that information."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e45d46",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: We’ve long had our disagreements,[p/] and looking back,[p/] she may have resented me for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dbb6a",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: At that point,[p/] there wasn’t anything I could do to stop her."
}

{
  "id": "line:066d222",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Really?[p/] I thought you and the professor were on good terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3c1d",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: I’d thought so too,[p/] but I suppose it was all a façade. [h=\"Hmph...|I was never on good terms with that witch...\" e=\"a\"]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65502",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "THEODORE: She was just biding her time until she could take my position as headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e729d8",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "CELESTE: If he's the one behind this,[p/] he had to have known about Bellwether’s betrayal weeks ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c80353",
  "node": "Cross_Theo2",
  "text": "TYRION: Right...[p/] The question is:[p/] how do we prove it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ecc9c",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: Redmond.[p/] You keep saying that you didn’t know about Bellwether’s plot before yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:008fb17",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you still plan on standing behind that claim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095bf43",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "THEODORE: Of course I am.[p/] It’s the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a011d4",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m sorry, Redmond,[p/] but you should really close your doors during your meetings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3734b",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "THEODORE: W-[p/][s/]What...? [h=\"No!|...Did someone see us?!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd8fbe",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: It [i]is[/i] true that Bellwether revealed her plan to you during one of your meetings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0129b6d",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: In fact,[p/] Jan Hughes happened to overhear that same meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:058f78e",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: But he only overheard the part where the staff would be replaced."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dcd76",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09271dd",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: And that's the strangest part, Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbf610",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: According to Mr. Hughes, this meeting..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1b5c4",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Occurred weeks ago!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04877ec",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: You can’t accuse the headmaster of perjury based on a rumor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e11c89",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: Everything you’ve just said is based on second-hand information!"
}

{
  "id": "line:036e292",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: Mr. Hughes [i]distinctly[/i] overheard that the staff would be replaced with Arcane Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:00204b2",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "TYRION: That is [i]too[/i] specific and [i]too[/i] accurate to assume that he misheard."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b778c",
  "node": "Theo2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: The professor must have only revealed her plan for the Arcane Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:091b137",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "AriaC: That [i]still[/i] doesn’t prove that he knew about her treachery beforehand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847335",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Professor Bellwether had no authority over the cleaning staff’s employment."
}

{
  "id": "line:060ec2c",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: It wouldn’t make sense for her to [i]just[/i] reveal her plan for the Arcane Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0499378",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: That would only make sense if he knew that Bellwether would be taking his job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed62e",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, tell me one thing, Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:04feba6",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Why did you find the need to lie about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0250d6f",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Is it because you saw a need to establish an alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5c28",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbfb44",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Redmond.[p/] I'm only going to ask you one more time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0186a3a",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]Did[/i] you murder Catherine Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d8ab7",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_2",
  "text": "Theodore Redmond had done something truly terrible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f047",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: The school board rejected my proposed staffing budget."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d4883",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: We won't be able to hire more custodians..."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e281",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: Of course they rejected it.[p/] Our current janitor simply needs to stop lazing about."
}

{
  "id": "line:093ee7b",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: Then you wouldn't have to spend all of your free time helping him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7c17",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: How did you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:084fca6",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: Is [i]that[/i] how they found out![p/][s/] Did you [i]tell[/i] them?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089d5e8",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: I did..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e49e8",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: Why?![p/][s/] What I do after school hours is none of your concern!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed17d",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: It [i]becomes[/i] my concern when the headmaster of [i]my[/i] academy debases himself in such a manner."
}

{
  "id": "line:030bd70",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: You were mopping floors alongside him like a common servant.[p/] Have you no shame?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099b2f4",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: What else was I supposed to do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02935f2",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: You can't possibly expect one man to keep an entire school clean!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b5016",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: Hughes is clearly capable.[p/] The academy is spotless despite his lounging about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0468fd0",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: Only because he's working during every waking hour!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db498c",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: He barely has enough time to sleep!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09adc12",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: Please.[p/] I've caught him napping on the job more times than I can count."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8658",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Catherine: Honestly,[p/] you coddle these animals far too much..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ddd16",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_3",
  "text": "Theodore: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e060f",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: Professor Bellwether,[p/] I've called you here to discuss your treatment of certain students."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b04746",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: This again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5fea1",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: Do you remember Gillian Fletcher?[p/] He was a part of your Advanced Illusion Track."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2eee",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: I remember failing him.[p/] His performance during the final exam was laughable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d826c6",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: ...They found his body in the lake last night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b487a0",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e382cb",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: I had always warned you that something like this might happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:05412bd",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: I understand you feel that you have responsibilities to the kingdom,[p/] but our students are still human beings."
}

{
  "id": "line:030f989",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: I fail to see how any of this is [i]my[/i] responsibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a24e9",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: Professor![p/][s/] Surely,[p/] even [i]you[/i] must understand—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:045d39d",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: No,[p/] I think it's [i]you[/i] who fails to understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0464",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: He may have been a mage,[p/] but he could never walk the path of the Scaled Lord's chosen with such a plebeian constitution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0051723",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: What did you think would happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0319479",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: The [i]real[/i] act of cruelty was placing that layabout next to our kingdom's best and brightest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa3133",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: What did you think happens to trash when they're faced with their betters?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb6cd6",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: [i]You[/i] never allowed him the opportunity to succeed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7dd2e",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: Don't think I'm blind to what's been happening!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0152959",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: I have received several reports that you've been harassing the students admitted through the scholarship program!"
}

{
  "id": "line:099138e",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: Then take those reports to the school board, Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9fbd5",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: If these urchins fall apart over the tiniest bit of criticism,[p/] then they have no place here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c1fe3",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: They can't handle it, Redmond.[p/] It's that simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad0caa",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Catherine: Maybe this incident will finally make you see reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:073bac9",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_4",
  "text": "Theodore: You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ca60e",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: What do I do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:060f3c7",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: How do I stop her?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eac040",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: It's only a matter of time before the school board names her as the new headmaster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:037b63a",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: After that,[p/] I won't be able to protect anyone from her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de4362",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: I'll be powerless..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f74343",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: That's not how I see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0238ca1",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b50f93",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: You're clinging to shadows, Redmond.[p/] Titles,[p/] influence,[p/] reputation—[p/]they're all just illusions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0688717",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: Strip those away,[p/] and you're Bellwether's equal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0307f12",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: Hmph...[p/] If only it truly worked like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06df535",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: Reality is far more complicated than that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06822f3",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: Is it, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78c15",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: Her friends on the school board can't pump blood through her veins."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c159",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: Those nobles she dotes on can't draw breath into her lungs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a521bd",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: All are equal in death.[p/] The survivors are the ones who determine what will be."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5ae0",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: It doesn't matter if you're a commoner,[p/] a noble,[p/] or the Scaled Lord himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06bb0",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Theodore: W-[p/][s/]What are you saying...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a6959",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: You should fight for what you believe in."
}

{
  "id": "line:054031d",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_5",
  "text": "Eris: Do whatever it takes to create the universe you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:048764b",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "He had truly despised Catherine Bellwether with all of his heart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3cd18",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "In his mind,[p/] this world was a better place without her in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ba64d",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "Yet the sound of that rapier piercing her heart had been echoing endlessly within his head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0681e7a",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "It was as if her ghost were floating over his shoulder,[p/] torturing him by repeating her last anguished gasps."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f04be",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "It made his stomach churn.[p/] He took no pleasure in taking her life,[p/] and his soul felt forever scarred from what he'd done."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fe33f",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "Eris: ...But you've already come this far, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07eb2a2",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "Theodore: I [i]have[/i] already come this far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c62033",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "THEODORE: What a fine mess this is... [h=\"I’m not done...|Not yet...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:001c883",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "AriaC: ...H-[p/][s/]Headmaster?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ebf10",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "THEODORE: So,[p/] you truly plan on pushing this,[p/] do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3e140",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I won't let anyone stop me from getting justice for Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:001e62c",
  "node": "Theo2Obj_6",
  "text": "THEODORE: Well,[p/] your thesis [i]sounds[/i] promising, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but I believe your arguments could use a little work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0033a9c",
  "node": "TheoCornered",
  "text": "Theodore: You think I killed Catherine Bellwether?[p/][s/] Me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05243d7",
  "node": "TheoCornered",
  "text": "Theodore: I am an elderly man in his late 80’s."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df88df",
  "node": "TheoCornered",
  "text": "Theodore: I can barely walk,[p/] much less wield a rapier."
}

{
  "id": "line:07732ff",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Construct|Contructs"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c760",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you and Bellwether weren’t the only people in that room, were you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0abcc90",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You needed the Arcane Construct to carry Bellwether’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:075cf5b",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That means that the Construct would have already been in your office."
}

{
  "id": "line:039b645",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And with your privileges,[p/] you could have easily programmed the Construct to stab Bellwether for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e69847",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "Theodore: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0127d4d",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "No...[p/] That’s not right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d49811",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "He's technically correct.[p/] There's no way he could have overpowered Bellwether by himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c39f44",
  "node": "TheoCornered2",
  "text": "But was he [i]really[/i] by himself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0920e3f",
  "node": "TheoCornered3",
  "text": "Theodore: E-[p/][s/]Even so,[p/] think about what would have transpired afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e0c1",
  "node": "TheoCornered3",
  "text": "Theodore: Do you recall Ms. Steelwind’s timeline of Bellwether’s witnesses?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe1bd4",
  "node": "TheoCornered3",
  "text": "Theodore: With your theory,[p/] the Construct would have spent more than [i]an hour[/i] in the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:070079c",
  "node": "TheoCornered3",
  "text": "Theodore: Having it there would have risked my so-called ruse from being discovered. [h=\"I was lucky.|Lady Frega can’t tell night from day.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ab8ae",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "Logic"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5b97",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "Intuition"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df927b",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: The timing deduced from Ms. Frega’s testimony is predicated on one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0081cc5",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: She saw Ms. Bellwether exit your office after your meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d5bab",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: However,[p/] if we assume that you’re [i]lying[/i] about when this “meeting” ended,[p/] your entire argument falls apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b447e",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega would have encountered Bellwether after her death at 2:01 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:068d8f5",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "THEODORE: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Frega wouldn’t have made a mistake like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0354d79",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega thought it was [i]morning[/i] when she saw Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:082a1c5",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "TYRION: She can’t reliably tell the time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6023",
  "node": "TheoCornered4",
  "text": "Empathy"
}

{
  "id": "line:07890a1",
  "node": "TheoInterpret4Fail",
  "text": "Tyrion: Redmond,[p/] what you’re saying clearly doesn’t match with what you’re thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d6c6e",
  "node": "TheoInterpret4Fail",
  "text": "Theodore: What kind of weak assertion is that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b34710",
  "node": "TheoInterpret4Fail",
  "text": "Theodore: How could you [i]possibly[/i] know what I'm thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c806",
  "node": "TheoInterpret4Fail",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/]Oh, um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c9dd1",
  "node": "TheoInterpret4Fail",
  "text": "I needed to choose my words more carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0f09",
  "node": "TheoCornered5",
  "text": "Theodore: T-[p/][s/]Then what about where the rapier was placed?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064e857",
  "node": "TheoCornered5",
  "text": "Theodore: If I really [i]was[/i] the murderer,[p/] then that would mean I planted the weapon in young [i]Wallace’s[/i] locker!"
}

{
  "id": "line:075483d",
  "node": "TheoCornered5",
  "text": "Theodore: Several of the students had lockers there that I had access to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea387a",
  "node": "TheoCornered5",
  "text": "Theodore: Wallace is one of my prized students.[p/][s/] If I had to frame anyone,[p/][s/] he would be the [i]last[/i] person I chose!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02deebd",
  "node": "TheoCornered6",
  "text": "LockerBlood2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4937f",
  "node": "TheoCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’re right, Mr. Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0049f20",
  "node": "TheoCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You wouldn’t try to frame Wallace,[p/] but you [i]would[/i] try to frame Miriam Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7b241",
  "node": "TheoCornered6",
  "text": "He wouldn't have [i]intentionally[/i] framed Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b14fcb",
  "node": "TheoCornered6",
  "text": "Something must have confused him about whose locker he placed the rapier in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0570e3c",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would have been the perfect act of revenge, wouldn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a47f36",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You murder your treacherous co-worker [i]and[/i] frame the daughter of the family that helped her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cf67f",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Miriam had been implicated,[p/][s/] the Inquisition would have immediately swept Bellwether's murder under the rug!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c027e",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But something went wrong, didn’t it, Redmond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08096cd",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The labels on Wallace’s locker and Miriam’s locker were switched."
}

{
  "id": "line:0561896",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyone who saw that would have easily mixed them up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70fd4",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Theodore: I am the [i]headmaster[/i] of the Imperial Academy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0316378",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Theodore: I have records of all the students’ lockers and where they’re located!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44ec5",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Theodore: If I truly planned this,[p/][s/] I would have [i]known[/i] where Wallace’s locker was!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9c966",
  "node": "TheoCornered7",
  "text": "Theodore: A simple change in labels wouldn’t have led me to make a careless mistake like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5def0",
  "node": "TheoCornered8",
  "text": "Construct|LockerCon"
}

{
  "id": "line:026ff59",
  "node": "TheoCornered8",
  "text": "TYRION: But it wasn’t you, was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076afea",
  "node": "TheoCornered8",
  "text": "TYRION: Your Arcane Construct was the one who planted the rapier in the locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a31b15",
  "node": "TheoCornered8",
  "text": "No...[p/] He would have noticed if the locker IDs were switched."
}

{
  "id": "line:0376f38",
  "node": "TheoCornered8",
  "text": "But that was all based on the assumption that [i]he[/i] was the person who planted the rapier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c125a4",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "TYRION: I bet you commanded it to “place this rapier in the locker of Miriam Frega”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892bd9",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "TYRION: But it saw the ID number on Wallace’s locker and assumed that it was Miriam’s."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7cf9",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "THEODORE: T-[p/][s/]This is...![p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:048b546",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "Redmond was desperately stammering."
}

{
  "id": "line:057fa3f",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "THEODORE: Ms. Steelwind,[p/][s/] say something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057903b",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: ...What?![p/][s/] I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e9883",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: Agh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:013e35a",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] Your theory may be plausible but there’s no evidence to support it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066252e",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "THEODORE: Ha![p/][s/] That’s right![p/][s/] You don’t have any proof, do you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068bc77",
  "node": "TheoCornered9",
  "text": "THEODORE: Saying that I could have committed the murder isn’t the same as proving I did it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04af87d",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "LockerCon"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edcfee",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Arcane Construct is [i]still[/i] in the locker room where it planted the rapier!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09442f4",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: All we have to do is take a look inside it,[p/] and we’ll see the blood inside!"
}

{
  "id": "line:073923d",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "THEODORE: Is that so, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7892a",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "What...?[p/] Why did he still look so confident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de228f",
  "node": "TheoCornered10",
  "text": "No...[p/] Wasn't there some sort of evidence that would track the orders given to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bbafc",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: No...![p/] Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25da4",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: I already checked the inside of that Construct during my investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7f9d3",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: The interior was completely clean."
}

{
  "id": "line:00753d7",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "TYRION: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc373b",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "THEODORE: The Constructs’ primary function is to assist and [i]clean[/i], dear Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:098648e",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "THEODORE: They have a function that allows them to clean [i]themselves[/i],[p/][s/] inside and out!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84f0c",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "Tyrion: That still wouldn't erase the magical traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:07245a2",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Healing spells may leave traces of [b]necromancy[/b],[p/] but so would a healing potion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f0966",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "Theodore: With no evidence of blood,[p/] there could be a myriad of reasons why those traces are there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e48e4",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] we can still look at its command history, right?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:073888f",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Think about it, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0938",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: Do you honestly think that the murderer would leave behind evidence like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d6de5",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I’m sure that [i]whoever[/i] orchestrated this plot,[p/] they ordered the Construct to wipe its logs when it was finished."
}

{
  "id": "line:061840a",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "TYRION: N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d2ac5",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye",
  "text": "THEODORE: That’s right, Mr. Cuthbert!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0592732",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: Your case against me is theoretical at best!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fecdd",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: But I suppose I can still give you marks for trying!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da3548",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "He thought of everything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0689a84",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "Did he really get rid of all of the evidence?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ceefa",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "I was running out of options."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fd096",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "But I still had [i]one[/i] option left."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d69fa",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Ha![p/] It’s unbecoming to glare like that, young Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cb373",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...? [h=\"He's doing it again...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:013ffb7",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "I needed to bring myself back to that moment with Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:080eaa5",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "Everything was at stake for Wallace in this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a701",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "He endured the collective hatred of everyone who didn't understand what he was doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0895647",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "Yet he stayed true to his ideals,[p/] no matter how much it harmed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bf978",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "He studied [b]necromancy[/b],[p/] all for the betterment of mankind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0419bfc",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "His life and his future were in my hands,[p/] and I would [i]not[/i] see his potential destroyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b36d1b",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "I activated the Empowered Eye again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf26c0",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "Redmond did a good job of covering his tracks,[p/] but there was no such thing as the perfect crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:063a647",
  "node": "TheoEmpEye_2",
  "text": "There had to be something that he forgot to get rid of!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0376018",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Why was the Construct in the locker room...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0951193",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: It shouldn't have been there if it had followed my orders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c92bd1",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: No matter...[p/] It wiped its logs.[p/] That's all that matters."
}

{
  "id": "line:081d801",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: They have nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:01145bd",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "So, he [i]did[/i] order it to wipe its logs..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b050b8",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "In order to cover all of its tracks,[p/] it probably would have done this last."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afab33",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Construct|Logic|Map"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e54a98",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: The Construct's orders were clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e1c82",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Plant the body in Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:0404f9e",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: And then plant the evidence in Frega's locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a05aca",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: It was [i]supposed[/i] to head to the Storage Room afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0560fa6",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8b749",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Interesting...[p/] The Construct wasn't [i]supposed[/i] to be in the Locker Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:007386c",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edcdb8",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I can't believe I let this boy push me this far..."
}

{
  "id": "line:094a8bb",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I was too careless...[p/] I should have been [i]much[/i] more wary of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845617",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Eris"
}

{
  "id": "line:0995cf4",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Agh...[p/] My head..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eeea5",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: The stress from this trial must be giving me a migraine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2b41",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "That was strange...[p/] Why couldn't I make him think about Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0913395",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Well,[p/] I suppose it doesn't matter.[p/] I had no reason to think Eris was involved anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbea66",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:094f3aa",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: It's all Tymora's fault that I'm even here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b465f",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: If it weren't for my debts,[p/] that boy would have never even [i]met[/i] Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f35420",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Catherine|Blood2|Catherine Autopsy|BellRep|BellPlan|BellPlan2"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b4c95",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I can't believe I put myself into this mess for [i]Bellwether[/i] of all people..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ef8c5",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: ...Why do I feel remorse for her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0664c2a",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: She [i]deserved[/i] what happened to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d6d6a",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Jan|Valentina|Valerie"
}

{
  "id": "line:09adbc8",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I wasn't just thinking of myself..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b461cf",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: The staff...[p/][s/] Bellwether would have thrown them onto the [i]street[/i] if not for what I did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08862f0",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Miriam|Four|Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:0046ada",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: This is all the nobility's fault!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a23f2",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: This [i]whole[/i] time they were plotting to throw me out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c81931",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: It's [i]their[/i] fault that Bellwether is dead![p/][s/] Not mine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ffb61",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Her blood is on the hands of the Fregas [i]and[/i] the Steelwinds."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e14db",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Foul"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8ef8a",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I wonder...[p/] Did I leave any other pieces of evidence behind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b849cb",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I was far too reckless..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f68c8",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: But I needed [i]some[/i] way to keep that lecture hall empty."
}

{
  "id": "line:067a461",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Oh, right.[p/] He must have botched the alchemy experiment on purpose to keep the lecture hall clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1b413",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "But that didn't really tell me anything I could use right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd1a5c",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Head Action|Lockdown"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc58a9",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I had to do everything I could to shift guilt away from myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf010",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: ...But did I leave any holes in my alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088335c",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: No...[p/] I accounted for everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16e94",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: There's [i]no[/i] possible way I left any evidence behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b888e",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "JanTest2"
}

{
  "id": "line:07750bd",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: ...My [b]illusion[/b] should have been flawless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd45e4",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I can't believe this boy was able to deduce what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a1027",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Blood|Blood2|Cheat|Rapier|Rapier2"
}

{
  "id": "line:070381a",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I did everything I could to cast doubt on Frega's brat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847b06",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: I can't believe Valerie placed a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7cf75",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: To make matters worse,[p/] the Construct placed the evidence in the wrong locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b75b2",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "So, he [i]did[/i] send the Construct to the locker room to plant the evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001de9",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "He must have also fabricated the documents that accused Miriam of cheating."
}

{
  "id": "line:03de571",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "It was all to make [i]her[/i] look like the murderer,[p/] but this doesn't give me anything new to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5f928",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: ...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0932b",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Theodore: Why am I thinking of this [i]now[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090b26e",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] That piece of evidence didn’t evoke any useful thoughts from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:07efe6e",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "Maybe I needed to try PROJECTING something related to the Construct's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:050af18",
  "node": "TheoEye",
  "text": "There was nothing there for me to use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a573d5",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] He ordered the Construct to go to the Storage Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebf8fb",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye",
  "text": "It should have done that [i]after[/i] it was finished planting evidence in the locker room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdacb6",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye",
  "text": "But we [i]found[/i] it in the Locker Room..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f44c6f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Lockdown|Head Action"
}

{
  "id": "line:025b486",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Redmond clearly didn't intend for the Construct to end up in the Locker Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:004ad59",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_2",
  "text": "Someone or something must have interfered with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6413c",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_3",
  "text": "Right...[p/] The body was probably reported earlier than Redmond expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d06d69",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_3",
  "text": "That meant he probably started the lockdown [i]while[/i] the Construct was still in the Locker Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:096a4da",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_3",
  "text": "But does this change anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a3652",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_4",
  "text": "No...[p/] The lockdown prevented the Construct from leaving the Locker Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7d94d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_4",
  "text": "Would that have affected any of the elements at play during that time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0beedb6",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "Right...[p/] The series of commands would have been interrupted..."
}

{
  "id": "line:035640f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "Wait a minute!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c31939",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Constructs execute a series of commands in the order that they are given."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e4ef8",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "MIRIAM: But let’s say one of those tasks is impossible to complete."
}

{
  "id": "line:0837036",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "MIRIAM: When the Construct gets to that task,[p/] it will deem the entire series impossible to complete."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eefb6d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "MIRIAM: As a result,[p/] it will stop executing the series altogether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0902785",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_5",
  "text": "Celeste: So if a task in a series of commands is impossible,[p/] then that command will interrupt the entire series."
}

{
  "id": "line:080cba1",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "If Redmond was trying to cover his tracks,[p/] the Construct’s [i]final[/i] command would be to wipe its memory..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04429b4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "But if its orders were interrupted by the lockdown,[p/] then—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c9b64",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Steelwind,[p/] I have nothing more to ask this witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeae3f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05215ef",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "CELESTE: You’re not giving up, are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002f662",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "CELESTE: Yeah...[p/] I thought so,[p/] but how are you going to prove he did it if he’s not on the stand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7b69f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "TYRION: Don’t worry.[p/] The next witness’s testimony will be all I need."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beb659",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "CELESTE: \"Next\" witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08104fb",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: That look on your face isn’t one of resignation..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027a686",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "THEODORE: Ha![p/][s/] It’s nothing but desperate bravado."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05fae",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "THEODORE: Now,[p/] if you’ll excuse me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0435a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: ...You’ve let him get away, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e6ec",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: I hope you know what you’re doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e45a1a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "TYRION: I do, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:075d407",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "TYRION: First,[p/] I’d like for the Inquisition to bring in the Arcane Construct in the academy’s locker room."
}

{
  "id": "line:072a363",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: We’ve already established that the murderer could have wiped its history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c704a7",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "TYRION: Please...[p/] Just humor me for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:049a2bd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d99340",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_6",
  "text": "AriaC: Bailiff,[p/] please relay Mr. Cuthbert's request to Commander White."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4b88d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "AriaC: Well...[p/] Here's your Construct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae4042",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "AriaC: I hope you know what you're doing, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0113f60",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "TYRION: Construct!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038449b",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Construct: WHAT ARE YOUR ORDERS?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ef7bb",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "TYRION: Please recite your command history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0591fd1",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Construct: REPORTING."
}

{
  "id": "line:002dfef",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 1:[p/] STANDBY IN \\[Headmaster’s Office\\]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d24433",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 2:[p/] AWAIT VOCAL SIGNAL \\[“Attack!”\\] FROM \\[Theodore Redmond\\]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4238",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Redmond stood up from the gallery,[p/] his face turning from confusion into terrified realization."
}

{
  "id": "line:0900300",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Steelwind watched him carefully,[p/] clutching the handle of her cane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08792",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 3:[p/] TREAT \\[Catherine Bellwether\\] AS A HOSTILE ENTITY AND NEUTRALIZE."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7cf46",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "THEODORE: Construct![p/][s/] Wipe your—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c4cc",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]Hodl[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b10a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "Before he could finish his order,[p/] the prosecutor whipped out her cane and pointed it square at the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee663a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_7",
  "text": "The headmaster tensed as his body tightened and he fell over,[p/] restrained by magical energy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2976a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "He struggled against the spell to no avail.[p/] He could only watch through gritted teeth as the Construct continued."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b042",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "JUDGE: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7707",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "AriaC: Excuse the interruption.[p/] Please continue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beee3a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 4:[p/] AWAIT VOCAL SIGNAL “Leave” FROM \\[Theodore Redmond\\]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d10c1f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 5:[p/] MOVE TO CLASSROOM 2-B. REPLY TO ANY INQUIRIES WITH VOICE LINE #3"
}

{
  "id": "line:040e93f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND 6:[p/] REMOVE \\[Catherine Bellwether\\] FROM INTERIOR FRAME AND PLACE ON FLOOR."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a93156",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: Thank you, Construct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a032c7",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: You can stop now.[p/] I think we all know the rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de8e08",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: But just to be clear,[p/] who gave you this series of commands?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04520b4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "Construct: COMMANDS WERE PROVIDED BY Headmaster \\[Theodore Redmond\\]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f324c",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "THEODORE: How...?[p/][s/] HOW?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:029f4de",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "THEODORE: I ordered the Construct to wipe its command history!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d9c2e",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: Redmond,[p/] Constructs don’t follow the same logic that humans do."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c580a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: They’re prone to error when their commands are impossible to execute."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c922dd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "THEODORE: “Impossible”?![p/][s/] How were my commands impossible?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03728e3",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: You were the one that [i]made[/i] it impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a9673",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "TYRION: You activated the lockdown system."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f2f5b",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_8",
  "text": "THEODORE: The lockdown...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5b21",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: I imagine you never expected anyone to go to Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6edf",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the Ianus twins discovered the body earlier than you expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fb6ad",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: You had no choice but to immediately activate the lockdown system when it was reported.[p/] It would have been suspicious otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d31e34",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: However,[p/][s/] the Construct was still in the Locker Room when you did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a67127",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "THEODORE: So [i]that’s[/i] why it was there..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001672",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: The Construct finished its tasks in the Locker Room,[p/] but then it tried to follow your next command."
}

{
  "id": "line:005726c",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: It attempted to move to the Storage Room,[p/] but was prevented from doing so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b17421",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: Completion of that command was impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:058a2f2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: So,[p/] the series of commands was stopped [i]before[/i] it wiped its history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07d69",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "THEODORE: No...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:002fe52",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: Theodore Redmond![p/][s/] You ordered your Construct to murder Catherine Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0389067",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: Then you had it place the murder weapon in a locker to frame Miriam Frega!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0267e8e",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "TYRION: And we have your Construct’s testimony to prove it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc35e2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's your last move, Redmond.[p/] That’s checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f3e0",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "AriaC: I...[p/] can’t believe it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0181ac9",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "AriaC: How could you do something like this, Headmaster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00bf8",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...She was going to take everything from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d05465",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: My position.[p/][p/][s/] My academy.[p/][p/][s/] My students."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2bb5",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: Everything would be gone.[p/][s/] It was going to be [i]stolen[/i] by her and the Fregas!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01aa506",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "AriaC: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:023ac6e",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "AriaC: Why didn’t you say anything...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5702",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "AriaC: I could have—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0680e09",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: Don’t you [i]dare[/i] stand there and act ignorant, Lady Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09811d4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: Do you think the Fregas acted alone?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a069b3",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: The Grand General is also on the school board,[p/] and he endorsed this plan just as much as they did!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3ada3",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: I have nothing to say to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84f55",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: I thought you were different.[p/] I listened to you and the prince's lies about societal reform."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa609",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: In the end,[p/] you were just like the rest of them..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f764b4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: By the Scaled Lord,[p/] what have I done?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7f50",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: I was even willing to sacrifice poor Wallace..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d38d2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_10",
  "text": "THEODORE: Why did I ever listen to[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba9570",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "Theodore: Why did I do this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04955e9",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "JUDGE: ...It appears we have a full confession."
}

{
  "id": "line:010f75a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "JUDGE: The court sees no reason to prolong this any further."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce0291",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "JUDGE: Bailiff,[p/] please escort the witness to a holding cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df7936",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "WALLACE: Mr. Cuthbert![p/][s/] You...[p/][s/] You really did it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0503f1a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: It feels amazing, right?[p/] Like a big weight being lifted from your shoulders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd6095",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "WALLACE: It does,[p/] but Headmaster Redmond—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97bcd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "WALLACE: What am I going to do now...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f97fd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "WALLACE: Headmaster Redmond was the only reason I could even [i]attend[/i] the Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8464c",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "WALLACE: If the school board replaces him with someone like Bellwether—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8b3ed",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: C-[p/][s/]Come on![p/][s/] Don’t think like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d3474",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "CELESTE: You've been acquitted![p/][s/] You still have your freedom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5fda0",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "I wanted to agree,[p/] but the study of [b]necromancy[/b] was outlawed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ea226",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "Without Redmond’s support,[p/] there weren’t many places he [i]could[/i] learn it."
}

{
  "id": "line:062fc69",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_11",
  "text": "And then there was staff at the Imperial Academy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03400fd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: H-[p/]Hey,[p/][s/] not you too!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f58165",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "TYRION: Sorry...[p/] But Valentina,[p/] Valerie,[p/] and Jan.[p/] They’re all going to lose their jobs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4c11",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Come on![p/][s/] You found the truth [i]and[/i] you put a murderer behind bars!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8ce78",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: You saved Wallace!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bafd2e",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Ruby: She's right."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ff16d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "As we exited the courtroom,[p/] we were greeted by Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb82ed",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Ruby: At the end of the day,[p/] you saved Wallace from a wrongful conviction."
}

{
  "id": "line:011041f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Ruby: You did what you set out to do.[p/] You should be proud of yourself for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a4d8",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "TYRION: I just wish I could do more."
}

{
  "id": "line:032b480",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Nope![p/][s/] None of that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092720a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Celeste: I’m taking all of us to that restaurant we went to last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c68cf",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you...[p/] remember how much that place cost?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d2317",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "CELESTE: Don’t worry.[p/] I have plenty of gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ce17",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Am I the only one on this team not making any money?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044f7fc",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Why don't you meet us there, Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c918b4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Ruby: I need to talk with Tyrion for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0157f02",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb5794",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Celeste: Let's go, Wallace!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06be91d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_12",
  "text": "Wallace: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:082dff8",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4fc85",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You used that ability again, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a1838",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "She didn't appear to be praising me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e092c2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/]I did...[p/] I didn't really have a choice..."
}

{
  "id": "line:080154a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: The Eye of Horus is a powerful tool, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aecb20",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: But that's twice now that you've used that ability to get out of a tough spot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0612938",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: You can't keep relying on it if you want to grow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0041470",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Ruby: One day,[p/] you'll find a witness that it [i]won't[/i] work on."
}

{
  "id": "line:08510b5",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's worked for me this far, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fadd5f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6c12",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll try to rely on it less next time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f55cf6",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "TYRION: And that marked the end of another case in my career as a defense attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b139",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "TYRION: Another life saved,[p/] and another murderer brought to justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0744e57",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "TYRION: ...But I still couldn’t shake this feeling of uneasiness."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a24a4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "TYRION: Was it guilt for what would happen to the faculty staff?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0575ee5",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_13",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Or was it something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe963b",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valerie: I can't believe it...[p/] It was really Theodore the entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0328222",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Jan: Can we talk about something else?[p/] Thinking about all that is really bumming me out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed4764",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I hope I'm not interrupting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1283",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valentina: Oh, great...[p/] What do [i]you[/i] want?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9684",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I've always tried to act with more compassion than my fellow aristocrats,[p/] but I suppose I'm still blind to the privilege I was born with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65db8",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I am truly sorry if my words during the trial were insensitive to your circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdcd10",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I've been speaking with the students here.[p/] There's quite a bit of outrage about your firing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0f7c5",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valentina: Wait,[p/] really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c58b6",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: The idea of a machine doing your job doesn't seem to sit well with the student body."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dc9e6",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: While not everyone was as sympathetic as I'd hoped,[p/] most everyone agrees that your leaving would be a tremendous loss."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34e50",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I've spoken with the head of the student council.[p/] We believe that we can convince the school board to keep you on staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f9b39",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valerie: You can do that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa60b",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: But is that what you want, Valentina?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b909",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I don't see the working conditions here improving without Redmond as headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e01c71",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valentina: Well...[p/] we've got to make a living somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f0478",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: ...There's actually a merchant out in Aurinax who takes an interest in people like you and your sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab692d",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: He's recently purchased a condemned building in the city,[p/] and he's looking to turn it into a restaurant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbb94e",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: I remember how delicious your meals were when I was a student here.[p/] I'm certain he would hire you if I asked."
}

{
  "id": "line:078b92e",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valentina: Really?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c320d",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: Would you be interested in that?[p/] It's a bit of a gamble,[p/] but your employment wouldn't be left to the whims of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eec835",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Valentina: O-[p/][s/]Of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76e7c",
  "node": "ValFinal",
  "text": "Aria: Good.[p/] I'll contact him later today.[p/] You'll probably be hearing from him soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bf369",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f606ba",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valerie: She's not so bad for a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcc778",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: ...I don't know if I buy it.[p/] You've heard about what her dad's been doing, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038486e",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valerie: Don't be so pessimistic.[p/] She seems nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1514",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: I'm kind of with Valentina on this one.[p/] Something's always been up with the Steelwinds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb795",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: Do you remember that scandal all those years ago?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8d4c0",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valerie: No, actually.[p/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a973",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: Right,[p/] you two were probably just kids when it all went down,[p/] but it was big news at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed9917",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: That girl's mom went on a rampage and massacred a village full of farmers—[p/]children included."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca8278",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2fce0",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: Lucio Steelwind's violent streak didn't start with these rebellions."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1030",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: I think they had a bad marriage or something.[p/] He couldn't wait to get rid of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd699",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: After what she did,[p/] he personally prosecuted her and demanded a death sentence."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a8e2e",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: He even carried out the execution himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0496601",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valerie: He really is a monster, isn't he...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:073ba7f",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah,[p/] I'm not sure if I'd trust [i]anyone[/i] raised by a guy like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:033ce0d",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: See?[p/] There's always something up with the aristocrats."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2483a",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: As far as I'm concerned,[p/] I'm not getting my hopes up until I hear from this \"merchant from Aurinax\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dd35a",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: But hey,[p/] if I do get that restaurant,[p/] we'll need [i]someone[/i] to help us keep it clean."
}

{
  "id": "line:004d081",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: You interested, Jan?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0964a8a",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: Cleaning one small restaurant instead of an entire school?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1c265",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Jan: I'm falling asleep just thinking about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fbee2",
  "node": "ValFinal2",
  "text": "Valentina: Okay...[p/] Just make sure you still do your job, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc606",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "KNIGHT: Man...[p/] Steelwind's been keeping the old timer here for hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:042a3ec",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "KNIGHT: What’s there to even ask at this point?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09094c8",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "Orym: Turns out she doesn't trust his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:02549df",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "Orym: Something about his memories not matching up with the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ebb77",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "Knight: I mean he [i]is[/i] pretty old."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba596",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] Well,[p/] she found that damned symbol etched into his desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:085dd0d",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ORYM: Or what did she call it?[p/] The \"Purple Mark”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0265014",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "KNIGHT: Oh,[p/] for the love of—[p/] Not [i]this[/i] again..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe7f2f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ORYM: Look.[p/] If the little lady wants to chase the boogeyman,[p/] just let her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7a406",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ORYM: At least this time,[p/] she’s doing it personally instead of dragging us into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5e60",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ERIS: Cast [b]Sleep[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a58fc9",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ORYM: H-[p/][s/]Hey!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9963f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_14",
  "text": "ORYM: What’s...[p/] up...[p/] with...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020b7fb",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e54030",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07383f6",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: Wait a minute!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c62072",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: I remember it now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5b539",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: But how—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05518c0",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "Eris: That was close."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4b891",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "Eris: My elation over meeting him almost made me forget."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c95db",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: Eris...[p/][s/] What are you doing here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:015e26f",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: W-[p/][s/]Why...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037aead",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: It was you![p/][s/] You put those ideas into my mind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7eb41",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "THEODORE: [i]You’re[/i] the one who told me to murder Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b670f4",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "Eris: Oh...[p/] You people never fail to amuse me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe5eb2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "Eris: I didn’t [p/][s/]\"[i]make[/i]\" you do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9f7b3",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_15",
  "text": "Eris: Everything you did that day—[p/]all the planning,[p/] all the preparation—[p/]that came from your [i]own[/i] mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:05123f2",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: And I have to say,[p/] I was quite entertained with the scheme you came up with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa3103",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: You even broke into Lady Frega’s room!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09647d7",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: I never thought you were capable of such things, Young Theodore!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0899f8a",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: Hm...[p/] It’s such a shame, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e88267",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: I wished I could have gotten Wallace to play the villain instead of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a7127",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: Could you imagine if [i]he[/i] turned?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b22cd",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: Armies of the undead,[p/] running rampant in the streets.[p/] It would have been spectacular."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38ae1",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: But alas,[p/] even [i]I[/i] couldn't corrupt him."
}

{
  "id": "line:048edfc",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: He falters in every other situation,[p/] but when it comes to [b]necromancy[/b],[p/] his will is adamantine."
}

{
  "id": "line:071f380",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "THEODORE: Answer me![p/][s/] Who are you?![p/][s/] [i]What[/i] are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:044a56b",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: Who am I...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcaccb",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "Eris: [j]I’m the ruler of the Sixth Circle—[p/]the Lord of Shadows.[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f9100",
  "node": "TheoAfterEye_16",
  "text": "THEODORE: AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b53292",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Bed"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e2fcd",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "It was an extravagant bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3d638",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "Miriam appeared to live pretty well here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a2440",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Dresser"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf51c6",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "It was a dresser.[p/] It probably contained Miriam's clothes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1903e",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "...It would definitely be a bad idea to take a closer look with Miriam here."
}

{
  "id": "line:028932a",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Table"
}

{
  "id": "line:0914c8b",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "It was a table for guests."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02a17",
  "node": "Dorm_Examine",
  "text": "...But it didn't look like it's seen much use until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aa622",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Questions"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6f5c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Frega.[p/] I was wondering if we could ask you some questions about—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3302a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Excuse me?[p/] I don’t believe anyone has permitted you to speak."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cc17d",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Oh,[p/] here we go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb0686",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste was still smiling,[p/] but I could faintly hear her grinding her teeth together."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fab68",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...S-[p/][s/]So,[p/] we heard about what happened to Professor Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0270cc9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I can’t believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3ba55",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes...[p/] It’s quite tragic what happened to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf6c19",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: She had always been a friend of House Frega..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027f161",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "She was obviously going to be more receptive to Celeste Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:014877c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "It might be better to let Celeste take the lead on the questioning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0022d5d",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: We heard that you saw her on the day of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f47f1",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Could you tell us more about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ff6b4",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh, you heard about that from your relative, did you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bf9df",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: If you don’t mind me asking,[p/] why are you so interested? [h=\"She’s not like Aria.| ...Is she?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c646d3",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Oh,[p/] you know.[p/] I’m just curious, is all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba1d63",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You know how uneventful life can be sometimes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aff915",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Being a noble and all."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3275",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Alright,[p/] she really needed to tone it down."
}

{
  "id": "line:043c1b8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh,[p/] is that all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0107355",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I was worried you were going down the same path as that poor,[p/] confused Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e80bc5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Well,[p/] I’m in the middle of a study break anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d04db",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I suppose I have some time to spill some tea."
}

{
  "id": "line:060afdc",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Speaking of...[p/] Construct,[p/] please prepare us some tea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f75e74",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: Use that lotus tea we imported from the Eastern Kingdoms. [h=\"She might be useful.|I should win her favor.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:061c83e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Construct: ACKNOWLEDGED."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8a6c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: “Lotus tea”...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8997a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You...[p/][s/] have Lotus Juice?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:014e0b5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "...I could feel myself slowly losing control of this situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5cb88",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: What did you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058ab27",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I heard that you were one of the last people who saw the professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:080f9da",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Where did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e23d7",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I was in the hallways when I saw her coming out of the headmaster’s office."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ba1b5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: She appeared to be heading towards the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb302e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you remember what time this happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035523c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Ah...[p/] I’m not really sure, honestly."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dafaa",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It’s a little embarrassing,[p/] but I have a bad habit of getting too absorbed in my work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0301c46",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Sometimes entire [i]hours[/i] will pass without my notice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3df78",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you have a rough idea at least?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021e132",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I believe it was in the morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e392b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "So it was [i]before[/i] her meeting with the headmaster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0753951",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Did anything seem off about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094bb6a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...No.[p/] It was a short encounter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb0984",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I merely greeted her,[p/] and she responded in kind. [h=\"Or at least...|that’s what [i]should[/i] have happened...\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01eb27e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "That thought just now...[p/] What did it mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c0270",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "I slowly glanced at Celeste and caught her attention."
}

{
  "id": "line:0948e46",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Using small motions,[p/] I shook my head.[p/] Miriam was holding something back."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a2d8b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Were you and the professor [i]really[/i] on good terms?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03357e7",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I heard she was pretty mean towards the other students."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db496a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Towards the riff-raff, maybe,[p/] but not to students like us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e75c7",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: She was my personal instructor during summer break."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e15376",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: She fulfilled a similar role to both—[p/] ...to my sister when she studied here."
}

{
  "id": "line:052f7a1",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: She was a long-time friend of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e84b73",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: That’s why we were planning on appointing her as the new headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa32cd",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/][s/] What did you just say?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e66396",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Replacing the Headmaster"
}

{
  "id": "line:0262b4f",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Did you just say that they were going to appoint [i]Bellwether[/i] as the new headmaster?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc11a0",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh, I’m surprised you didn’t know."
}

{
  "id": "line:003a812",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: House Frega holds several seats on the academy’s board, along with the Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bde32a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: We were making plans to have her replace that lout: Redmond."
}

{
  "id": "line:089825c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "They were going to sack the headmaster?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb20db",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Did Headmaster Redmond know about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba8b63",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh, of course not.[p/] This was part of a large-scale plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:05225d8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Along with Redmond,[p/] we were also going to replace all of the staff members with Arcane Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbdc54",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: We had to keep everything under wraps,[p/] or else the help would have left before we were ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:015863a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: And where would [i]that[/i] leave us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0840985",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "But Jan supposedly overheard Bellwether talking about the Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:083a63c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Did Bellwether prematurely reveal the plan to Theodore...?[p/] Or was Jan lying about how he found out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094c686",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: ...But alas.[p/] With Bellwether gone,[p/] we’ll have to delay our plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a7a2",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Frega's Rapier"
}

{
  "id": "line:0989729",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] We heard that Aria took your rapier as evidence for the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a011c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Can you believe her?![p/][s/] She [i]still[/i] won’t give it back to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c199c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: My father will have my head if I can’t get it back soon!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b5143",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: How did it even become a part of the investigation anyways?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5888d",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I don’t know![p/][s/] Aria won’t tell me anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3a03",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I swear if that [i]necromancer[/i] was the one who stole it,[p/] I’ll execute him myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:053505b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...So someone [i]did[/i] steal it from you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091fb57",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes...[p/] From right out of my room..."
}

{
  "id": "line:041fd5e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: When did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b5c03",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: About a few weeks ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd39f8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I noticed when I came back from one of my classes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0535ce1",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Someone removed the rapier from its display case in my room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b54193",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...How did they get into your room in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039974a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you think someone used magic to teleport past the door?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06755c1",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Please.[p/] I’m a master of [b]conjuration[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:07757b1",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: If someone attempted that,[p/] my enchantments would have shunted them out."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e0238",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "That meant that the thief came through one of the doors or windows."
}

{
  "id": "line:095d864",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I bet it was that necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0916ee8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: I’m sure a street child like him just [i]knows[/i] how to pick a lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f26ed",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Your Grades"
}

{
  "id": "line:0619e0a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I’ve heard that you’re one of the academy’s top students."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c7434",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Your grades must be amazing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5fc4e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Of course![p/] As an inheritor of House Frega,[p/] my grades are impeccable! [h=\"It feels good|to have my greatness recognized.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0985ed5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "That was strange...[p/] I didn't see anything contradictory through the Eye this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b31850",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Was she just delusional about how good a student she was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0baadee",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "I gestured to Celeste to continue pressing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0429591",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f2d2f",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: What kind of magic do you study here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0092c43",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: You must be joking.[p/] I study magic from the school of [b]conjuration[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f8ea",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Just like[p/] most members of my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:010e809",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: The school of [b]conjuration[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b56705",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: That’s the type of magic that specializes in spatial manipulation, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcb044",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes.[p/] I consider myself quite the expert in that field."
}

{
  "id": "line:042b241",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Why,[p/] the Crown Prince himself has asked for my assistance in a research study. [h=\"It's nice to finally work|with someone of my caliber.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e474aa",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Again,[p/] I didn’t see any thoughts that contradicted what she was saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d539d9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "If she was smart enough to get the Crown Prince’s attention,[p/] why would she be cheating?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a65e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Aria Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:042c2e5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You said something about “my wayward relative” before."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ef8c9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Were you talking about Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093133b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I’m terribly sorry if I offended you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0942ff8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: But I’m sure it must pain you to see the way that she’s been acting lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a1441",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/]Yes...[p/] It’s...[p/] been [i]extremely[/i] hard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a84c0e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Hang in there, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a932",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Did you know that she even interrogated [i]me[/i] about the murder yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036257b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Can you believe it?[p/] A [i]Steelwind[/i] running around a crime scene like a common knight."
}

{
  "id": "line:035df47",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Why,[p/] if I tried something like that,[p/] my father would disown me."
}

{
  "id": "line:080f418",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: She's so desperate to prove that she's nothing like her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead017",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that really what you believe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04484a2",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or are you just hiding the fact that you're here on your father's behalf?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee3121",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: I am [i]not[/i] working with my father! [h=\"I working against him|just as much as you are!\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bff9ee",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: My apologies.[p/] I didn't mean to lose my temper like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04780b5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Is that why she became a prosecutor?[p/] Was it all to reject her bloodthirsty father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036f91f",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Honestly,[p/] she probably thinks she can do anything just because of her betrothed. [h=\"She's so full of herself.|Aster deserves better.\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d8ce7",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: But if the Grand General keeps drowning these villages in blood,[p/] I imagine even [i]that[/i] will be in jeopardy. [h=\"And when that happens,|I'll steal him back.\" e=\"hs\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0261d4e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f26d",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste's eyes perked up.[p/] I'd be lying if I said mine didn't, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2703d",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "I was also curious about who this “Aster” was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e08c15",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "But I shook my head when she looked at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:010bac9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "We couldn't risk blowing our cover for some gossip about the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:052ce27",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Arcane Construct"
}

{
  "id": "line:038d11b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You have an Arcane Construct in your room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0436318",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I thought they were only in the library and the locker room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc51ee",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: [i]This[/i] Construct was a gift from House von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:09df5dc",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: I have to say,[p/] they’re quite convenient to have around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8914e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They look really cool.[p/] Maybe I should get one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6e509",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: You should."
}

{
  "id": "line:082e116",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam: A Construct would be far more useful than this attendant of yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a21dd7",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Yeah, maybe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365bd9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Unfortunately,[p/] there are still some issues with their intelligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:053157e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Their “intelligence”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032761e",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It happens when you give them complex commands."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b95c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Hm...[p/] It might be easier to show you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07af6f4",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Miriam turned to the Construct and began beckoning it over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d789c8",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Construct,[p/] please retrieve my textbooks and bring them here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0842825",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Then,[p/] cast [b]Steelwind Strike[/b] at this location."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5531c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: After that,[p/] retrieve some plates and set them out at this table."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3908",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039b9d5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "The Construct stood up and retrieved Miriam’s textbooks from one of the shelves in the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:057c57a",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "It brought them to the table they were sitting at,[p/] just like she'd ordered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faa88c",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "But then it suddenly stopped."
}

{
  "id": "line:021a841",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:029c7c9",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: The Construct obviously can’t cast [b]Steelwind Strike[/b],[p/] so my second command was impossible to carry out."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eb0b5",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: But did you notice something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56d17",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It ignored your third command, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0952f8f",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Exactly.[p/] My third command [i]was[/i] possible to carry out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af1c8b",
  "node": "Dorm_Talk",
  "text": "MIRIAM: When the Construct gets to that task,[p/] it will deem the [i]entire[/i] series impossible to complete."
}

{
  "id": "line:0825872",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: A Runestone?[p/] I have one as well,[p/] but mine is the latest model."
}

{
  "id": "line:04161d0",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0514326",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have a newer model?![p/][s/] Can I see it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064e8f6",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0982f9f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Your attendant doesn't appear to actually do much."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d4df8",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: How [i]do[/i] you put up with him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a0f0e",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] You know how it is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:067ef00",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "I couldn't help but appreciate how angry she was getting on my behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12828",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: I wasn't aware another Steelwind had enrolled at the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b1ba3",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Which branch family were you from again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfc135",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]It's one of the far-off branches."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4091",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: We're not that well-known."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc89c0",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f6f56",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aria|SteelOrd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d964c1",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Honestly,[p/] I don't know what Aria is thinking..."
}

{
  "id": "line:030ca32",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: At this rate,[p/] it won't matter [i]which[/i] House she belongs to."
}

{
  "id": "line:060b912",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: She'll be ruined..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0753735",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you...[p/] actually concerned about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6d23f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] Of course, not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:058259a",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: By the way,[p/] do you happen to know Eris Illmater?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01728d9",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: O-[p/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0199b4f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: I would stay away from her if I were you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09da139",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: I've heard some unsavory things have happened to people who cross her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a888c4",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: It's no wonder that she's joined forces with that necromancer..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04361bf",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherine|Catherine Autopsy|BellRep"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb2be7",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: It's such a shame what happened to the professor..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbf954",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: She truly was the best and most vigilant among the faculty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3014c",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "She was certainly [i]something[/i]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:002c2d5",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: I can't believe it took so long for that necromancer to be detained!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b40969",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: All it took was a [i]literal[/i] murder!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf60ea",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The trial isn't over yet.[p/] He's innocent until proven guilty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0399523",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Oh,[p/] of course,[p/] [i]you[/i] would say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08646a1",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: You trash can't [i]help[/i] but sympathize with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f3f2f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Do [i]not[/i] talk to him like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0fbd8",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]Wha—?! [h=\"Why do I suddenly feel|so terrified of her?\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca09bb",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/]Sorry...[p/] Just...[p/] don't,[p/] okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01feb0f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: O-[p/]Of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efd67a",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Ugh...[p/] With the professor gone,[p/] the headmaster is just going to bring more of those street urchins into the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05841c1",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is that really so bad, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0708018",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Every mage should have the right to develop their powers."
}

{
  "id": "line:08eac25",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Don't tell me that Aria got to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eef7f",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Mages were chosen by the Scaled Lord through divine right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0772c85",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, here we go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a5ce",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Magic is something that should [i]only[/i] be held by the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac49cb",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: These [i]bastard[/i] children have no right to call themselves mages!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad8300",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5259",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "...Maybe it was a mistake to put Celeste in this situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3fade",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Player: Miriam|Four"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db1b73",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: The Fregas primarily control Wyverngarde's finances, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79a75",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: But of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c96323",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: The Fregas own every banking house in the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e93c36",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: One could even say that we alone are responsible for Wyverngarde's prosperity."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1a4c",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "...How about sharing that \"prosperity\" with the commonfolk?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b4da6",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Player: Blood|Blood2|Rapier|Rapier2"
}

{
  "id": "line:096b60a",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: Ugh...[p/] I really hope Aria returns my rapier soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efa6da",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It must be pretty important to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:019ec38",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: It is an ancient family heirloom,[p/] wielded by Beatrice the first:[p/] one of the first heroes of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ee327",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: ... [h=\"I wonder...|Is she okay...?\" e=\"sf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bf5ac",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "I mean...[p/] If she was one of the heroes of Wyverngarde,[p/] she was probably long dead by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af657e",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Player: Construct|Logic|LockerCon"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f72779",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What do you think about this, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c91ed4",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffe3d8",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: ...I’m terribly sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6a8c1",
  "node": "Dorm_Present",
  "text": "Miriam: But I don’t have much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08aef29",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "I followed Steelwind’s directions and found Miriam Frega’s dorm room."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eb1b9",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "The door leading inside seemed a lot more ornately decorated than the other rooms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0315c3f",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "I went to knock on the door,[p/] not realizing that it was only partially closed."
}

{
  "id": "line:07abbf1",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "As my fist came into contact with the wood,[p/] I accidentally pushed it open."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee21c",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e7653",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "As the door swung open,[p/] I made eye contact with the girl inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:074aef3",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "She seemed to be studying at a desk,[p/] but she was now staring at me, stunned."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dad09",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "I slowly saw her expression shift from a puzzled look to a furious and violent scowl."
}

{
  "id": "line:027a762",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: Excuse me?![p/][s/] How [i]dare[/i] you barge into my room! [h=\"These insects!|They have no respect!\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc6ef4",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: S-[p/][s/]Sorry![p/] I was trying to knock,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5fdc6",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: Construct![p/][s/] Remove these hoodlums from my room!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2c55",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "From the corner of the room,[p/] an Arcane Construct stood up and began charging towards me at a terrifying speed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f189",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Before I even knew what was happening,[p/] it raised its fist to strike me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a45ce",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da62e0",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Flustered,[p/] I fell back and raised my arms to shield myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:005fed7",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "I closed my eyes,[p/] bracing for the impending impact."
}

{
  "id": "line:010c79f",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "...But instead,[p/] I heard the clang of steel striking stone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8dc43",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Confused,[p/] I opened my eyes to see Celeste standing between the Construct and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0ffd8",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Her sword was drawn,[p/] and it was locked with the Construct’s fist."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f65357",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Despite the Construct's imposing size and strength,[p/] Celeste was slowly pushing it back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b84cde",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Upon taking a closer look at Celeste,[p/] the girl narrowed her eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:035b131",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Construct.[p/] Stand down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f35d6e",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: I’m terribly sorry for that.[p/] I wasn’t aware that this man was your servant."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d4b87",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Celeste's hand was firmly clenched around the hilt of her sword,[p/] but she put it away without another word."
}

{
  "id": "line:085cf4e",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Miriam: I haven’t noticed you around campus.[p/] Are you a new student? [h=\"If the academy allowed her to bring her retainer,|she [i]must[/i] be important.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e072fc",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000444e",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "I saw an opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9585d",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Y-[p/][s/]Yes.[p/] My...[p/] master just enrolled here recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c05e7d",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Celeste squinted at me,[p/] confused.[p/] I just tilted my head towards Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4a9b",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Y-[p/][s/]Yes![p/] I just...[p/][s/] started here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f3047",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I take it [i]you’re[/i] Miriam Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060010a",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Yes.[p/] It seems that my reputation precedes me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7f58",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It is a pleasure to make your acquaintance, Lady..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab68a",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’m Celeste.[p/] Celeste M-"
}

{
  "id": "line:081d336",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "She caught herself,[p/] pausing for what was a very awkward moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b16b",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: MSsssteel...[p/][s/]wind![p/][s/] I’m Celeste Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8e1e0",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Was she serious?[p/][s/] There was no way Miriam was going to believe—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0429bae",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "MIRIAM: S-[p/][s/]Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08cfc60",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Um...[p/][s/] It’s a pleasure to meet another member of such an esteemed house! [h=\"She must be from a distant branch family...|Father may have a use for her...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e63408",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Wait...[p/][s/] She was actually buying this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:045888b",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] just moved in,[p/] and I thought that I should introduce myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4c76",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Seeing as you’re a top student in the field of [b]conjugation[b/]."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4d4e",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: [b]Conjuration[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65fd9",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0453e06",
  "node": "Dorm_Check",
  "text": "...Well,[p/] there was no backing out now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0570795",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "TYRION: Lady...[p/] Steelwind.[p/] I’m afraid we must leave now if we want to make our next engagement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5a8e9",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Oh,[p/][s/] right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0949bd2",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: Let’s go...[p/] servant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7a06",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "MIRIAM: Oh?[p/] Leaving already?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0790f60",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "MIRIAM: It was a pleasure talking to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0450abf",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah![p/][s/] Sure!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc106",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: See you around."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b18e4",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "I made my way back to the foyer with Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0662af3",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "With all the time we’d spent,[p/] we only had a brief amount of time before night fell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f06182",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "But luckily,[p/] we'd found a lot during our investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1d813",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "CELESTE: Are you sure you didn’t want to talk to her more?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbfbf8",
  "node": "DormEnd",
  "text": "CELESTE: We were getting a lot out of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5b978",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: We already got a lot of useful information out of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670090",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: The more time we spend with her,[p/] the more likely she is to see through our ruse and warn the prosecution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8bac9",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:013930b",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: So...[p/] Why “Steelwind”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2417d",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I don’t know![p/][s/] I panicked!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c1845",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I don't remember any of the other houses' names.."
}

{
  "id": "line:066ce8f",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: Pierce would've had a lower profile."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0c695",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’m not using that creep’s name!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0666175",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Hopefully,[p/] Steelwind doesn’t mind us “borrowing” her name."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e25b8",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: And we got her statement on what she saw that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f2ca1",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: There's also what she said about her rapier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a1eb",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I bet she was lying when she said it was stolen..."
}

{
  "id": "line:023eedc",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: She was probably trying to establish an alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef6afd",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m...[p/] not so sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f31583",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Why do you say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04624b5",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: Doesn’t it feel...[p/] too obvious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d2965",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: If she was lying about the rapier being stolen,[p/] that would imply that she planned all of this in advance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8fb74",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: But if she had to choose a murder weapon,[p/] why would she choose something that [i]literally[/i] has her family's name on it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080ff10",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: I’d understand if the murder was a spur-of-the-moment decision and somehow occurred in her dorm room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0368200",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: In a situation like that,[p/] she might've just used something nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa1322",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: But if this was a premeditated murder committed by Miriam,[p/] that rapier would be the [i]last[/i] weapon she would choose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb0647",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right...[p/] I guess that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:09250c7",
  "node": "DormEnd_1",
  "text": "TYRION: There’s also the “evidence” of academic dishonesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adc8a2",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: It doesn’t match up with what we heard from Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc2ab",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: You mean all that stuff about working with the Crown Prince?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8a4a",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: She was probably just making things up to look good in front of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0453b3a",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I have...[p/] an insight when it comes to things like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a2588",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Under certain circumstances,[p/] I can usually tell when someone is lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f44003",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I'd be able to see through a lie as grandiose as that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26674",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "People could subconsciously shield themselves from the Eye of Horus,[p/] even if they didn't know about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d48b97",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "But when they did that,[p/] I wouldn't be able to see [i]any[/i] thoughts from them."
}

{
  "id": "line:09171b4",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "I saw that she was lying about her encounter with Bellwether.[p/] I would’ve seen dissonant thoughts if she were lying about her grades, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ced958",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Well,[p/] I guess your insight has never failed us before,[p/] but what does this mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0334cde",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: ...I don’t know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d32868",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: Even with everything we’ve found,[p/] I’m still not sure who the real culprit is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db9b1e",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: At the very least,[p/] I think we should still try to pull Miriam onto the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d44196",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "TYRION: If she testifies in court,[p/] I might be able to find something I can use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2a0fd",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "But that was a big “maybe”.[p/] She was the daughter of the Duke of Finance."
}

{
  "id": "line:073470d",
  "node": "DormEnd_2",
  "text": "If I didn't play my cards right,[p/] that move could spook the judge enough to make him end the trial then and there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03431",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait, do we have time to kill?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e87ebe",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do you want to head back to the library?[p/] You could continue your research."
}

{
  "id": "line:0359944",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "She was fidgeting with her hands.[p/] Her feet were already shuffling toward the library doors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dedc91",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You just want to read [i]Dagger at Daggerfall[/i], don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8e1dc",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: It's [i]Death at Daggerfall[/i],[p/] and it's a great series!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a67c47",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Every time I try to pick one of those books up,[p/] I figure out who the killer is within the first few chapters."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef9e6",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah?[p/] Well, I'm a normal human being, okay?[p/] I'm not some murder-solving prodigy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78b29",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Why don't you go read one of those [i]Wraithbound[/i] books?"
}

{
  "id": "line:089a463",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe you'll find the unpublished sequel there, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:051f53c",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] that series has been finished for centuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:0259c51",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Wallace: The nobility paid Corrin Bloomveil to write stories about evil necromancers![p/][s/] He's a sellout!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04def7e",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Wallace: Liches are magically impossible,[p/] but people still just eat that nonsense up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d2f7f",
  "node": "DormEnd_3",
  "text": "Wallace: That man single-handedly threw the study of [b]necromancy[/b] back into the Stone Age!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b5613",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001e8d6",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't stop thinking about what Wallace said about Corrin Bloomviel."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ab330",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Look,[p/] I get that you really like that series,[p/] but they're just books, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4afc8",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're more than that to me.[p/] Those books inspired me to do what I'm doing now."
}

{
  "id": "line:00af226",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] The story about the magic light swords inspired you to become a defense attorney?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7d060",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: A long time ago,[p/] I experienced firsthand how corrupt Wyverngarde was.[p/] I started assuming that the nobles would always win."
}

{
  "id": "line:065b733",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But those books made me want to believe in a world where good could triumph over evil against all odds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6dd0a",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And if I'd never had that,[p/] I don't know if I'd be here today."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca907",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: I get that,[p/] but Wallace really cares a lot about [b]necromancy[/b] too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc8691",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: We've been [i]feeling[/i] the stigma against it for this entire case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fb01",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Is it really so hard to believe that those books contributed to how bad things are for him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0999a21",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: You've said it yourself.[p/] It's one of the most popular books out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6c893",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you even know what kind of person Corrin Bloomviel was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a1fe",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Not really."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c4295",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: So he [i]could[/i] have been paid off by the nobility to write those books."
}

{
  "id": "line:0177a64",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Someone who did that could never write something so beautiful."
}

{
  "id": "line:071e31f",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll grant you that it's likely he played into harmful stereotypes about necromancers,[p/] but I'm sure it was just an unfortunate mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a8868",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure there are historical records that will note his many good deeds and contributions to society."
}

{
  "id": "line:055b466",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe if I show Wallace that,[p/] he'll understand that he wasn't all that bad."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0cadf",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Sure, sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0341",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "I looked over to her.[p/] She was already shuffling towards the entrance of the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c479dd",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright, let's just go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc29b6",
  "node": "DormEnd_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Woohoo!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a96eea",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "She barely acknowledged me.[p/] She flung open the doors to the library and ran inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0074c5a",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "By the time I entered the library,[p/] she was already sitting at a table,[p/] her eyes glued to the unpublished manuscript."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cc8c4",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright,[p/] where to start...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4ff21",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ah, here we go.[p/] Corrin Bloomviel's autobiography."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb96d7",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] That hour flew by.[p/] I still couldn't finish—"
}

{
  "id": "line:008304c",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god...[p/] How many books did you get?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea3b2",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: HE WAS A STEELWIND, CELESTE!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07476f5",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: I—[p/][s/] What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0375c17",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: He wasn't just paid by the nobility![p/][s/] He was [i]of[/i] the nobility!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0220f42",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Was that in the historical records?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0638344",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: No![p/][s/] It's all one giant conspiracy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0316407",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I found his old submissions to writing competitions that he'd made under his original name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0987537",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prose he used back then matches his style too closely![p/][s/] It's uncanny when you compare them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:006eb55",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Some of these submissions even contained story elements that he later used and polished in [i]Wraithbound[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94f6f",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: How did you even—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead09c",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: His real name was Lorenzo Steelwind,[p/][s/] born in the year 208!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8fda",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: He deserted the army and was disowned by his family,[p/] but they paid him off, Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c95726",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: They saw that the masses liked his writing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbd5b7",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: They corrupted him![p/][s/] They used his artistry as a weapon to turn the public against the necromancers!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07912b2",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he just [i]went[/i] with it![p/] They dangled his inheritance in front of him like a carrot on a stick!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae190",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] what in the actual hell?[p/] We've only been here for an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f47bb",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] If I just had more time,[p/] I could find enough evidence to prove this once and for all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8c15a",
  "node": "DormEnd_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure if I can take a few more hours to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0583152",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] Tyrion, no!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6e92a",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Celeste: Wallace's trial is tomorrow morning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d61cd",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Scaled Lord,[p/][s/] how could I forget?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a7ad7",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Celeste: It's fine.[p/][s/] Let's just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3b931",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wallace will want to hear about what I found!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0136715",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Okay,[p/] whatever.[p/] Let's just go home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0477b19",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Naught could remain concealed, Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e9793",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Celeste: Sure, Tyrion.[p/] You did great.[p/] Good job."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d52d1",
  "node": "DormEnd_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Naught could remain concealed..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6ef8",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e8979",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know![p/] I wouldn't believe it if I hadn't seen all the pieces there myself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b40dd",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: That makes so much sense...[p/] The Steelwinds had always seen the necromancers as a threat to their power..."
}

{
  "id": "line:003a5cc",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Celeste: Guys?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb079b",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: But to think that Bloomviel was originally a part of their family..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0b812",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know, right?![p/] It's cruelly insane when you think about it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4633",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Celeste: Guys![p/][s/] Focus!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00478ba",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Celeste: Wallace is on trial for murder right now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ede2df",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f840b",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: Oh, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0623e0a",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/] I don't know what came over me."
}

{
  "id": "line:053454f",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: After I acquit you,[p/] do you want to talk more about what I found?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3df6",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Wallace: Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:083cd5d",
  "node": "DormEnd_7",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright,[p/] don't lose that confidence, I guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0108f0e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a893af",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "There was a steel door that led into the cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb7cc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "A magical mechanism covered by a steel box was placed over the lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:048248c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "They probably noticed that Celeste broke the lock last time she was here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01773b8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Torch"
}

{
  "id": "line:0722d8a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Lit torches were hanging on the cell walls.[p/] It seemed a bit irresponsible to light a fire in here."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b672b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "But prisoner safety was probably the last thing on the Inquisition’s mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a14826",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a272f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "The cell had a barred window.[p/] The bars were rusted."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e8aff",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "If a prisoner tried to escape,[p/] there would be a three-story drop to freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c49772",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce15f6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Alibi"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3509",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I-[p/][s/]I don’t understand..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb574",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I was with you in the library the entire time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01aea80",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: But why do they still think I’m the murderer? [h=\"It makes no sense...|unless.\" e=\"s\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0610fdf",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Y-[p/][s/]You told the Inquisition, right?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efe0fe",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Did you tell them that I was with you?! [h=\"Was I betrayed?!|Did they frame me?!\" e=\"sfa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09377af",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "He backed away from us,[p/] a look of suspicion on his face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0463072",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: W-[p/]We did,[p/] but they found traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3f50f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: They believe that Bellwether was murdered with a [b]necromancy[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:039ebbd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "He seemed to get even more tense,[p/] something I didn't think was possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbaa77",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Eris had mentioned that his studies were something he liked to keep to himself.[p/] I would need to be delicate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5a9a3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Necromancy"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fc900",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Wallace...[p/] We heard about the type of magic that you’re studying."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cd7c7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae10f3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: D-[p/][s/]Don’t worry![p/] The headmaster explained it to us already."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d75cfc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: You just want to use [b]necromancy[/b] to become a doctor, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b2fd3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think what you're doing is really respectable."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b5d84",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's nice to see a dark school of magic being used as a force for good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed09b1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d15b0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: You've got it all backwards! [h=\"It's because of [i]Wraithbound[/i]!|Those stupid books!\" e=\"a\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:004ec03",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "For the first time,[p/] I saw some genuine rage from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:017ab33",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: Real [b]necromancy[/b] has [i]always[/i] been about healing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99470",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: But because of garbage like [i]Wraithbound[/i],[p/] the public keeps calling for [b]necromancy[/b] to be outlawed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:029ebc8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I think calling it \"garbage\" may be a bit much..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2582",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: The nobility paid Corrin Bloomveil to write stories about evil necromancers![p/][s/] He was such a sellout!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3af49",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: Liches are magically impossible,[p/] but people still just believe that nonsense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07723da",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "I had to temper myself.[p/] He was clearly passionate about this,[p/] but I'll admit it stung to hear him talk about my favorite book like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab2547",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Maybe we should talk about something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f207cd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Spell Compendium"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4153",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...I understand that you have reservations about talking about your magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d119ae",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: But in order to build a case for you,[p/] we'll need to PRESENT your [b]Spell Compendium[/b] to the courts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51acc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I-[p/]I...[p/] don’t have one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067029",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Eris already told us about that.[p/] That's why she gave us a blank one for you to attune to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a21c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: ...D-[p/]Do I have to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd112a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: It would be extremely difficult to defend you without your Compendium.[p/] It's a core piece of evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:036c346",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2f85e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: O-[p/]Okay...[p/] I’ll attune to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce742c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "I understood why he was studying this type of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0725d0b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...But the spells in his [b]Compendium[/b] sounded fairly gruesome."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f833fb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "It was a little terrifying to know that spells like this even existed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d14dc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Sorry...[p/] A long time ago,[p/] I showed my [i]Compendium[/i] to someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb48e7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: After she saw my [b]necromancy[/b] spells,[p/] she told everyone in the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:049e19f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: That’s when Professor Bellwether started coming after me."
}

{
  "id": "line:034e496",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...That must have been difficult for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ea0c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: After that,[p/] I didn't really talk to anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:02feecb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb4cc4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: Yeah,[p/] I guess Eris was there too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad08d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "It seemed like it was a difficult time for him.[p/] No wonder he had so much trouble remembering."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c03758",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...Something similar happened to me after I left my hometown."
}

{
  "id": "line:095eaa1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Wallace and Eris"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d1d7d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: How did you and Eris become friends anyway? [h=\"Who [i]is[/i] she?|There's something off about her...\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1754f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "There was [i]another[/i] hint of fear from her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfab6e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] Sometimes the other students would steal the id number off my locker and switch it with another student's."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66ac2",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: They thought it was funny whenever that student got angry with me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:064a098",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Eris had a bit of a reputation around our school."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3c9ab",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Everyone was scared of her,[p/] even the students from the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc4fe",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Probably due to some baseless rumors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f08a71",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: One day,[p/] someone switched my id number with hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c53d4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I was so scared when she came up to me.[p/] I couldn’t even say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0b2a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: But she didn’t get angry like the others."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ed41",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: She just apologized and gave me back my nameplate."
}

{
  "id": "line:07caa6a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: After that,[p/] she started talking to me whenever she saw me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08ed6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: So...[p/] I have to ask..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01958d6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: If it’s caused you so much trouble,[p/] why are you still studying [b]necromancy[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0ffc9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I want to become a doctor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a099b6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: The headmaster told us the same thing,[p/] but why are you learning spells that can steal people’s life force and raise the undead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b83774",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Life and death are two sides of the same coin."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ce958",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: That’s the key principle behind [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aaca5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: The first undead was actually a failed attempt to resurrect a human using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:074e1b5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: Right now,[p/] [b]necromancy[/b] can only heal injuries and wounds,[p/] but it can’t do anything for diseases or deformities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7d727",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: If I could just keep studying,[p/] I [i]know[/i] I can develop [b]necromancy[/b] beyond that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c624b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I might even be able to create spells that can cure terminal diseases."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fb2d0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Catherine Bellwether"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f50731",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I think I can already guess,[p/] but how was your relationship with Catherine Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093c07e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: After word got out about my spells,[p/] Professor Bellwether would always find reasons to punish me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00409c8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: She’d start yelling at me for even the smallest mistakes."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dc115",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Wallace: It was pretty obvious she had it out for the students who didn't come from the noble families."
}

{
  "id": "line:01054ba",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: That’s terrible..."
}

{
  "id": "line:031d075",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I’d wake up each day,[p/] scared that she’d notice me in the hallways."
}

{
  "id": "line:02756b1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I knew how to avoid her and stay out of her way,[p/] but sometimes,[p/] she’d get bored and come looking for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:063fc30",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I can’t believe that after everything that she did,[p/] she’s just gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:053a57d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I'm sure you have mixed emotions about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:046c4bb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: I honestly don’t know [i]how[/i] I feel about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c3759",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: To be honest,[p/] I always wished she would just disappear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0687091",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "WALLACE: But now that it’s finally happened,[p/] I just feel even [i]more[/i] scared. [h=\"It feels like she’s going to|come back as a ghost to haunt me.\" e=\"fsa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0311396",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: What's this?[p/] Is it some kind of artificery?"
}

{
  "id": "line:081d299",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe026",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s fitted with artificery.[p/][s/] I can use it to take pictures of evidence and crime scenes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07209b1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Oh...[p/] I've seen some of the richer students using things like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c95ba6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry about him.[p/] He shows that thing to everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd3735",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I just think it's neat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0125b35",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: I know I shouldn't be asking this, but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01695f4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a11718",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Why are you helping me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08862fc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: I...[p/] don't have enough gold to pay you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa36d7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's because we know that you're innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:007ffe3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...Is that seriously the only reason?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0590149",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I became a defense attorney to help mages who are persecuted by the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f270d8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know how much our society mistreats the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c9399",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I want to alleviate that,[p/] even if it's just a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7d447",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a0876",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "He still looked like he didn't fully believe me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aec279",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: I wish I could be like you, Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e78988",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009a017",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: You look so reliable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec80a9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: I wish I could even be half as confident as you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e92bf",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't worry.[p/] I'm sure you'll get there one day."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ab670",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...I don't know about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05553b8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You seem to be good friends with Eris,[p/] despite your reputation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a69498",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Yeah...[p/] I have no idea why she spends time with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ce959",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry...[p/] I wasn't trying to imply-"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2941b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: No.[p/] I get it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dfe52",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it sounds like everyone at the academy is scared of her, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0788f37",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe she understands your situation better than anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:00da01b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Hm...[p/] Maybe..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f50413",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherine|Catherine Autopsy"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd5c1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: I still can't believe the professor is actually dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8da0b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] We just saw her this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:099018e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...It just doesn't feel real."
}

{
  "id": "line:085cd75",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Player: Valentina|Valerie|Discover"
}

{
  "id": "line:08306a5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know the twins who work in the Academy Kitchen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27b9b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Not personally.[p/] I only ever saw them when I went to get food in the cafeteria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab364",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...But I could tell that they were both scared of me, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:015e040",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: They always did their best to avoid talking to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d2a89",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Sometimes they'd give me extra food..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0855e19",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You seem to have a good relationship with the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0161de3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: He said that you were one of his star students."
}

{
  "id": "line:029d091",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: ...Really?[p/] He said that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5567",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: The only reason why I'm even allowed to attend the Academy is because of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0718b58",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02711e3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: He's running a scholarship program for mages born outside of the noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ef074",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Usually,[p/] only nobles can afford to attend the Imperial Academy,[p/] but he's allowed mages born through the commonfolk to enroll there for free."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d22ee3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Player: Wallace|WallComp"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a382c8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've met a lot of mages in my time,[p/] but I've never met a necromancer before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e43720",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] And you're not exactly what I was expecting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dba9d7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Sorry for disappointing you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027737e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]That’s not what I meant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75341",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93ed9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Wallace: Sorry...[p/] I can't tell you much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e37c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I looked around the dungeon,[p/] but I didn't see Wallace in any of the cells."
}

{
  "id": "line:083bf34",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: The Inquisition is probably still questioning him."
}

{
  "id": "line:09571db",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: We should come back later."
}

{
  "id": "line:04401d9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "As we arrived at the Ratholme Dungeons,[p/] I spotted Wallace locked in one of the nearby cells."
}

{
  "id": "line:08318c6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "...He was lying on the floor,[p/] muttering to himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd3c4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: It’s over...[p/] My life is over..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec96bb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Um...[p/] Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:012fbcf",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: Eep![p/][s/] Who are you?![p/][s/] What do you want?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d2b87",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wallace.[p/] It’s us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f996cc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: O-[p/]Oh...[p/] right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:093920b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: How are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04206d1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Apparently,[p/] not well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e701d0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: Please tell me you’re going to get me out of here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2722c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: I-[p/][s/]I keep telling them that I didn't do it,[p/] but they won't listen!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40f15",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I'm sorry, Wallace, but...[p/] they found traces of [b]necromancy[/b] magic on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c758e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: They’re convinced that you did this,[p/] and they're going to push your case to trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898df9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: W-[p/][s/]What?! [h=\"No!|Are they going to execute me?!\" e=\"sf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08934a6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: T-[p/]This—[p/][s/] This can’t be happening! [h=\"Are the walls moving?!|Are they closing in?!\" e=\"sf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:074988d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: ... [h=\"I can’t...|I can’t breathe!\" e=\"fs\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a64c3a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: P-[p/][s/]Please calm down!"
}

{
  "id": "line:086fe50",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wallace, we know that you’re innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0350940",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Wallace: But those [i]knights[/i] think I did this...[p/] Are they going to kill me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055d776",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I've spent my entire life learning how to deal with situations like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:053a3a7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you let me represent you in court,[p/] I can prove that you're innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bcf6e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: O-[p/]Oh, right...[p/] You said that you were a lawyer..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50c6e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: ...B-[p/][s/]But,[p/] I don’t really have any money to pay you with."
}

{
  "id": "line:02968fa",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Don’t worry about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0195a3b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: For now,[p/] let’s just focus on getting you acquitted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46243",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: W-[p/][s/]What...? [h=\"Do they seriously|want to help me...?\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:063881b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: ... [h=\"No...|They must want something from me...\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbb427",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: ...Well, I guess it doesn’t matter anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e7a34",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "WALLACE: It’s not like I have anything else to lose."
}

{
  "id": "line:089c7cc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "That wasn't exactly the reaction I was hoping for,[p/] but at least he was cooperating..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a981e",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Hm...[p/] I think I’m starting to put things together now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:046f42f",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "CELESTE: Have you figured something out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0806e64",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Yeah...[p/] I need a moment to think through everything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03928b0",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution wants to implicate Wallace despite his alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd9e9",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: They wouldn’t have a reason to do this unless the evidence heavily implicated him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0758a54",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: We’ve learned that Wallace is a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0298727",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: And he’s the only person at the academy that’s capable of high-level [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:08129e0",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce2",
  "text": "Player: Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:077f48c",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Wallace was the only person who studied high-level [b]necromancy[/b] at the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0937fd8",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce2",
  "text": "And there was a piece of evidence at the crime scene that painted him as a suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ce9a2",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb2d12",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: This means that they think Wallace used one of his [b]necromancy[/b] spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1109b",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Celeste: Even without seeing the traces,[p/] it’s pretty obvious that magic was used on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:000280b",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right.[p/] There aren’t any wounds on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0090",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And the Autopsy Report found no signs of poison or disease."
}

{
  "id": "line:09afdf0",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I know Prosecutor Steelwind,[p/] she probably already has a theory on which spell he might have used."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bc3f6",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution will probably argue that Wallace used one of his spells to kill Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:04418c0",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce4",
  "text": "0"
}

{
  "id": "line:052f29e",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Despite his reasons,[p/] Wallace knew how to use some disturbing spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0e52c",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce4",
  "text": "I needed to check my NOTES and read the description of each spell Wallace could use."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eb5f4",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce4",
  "text": "The body had no visible wounds or bruises."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9a65",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce4",
  "text": "Which spell could harm Bellwether without wounding or bruising her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f05e32",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "Tyrion: They will probably say that he used [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0374957",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "CELESTE: That makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ac755",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Necrotic Blight[/b] would have “drained the lifeforce from her body”..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c32dc0",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: But that’s where the contradiction lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9a193",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: Let’s suppose that Wallace [i]did[/i] kill Bellwether using [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:068c944",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: There’s something at the crime scene that wouldn’t be there if that were true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a38c9d",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce6",
  "text": "No...[p/] Steelwind would probably argue that Wallace used [b]Necrotic Blight[b/]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d3a04",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce6",
  "text": "But if that really [i]did[/i] happen,[p/] there was something on the body that [i]shouldn't[/i] be there."
}

{
  "id": "line:097da0e",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Necrotic Blight[/b] is a spell that doesn’t inflict any visible wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1ae5",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if that's true,[p/] there shouldn’t have been any blood at the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513ae2",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...But then what really happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0534cdd",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: [i]That’s[/i] the last piece."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9b410",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: And if I had to guess,[p/] the information we need is being hidden by one of the witnesses who discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:013aa51",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "CELESTE: Valentina..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b1166",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: She’s definitely hiding something."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f7778",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you notice how she reacted when I asked you to scan the room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:005d470",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "CELESTE: Yeah,[p/] she ran away.[p/] She didn’t even try to be subtle about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd14b4",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: With the way she reacted,[p/] I think she may have been trying to hide herself from your [b]Detect Magic[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2579e",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which can only mean that there's a magical trace on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:016ba04",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder what she's trying to hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:060a25c",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one way to find out."
}

{
  "id": "line:023fbd2",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The next time you see her,[p/] can you cast [b]Detect Magic[/b] from afar and scan her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f59ab",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: It's been a while since we talked to her.[p/] Valerie also mentioned that they still had work to do today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0496452",
  "node": "WallaceDeduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: She might be back in the Academy's Kitchen now."
}

{
  "id": "line:057c425",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "Player: 2-B"
}

{
  "id": "line:0879b66",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "This was Lecture Hall 2-B,[p/] where Bellwether's body was found."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bbf80",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "Player: 2-D"
}

{
  "id": "line:036d52d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "This was Lecture Hall 2-D."
}

{
  "id": "line:069b2f2",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "Player: 2-F"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f83e3b",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "This was Lecture Hall 2-F."
}

{
  "id": "line:040d3ff",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "Player: 2-H"
}

{
  "id": "line:048ca7e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "This was Lecture Hall 2-H."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89091",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Closet"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ac2ff",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "It appeared to be some kind of storage closet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0665966",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Examine",
  "text": "There wasn't anything of note inside of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:018609b",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Jan Hughes"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cba1f4",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Valerie mentioned that you were close to Lecture Hall 2-B before they found Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0995d05",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What were you doing when the twins discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0620fe5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: You might have been the last person to see her alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0306e6f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you see where she went after breaking the vase?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027a94d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Yeah,[p/] I think she went into that room over there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c37b25",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "Jan pointed towards Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb10bb",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you see anyone else enter the lecture hall?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091a140",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I’m honestly not sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d42c7",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I was more worried about cleaning up the mess she made."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a42d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Well...[p/] Did you notice anything off about her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a6fb",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: She [i]was[/i] in a pretty bad mood."
}

{
  "id": "line:016cb82",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: But honestly,[p/] that’s pretty normal for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ecd1",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: She was walking really slowly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea47e8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I didn’t notice her at first.[p/] She basically shoved me out of her way."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f64f1",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: After that,[p/] she knocked over that vase."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4a8b",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Then she yelled at me to \"Be quiet\".[p/] I didn't even say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:077cd1c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What can you tell me about Catherine Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02664d7",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I've heard that she had a pretty bad relationship with the staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e271c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: She had a “bad relationship” with everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4dcaa",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Students,[p/] the other teachers,[p/] I can’t think of many people who actually [i]did[/i] get along with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:01066e3",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m sure you had your own share of bad experiences with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a825f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Yeah...[p/] She’d always yell at me whenever I dozed off."
}

{
  "id": "line:001237e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I hate to say it,[p/] but things are a [i]lot[/i] more peaceful around here without her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8e752",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "That was blunt,[p/] to say the least..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b7ff",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "But from what I'd heard from everyone else,[p/] I couldn't exactly blame him for thinking that."
}

{
  "id": "line:072444a",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Firing the academy staff"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed73d5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Valentina...[p/] [i]mentioned[/i] something interesting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db2ed8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: She seems to think Bellwether was putting her job at risk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b5aa",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Oh, yeah...[p/] Bellwether was putting [i]all[/i] of our jobs at risk."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5cfe",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What made you think that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2af4e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: You know those Arcane Constructs in the library?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ac545",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Bellwether was the one who put them there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c633c9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh, yeah![p/][s/] They’re so cool!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05693fe",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Well,[p/] a few weeks ago,[p/] I peeked in on a meeting she was having with Theodore."
}

{
  "id": "line:001b340",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Apparently,[p/] the school board was planning to replace the staff with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5b43f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: O-[p/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0572cf7",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Well, I’m sure the headmaster rejected her proposal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0041633",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: I don’t know...[p/] From the way she was talking,[p/] it sounded like he didn’t have any say in the matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0735a07",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: But only the headmaster should have the authority to fire the staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ea236",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Why would she be that confident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0669cfa",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "JAN: Dunno.[p/] All I know is that she hated having commoners on campus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c39137",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Talk",
  "text": "Jan: She was really miffed when Theodore started hiring commonfolk from the community center."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e996",
  "node": "HallJanJan",
  "text": "TYRION: So, Jan.[p/] Are you a part of the staff here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023f77c",
  "node": "HallJanJan",
  "text": "JAN: Yep...[p/] I’m a janitor..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6c95",
  "node": "HallJanJan",
  "text": "JAN: I clean...[p/] and I do odd jobs here and there..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b5f76",
  "node": "HallJanJan",
  "text": "Well...[p/] Apparently, that’s all he had to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0678e36",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: What's that thing?[p/] Is it a rock?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85ec9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d2eb2",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Jan?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060ec66",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Oh![p/][s/] Sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:057871c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I dozed off there for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:042f14e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Player: Jan"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd9ce6",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you aware of the foul smell in Lecture Hall 2-B?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b67267",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0868d1d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Luckily,[p/] Aria isn't letting anyone into the lecture hall until the investigation's over."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c472f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: ...But,[p/] I'll probably have to get to it eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:003f7ac",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Alchemical messes are always such a pain to clean up."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c063c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I wonder if Aria can help me out like she used to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3b907",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Do you know Prosecutor Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093b3e9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: She went here a few years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:01db1b1",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: She'd always help me out using her magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:048964c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I miss that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:073b6e9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Man...[p/] I still can't believe someone killed Bellwether.[p/] It's unreal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b30ad0",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure you have mixed feelings about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af84e6",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah...[p/] I feel like I [i]should[/i] be happy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3faf",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: But honestly,[p/] I don't know [i]what[/i] to feel."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cd5ac",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: It's easier not to think about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b5c0f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Player: Discover|Valentina|Valerie"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f39e8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you friends with the Ianus sisters?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4efd5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah,[p/] us commoners got to stick together, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184b69",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I don't know if you got a chance to try it,[p/] but their food is amazing."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f5905",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Valerie always saves food for me.[p/] So I pay that back by washing their dishes when I have time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4782b",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess there's always give and take in a place like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0379389",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah,[p/] we even shared notes to figure out Bellwether's schedule."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b5633",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: That made it a lot easier to avoid her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bcd14",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Bellwether was kind of a menace here, wasn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2117",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Player: Theodore|Head Action"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fb5d4",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: How is working under Headmaster Redmond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008034f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: It's great."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3535",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I owe a lot to him for getting me this job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4848d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: But I suppose these things never last."
}

{
  "id": "line:094c7d8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "He must be talking about Bellwether's plan to fire the staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa5da",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "What could he mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c124e5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Player: JanTest|JanTest2"
}

{
  "id": "line:022232c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just want to go over your statement again, Jan."
}

{
  "id": "line:081054f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you sure you didn't leave out any details?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02a93",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I'm pretty sure,[p/] but I wasn't paying that much attention."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d0419",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I definitely didn't think the workday would end with a murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:012df20",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Player: BellPlan|BellPlan2|Construct"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdf1e9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Ugh...[p/] I just really hope we don't lose our jobs to those Constructs."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f13f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, if there's any silver lining to Bellwether's death,[p/] it's that she can't carry out her plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8b38e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Damn...[p/] That's kind of heartless, man."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f375c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...While I [i]do[/i] want to catch the real murderer,[p/] I don't have much pity for people who abuse positions of power."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db49f8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Well...[p/] I can't blame you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b0503",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I'm sure many people feel the same way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a249ef",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Right...[p/] Valentina mentioned something similar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0add900",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "I wonder what he meant by that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b8a8a",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you met Prosecutor Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ff0ca",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Not recently,[p/] but she used to go to school here a few years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b891c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What was she like back then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1d2a3",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Oh, she was great."
}

{
  "id": "line:031b27e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: She'd always reprimand Bellwether when she'd pick on the students and staff."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a29746",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: She's a Steelwind,[p/] so she was probably the only person in this school that could stand up to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aa5e4",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: The students elected her as the student-body president,[p/] and she took that job pretty seriously."
}

{
  "id": "line:011ddd5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Things were a lot better when she was here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00924bb",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: I don't care what people say,[p/] she was so much better than Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0007a1a",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Mr. Hughes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:098d695",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: Ugh...[p/] I don't know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5068",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "Jan: That's not my department."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbb5b8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Present",
  "text": "He wasn't being very helpful..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57eb4",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "I spotted Valentina again.[p/] She was speaking to someone in a blue-collar uniform."
}

{
  "id": "line:0592d23",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "I'd only met her briefly in the kitchen,[p/] but there was something[p/] different about her posture."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3ce73",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "And then there was the man in the uniform.[p/] Could he be the custodian that she mentioned?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e96fab",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "As I approached,[p/] I noticed he was slouched over.[p/] He barely looked awake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b29204",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Even while speaking to Valentina,[p/] he was sweeping the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:090e7a3",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "However,[p/] his movements looked robotic.[p/] He was just going through the motions without any awareness."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e7f96",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Valerie: Jan,[p/] I know you're tired."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e151c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Valerie: But we really need you to fix the plumbing in the kitchen sinks."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd192",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Jan: Ugh...[p/] Someone just died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0887cee",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Jan: Can’t we take the day off for [i]once[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06147fe",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Valerie: I'm sorry,[p/] but Valentina and I still need to cook for the students."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cfe96",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] Why was Valentina suddenly speaking in the third person?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f97db",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Valerie: Oh?[p/] Hello."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a021a8",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Valentina?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0192e33",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Valerie: Oh, my apologies.[p/] I’m not Valentina.[p/] I’m her sister: Valerie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc8e86",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Are you trying to trick us or something?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c90c43",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: You look exactly the same!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf414",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "I remembered reading about something like this before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b69db0",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: You two are identical twins, aren’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e42b49",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: Yes,[p/] that's correct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0881284",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] This meant that [i]she[/i] was the one who discovered the body alongside Valentina."
}

{
  "id": "line:052ac18",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Since we have you here,[p/] do you mind if I ask you some questions about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022b1e9",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: U-[p/]Um...[p/] I’m terribly sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:063155a",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: But I’ve already spent a lot of time looking for Jan here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d0e93",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: I’m really behind on my work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0967f00",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: But...[p/] [i]Jan[/i] was also nearby when we discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0104556",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "VALERIE: I’m sure he can answer your questions!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077e094",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Before I had a chance to object,[p/] Valerie quickly walked away."
}

{
  "id": "line:021cd2f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Do you want me to go after her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0126506",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’m pretty sure I can catch up to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0351b54",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: No...[p/] We don’t want to scare those two more than we already have."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cfdd5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] Valerie said that Jan was nearby when the murder happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b8a7",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Maybe he saw something they didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0821cd4",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Jan, was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7368f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you mind if we ask you some questions about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8da44",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "JAN: Ugh...[p/] Really...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb46fc",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "JAN: Well, whatever."
}

{
  "id": "line:0239bc2",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Jan: At least I have an excuse to take a break now."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d0af3",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, thank you for answering our questions, Jan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1dbae",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Jan: Sure, anytime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d06a7f",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: We still don't have any leads on other suspects.[p/] It's just a lot of people who saw and/or hated Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:00598b0",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Right...[p/] If it wasn't Wallace,[p/] it still could have been any other mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b0e08",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: The trial is coming up soon.[p/] We still don't know why there are traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:071bc2d",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on,[p/] don't be like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eff687",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: You always get to the truth in the end."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25057",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] it's only been one time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0522aa6",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: And after we acquit Wallace,[p/] it's going to be a grand total of [i]two[/i] times."
}

{
  "id": "line:0528605",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: It doesn't matter who tries to stop us—[p/]man,[p/] king,[p/] or god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e238e5",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "I couldn't help but chuckle to myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:008251e",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay, okay.[p/] I guess we still need to talk to Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:043a333",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's head to the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:092d29c",
  "node": "AcademyHall_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: See?[p/] There we go."
}

{
  "id": "line:050b919",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Painting 1"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c6118",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of someone.[p/] He looks like some sort of professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c1303",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: That's Professor Lukas Gilbert.[p/] He was an instructor here many decades ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:080a24d",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: He was quite the accomplished scholar,[p/] and well-beloved by the students here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b69f02",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: And this was all despite his lack of magical ability."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cc966",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: He studied magic without actually being able to use it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0462",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: Yes.[p/] He was quite remarkable."
}

{
  "id": "line:07617e7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: ...Unfortunately,[p/] we lost him to illness very early in his career."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2caa",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Painting 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0715dbe",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a mage...[p/] But he doesn't quite look like a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f29a05",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: Oh. That's Jason Steelwind.[p/] One of the chosen mages of the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e66900",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] \"Steelwind\"?[p/] As in-"
}

{
  "id": "line:097115e",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: Yes.[p/] He's the earliest recorded ancestor of House Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:03557f7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: Legends say that the Scaled Lord bestowed his power upon him and his allies to create the first mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:01031ff",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow...[p/] It's hard to even tell that he and the prosecutor belong to the same bloodline."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2ad18",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: As with all the noble houses,[p/] House Steelwind had quite humble beginnings."
}

{
  "id": "line:09301ed",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "If only they'd remember where they came from..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d72056",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Fireplace"
}

{
  "id": "line:09636d5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a fireplace with some burning wood."
}

{
  "id": "line:006f48d",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It looks pretty cozy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0095c34",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Chandalier"
}

{
  "id": "line:092aada",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a fancy-looking chandelier."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b70f8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a window with a view of a garden."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8929",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: The headmaster has a nice view from up here."
}

{
  "id": "line:08efb5e",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a small table for guests."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfa289",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that...[p/] wine?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfdf00",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: No, actually.[p/] It's just apple juice."
}

{
  "id": "line:052e26f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Examine",
  "text": "Theodore: Most of my guests [i]are[/i] students after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:026e60b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: This is terrible."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ba19b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: To think that one of my prized students would be accused of murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0567d75",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: We heard your voice on the intercom when the lockdown happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c792b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Are you the one who triggered it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df33f8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: Y-[p/][s/]Yes.[p/] I activated it when I received the call from Valentina."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2f975",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: She reported that Professor Bellwether was collapsed and unresponsive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0566bf1",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: How does the lockdown system work?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0951247",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: It’s an artificery network that's built into the walls of the entire academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05db327",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: In the event of an emergency,[p/] I can activate it using this stone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a33dcd",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "The headmaster pulled out a glowing stone from his desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a43dd5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "I could hear the hum of magical energy emanating from it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0943af2",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: Once activated,[p/] the system creates magical barriers throughout the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0187402",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: It’s designed to contain and protect each room in the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b532c",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Could a powerful mage breach any of these barriers?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058e529",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: I doubt it.[p/] The barriers can withstand a great amount of force."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cf860",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: They even block mages from teleporting through them."
}

{
  "id": "line:041f8a6",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: And once activated,[p/] even [i]I[/i] can’t turn it off for an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd8ed",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Wallace Nightgrave"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f36f7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Wallace's Spell Compendium"
}

{
  "id": "line:03104c8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: If you plan on defending Wallace,[p/] will you need his [b]Spell Compendium[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad6c5d",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Yes.[p/] Having a client’s [b]Compendium[/b] is instrumental to acquitting them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bde0e",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: You may find that a bit...[p/] difficult."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d1f05",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: After a certain incident,[p/] he destroyed his [b]Compendium[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be0e3f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What?[p/] Why would he do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034eb35",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Doesn’t he need it to cast his magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090a20b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: A [b]Spell Compendium[/b] is a device we use to keep track of what spells we can cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e21924",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: It’s really convenient for remembering the formulas and incantations of my spells, but it’s not actually [i]required[/i] to use magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:02eb4f5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...I thought of getting rid of mine a long time ago,[p/] but they’re really expensive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdce08",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: Luckily,[p/] I have an unattuned [b]Spell Compendium[/b] right here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e61d9",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Eris: I’d be more than happy to give it to you if it helps Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b638e7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Thanks!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d94a3b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Wallace just needs to maintain physical contact with it for ten minutes."
}

{
  "id": "line:04de206",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: After that,[p/] the [b]Compendium[/b] will attune to his magic and update in real time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0093f63",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Just make sure that you don’t let another mage like Celeste hold it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf82f5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "ERIS: Once it attunes to a mage,[p/] no one else can use it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b6fc2",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Theodore: Wait,[p/] then how did[p/][p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deda81",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: Wonderful.[p/] I just hope you can persuade Wallace to attune to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3791f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Meeting"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f00878",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that you had a meeting scheduled with Professor Bellwether this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:080b464",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What time was this?[p/] And when did the meeting end?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001248d",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: Our meeting was scheduled for noon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a94165",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: She arrived on time,[p/] and our meeting lasted until 1:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0661e66",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Did anything seem off about her to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee6d04",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: No.[p/] She seemed to be her usual self. [h=\"Her usual insufferable self...\" e=\"sfa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c33af0",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...If you don’t mind me asking,[p/] what was the purpose of your meeting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072fcf5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: We met to discuss routine administrative matters."
}

{
  "id": "line:01335fc",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: Despite our personal disagreements,[p/] we knew to stay civil when discussing professional affairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f04e2",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...But to be perfectly honest,[p/] it [i]did[/i] always feel like I was treading on eggshells when speaking with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02202fd",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you were her superior,[p/] weren’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08da9e2",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Didn’t she respect your authority?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0200613",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: We had many arguments about how I was managing the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:003ab77",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: And she was very vocal about her distaste for the students accepted through my scholarship program."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f276f0",
  "node": "Headmaster_Talk",
  "text": "THEODORE: She was...[p/] difficult,[p/] to say the least."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b07fd",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: What can you tell me about Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e8296",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: Earlier,[p/] you said that he was one of your prized students."
}

{
  "id": "line:0986f35",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We also heard that he's a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e91ed",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: I just need to understand if that's really true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0e050",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] You are correct.[p/] Young Wallace is a necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:027b6fb",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: What?![p/][s/] But why would he study something like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7443f",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: [b]Necromancy[/b] is probably one of the most dangerous and most scrutinized schools of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f514e",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: Its image has been tainted by myths of dark wizards raising armies of the undead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed04e5",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: However,[p/] it doesn’t just control the forces of death.[p/] It can also control the forces of life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caf399",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: \"Forces of life”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04658eb",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: The truth is that healing magic is also classified as [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f349e",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: Most healers don’t care to admit it because of the stigma it has,[p/] but that’s why Wallace is studying it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbd037",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "Theodore: He wishes to become a doctor."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d7566",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: But there are plenty of mages who know healing magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1dde",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: Why is Wallace being singled out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3fd2",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: For years,[p/] he’s been studying [b]necromancy[/b] beyond the basic healing spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5fcd",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: He believes that high-level [b]necromancy[/b] could revolutionize modern medicine."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2e7f",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...Unfortunately,[p/] many among the faculty don’t see it that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b05063",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: Wallace doesn’t hail from any of the noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac47cf",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: He was abandoned by his parents at an orphanage—[p/]presumably to avoid a scandal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e29ca8",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: He’s like me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7009e",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: Many of the faculty fear that he’ll use his knowledge to raise armies of undead,[p/] just like the necromancers of fiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfa13b",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: The Imperial Academy isn’t even [i]permitted[/i] to teach it to students beyond basic healing magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:071b044",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why did [i]you[/i] allow him to study it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01da515",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: After everything that has happened to him,[p/] I made an exception,[p/] even if I [i]was[/i] breaking the law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cee327",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: ...What happened to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffb012",
  "node": "Wall_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: ...I’m not at liberty to say more."
}

{
  "id": "line:090b7f6",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: ... [h=\"Nothing [i]kind[/i]...|I can tell you that much...\" e=\"saf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09632d4",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "Wow,[p/] that was a whole mess of emotions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59ec3",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: Truth be told,[p/] she was rather...[p/] unpleasant to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b6b16",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: Can you think of any enemies she might have had?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd511f",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: You might as well list anyone who didn't hail from the Four Pillar Families."
}

{
  "id": "line:0247af7",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: E-[p/]Eris..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ced2c",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: It's best not to beat around the bush with these sorts of things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0466b4b",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: As I'm sure you saw this morning,[p/] [i]asphalt[/i] was probably less abrasive than her personality."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec2add",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: Many people in this school did [i]not[/i] care for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:084e732",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: Maybe she wasn’t the nicest person,[p/] but would that really be enough to motivate someone to murder her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2827",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: She’d often target and harass students,[p/] especially those who were commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:058fd69",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: She even made a habit of expelling those students for the smallest infractions."
}

{
  "id": "line:039e04e",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: For commoners,[p/] magic can be our ticket out of poverty."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f017",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: I can’t imagine how it’d feel to have that opportunity unfairly ripped away from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0791980",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: She was akin to a grim reaper,[p/] hanging over the student body,[p/] waiting to steal away their futures."
}

{
  "id": "line:023796a",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "ERIS: The human psyche can only be pushed so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ce204",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "TYRION: What about her relationship with the faculty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063c856",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: In some cases,[p/] it was worse than it was with the students."
}

{
  "id": "line:04765c5",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: She’d often treat the staff like her personal servants."
}

{
  "id": "line:0218f7c",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: I’ve received many complaints from them about her behavior,[p/] but I was powerless to stop her."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e51e",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "CELESTE: But how?[p/] I thought you were the headmaster."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f6a0f",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: She's a close friend of the Duke of Finance.[p/] She’s used her position to curry favor with the noble houses over the years."
}

{
  "id": "line:053a645",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: As you can imagine,[p/] the academy’s board is controlled by the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a47cf8",
  "node": "Cath_Conv",
  "text": "THEODORE: If I ever tried to remove her,[p/] there would be dire consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa674",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Ah,[p/] a Runestone.[p/] You have one too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b86b54",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's one specifically created for attorneys.[p/] It lets me take pictures of evidence and crime scenes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05781f7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I never really understood the appeal of those contraptions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8cdfa",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/][s/] They're really convenient."
}

{
  "id": "line:085ddb1",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: ...I just could never wrap my head around how to use them."
}

{
  "id": "line:030ecd7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: They're just not for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02806e8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I'm sorry that your first visit to the academy ended so tragically, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b7934",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's no need to apologize.[p/] No one could have guessed that today would turn out like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae9958",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Nevertheless,[p/] I hope you found our resources useful for your research."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f554d6",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I'd [i]heard[/i] that Ms. Tymora had recently hired a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaedd5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I hope that you found our resources useful for your studies."
}

{
  "id": "line:041e37f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, definitely.[p/] I was able to learn a lot of spells today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7553f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: \"Spells\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e08839",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Why did everyone react like that?[p/] Was learning multiple spells [i]not[/i] normal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:047b292",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Anyways,[p/] I'm glad you enjoyed using our Library."
}

{
  "id": "line:07214f5",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Our academy [i]does[/i] offer scholarships for mages of the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:047789a",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Would you be interested in enrolling here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0300657",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: No offense,[p/] but I just [i]can't[/i] stand the idea of being cooped up in a school like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05752fa",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I like learning about magic in the field."
}

{
  "id": "line:0726781",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Ah...[p/] That's unfortunate..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04de71e",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you met the prosecutor, Mr. Redmond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac27d0",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Ah.[p/] I am already well acquainted with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4ce3f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: She was once a student here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9dcbf",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, right.[p/] She [i]is[/i] a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0877d62",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: What was she like when she attended school here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de2096",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: She was quite the overachiever.[p/] She was elected student council president during her first year in the General Arcane Track."
}

{
  "id": "line:017e5ec",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] She [i]would[/i] be one of those students."
}

{
  "id": "line:0614de6",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I [i]do[/i] miss those days. [h=\"She was working so hard|to escape from Beatrice's shadow.\" e=\"sa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03121cb",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Did you know?[p/] Eris is one of our top students in the study of [i]illusion[/i] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0194489",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Thank you, headmaster.[p/] I appreciate your praise."
}

{
  "id": "line:03daaab",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why [i]do[/i] you study illusion magic, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0fa3",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] no particular reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d56b35",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Eris: I just happened to have an affinity for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d9d51",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Eris: It's also quite enjoyable to use my magic to deceive people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0664d2b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] I guess she [i]did[/i] enjoy startling me."
}

{
  "id": "line:053fa5b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Player: Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d2afe",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora mentioned that you gave us permission to use the Library."
}

{
  "id": "line:030f680",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't thank you enough for that.[p/] We learned a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e671a",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Of course.[p/] I'm always willing to aid the younger generation in the pursuit of knowledge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb56be",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: How [i]do[/i] you know Ms. Tymora, anyways?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022476f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Ah...[p/] That's..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2494",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Oh...[p/] Did she defend him in a court case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091f42f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "From his reaction,[p/] it must have been a hard time in his life."
}

{
  "id": "line:021e4d7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "It'd be best not to pry further."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd551a",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Hughes doesn't seem like the most...[p/] reliable employee."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2daa",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Please don't speak of him like that. [h=\"He works far more|rigorously than anyone...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:07476a0",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Ah...[p/] My apologies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead391",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Maybe my impression of him was wrong..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fbec3",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: How long have you been headmaster of the Imperial Academy, Mr. Redmond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0099ad9",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: For as long as I can remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca629",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I have dedicated my life to nurturing the knowledge and growth of young mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910f72",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: And I hope to do so for many more years. [h=\"I've come this far...\" e=\"afs\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0771018",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "...His thoughts didn't match with what he was saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a7fc6",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Player: Map"
}

{
  "id": "line:049e651",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Imperial Academy is actually quite big when I look at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0039347",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Well, of course.[p/] We [i]are[/i] the primary source of magical education for mages throughout the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d4b72",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: As you may well know,[p/] most of the mages enrolled here are of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0144582",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Their families have invested a lot in our facilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1a94b",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind told us there was a bit of a mishap in Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:00438d4",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: A-[p/]Ah,[p/] yes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b459c",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I was filling in for the alchemy instructor when I accidentally misread the instructions she left."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b1d04",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I'm quite embarrassed to admit that my old age is catching up with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca1541",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, I didn't know you were the instructor for that alchemy class."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bc7c9",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherine Autopsy|Blood|Blood2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f37e3f",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: It's a terrible thing that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2db59",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: To think that someone would commit [i]murder[/i] within the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0265c79",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Using [b]necromancy[/b] no less..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540066",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: ...Yes.[p/] It's all a lot to take in..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e033c",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Mr. Redmond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062da10",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: Ah...[p/] My apologies."
}

{
  "id": "line:097f7e7",
  "node": "Headmaster_Present",
  "text": "Theodore: I've learned a lot in my years,[p/] but I can't say much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76cdd",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "I followed the map that Steelwind gave us,[p/] arriving at the Headmaster’s Office."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d1954",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "Theodore: Oh?[p/] Hello, there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbb361",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "Theodore: I wasn’t expecting guests today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3f8cb",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "An elderly man rose to greet us,[p/] his hand trembling as he walked towards us with the support of his cane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365ee4",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "His face was wrinkled,[p/] but his eyes were sharp.[p/] His expression held the wisdom of a life long-lived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcab2a",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "I recognized his voice.[p/] He was the one who made those announcements during the lockdown."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e70f8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Sorry for coming unannounced."
}

{
  "id": "line:0206bb8",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: You must be—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c50e0",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: My name is Theodore Redmond.[p/] I'm the headmaster of the Wyverngarde Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbd05c",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: And judging from [i]your[/i] appearance...[p/] You must be the protégé of Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:060f727",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: To what do I owe the pleasure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d53db9",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: They must be here to investigate the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcea42",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Wait...[p/] Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2ab38",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought you went to see Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7102e",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: Unfortunately,[p/] the Inquisition is questioning him right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ad3d3",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "ERIS: They aren't allowing visitors."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e0b4c",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: He must be so scared right now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e01ec",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I hope he’s okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f189",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "Right...[p/] She had the same experience not too long ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04ae3",
  "node": "Headmaster_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: I can't believe this is happening... [h=\"Why in the Lord's name|did they arrest Wallace?\" e=\"afs\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01dac03",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie: ...How are we going to get all of this out on time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064cae9",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "The myriad of empty plates laid around the kitchen filled Valerie with dread."
}

{
  "id": "line:035ea3d",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "It was almost time for breakfast,[p/] and soon the students would be upon them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0821d4a",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina quickly passed by her sister as she snatched a tray off the counter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b18d51",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "She was jumping between multiple stations,[p/] but even then,[p/] each movement she made was quick and purposeful."
}

{
  "id": "line:018af6b",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "The kitchen was a machine.[p/] Valentina just had to turn each gear singlehandedly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0819b47",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "But in her hands,[p/] it ran like clockwork...[p/] Most of the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c47717",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: Val,[p/] are you finished plating the smoked salmon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93e8c",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie: R-[p/][s/]Right![p/] Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08268f0",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie stared at the excess assortment of food they had prepared for the noble children."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddfb2a",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "She grimly remembered the years she and her sister spent starving in an orphanage."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ea2ed",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Are they even going to eat all of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e3561",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: They won't.[p/] They’ll taste a few of them and throw the rest out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df1830",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: It still has to be perfect when it hits the cafeteria."
}

{
  "id": "line:08312e8",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie: Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acccfd",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie watched as her sister lifted each of the croissant slices,[p/] measuring their width against her index finger."
}

{
  "id": "line:037dfe6",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: These slices are too thick.[p/] It's going to overpower the salmon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a952a6",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Does that really matter?[p/] I thought they really liked your croissants."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dde69e",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: Trust me.[p/] If the ratio's off,[p/] they [i]will[/i] make sure we know."
}

{
  "id": "line:00787e0",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Valentina: Some of these kids would have us executed for bad plating if they could."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a33853",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Before Valerie could respond,[p/] one of the kitchen timers went off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3cd1c",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina quickly rushed to the stove and began melting butter in a pot."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef4bb",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valerie: About that...[p/] One of House Frega's attendants came by earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f4ca8",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina barely glanced away from the pot as she poured a bowl of eggs into it and began beating them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0691e19",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Her face tightened at the mention of Lady Frega.[p/] Her whisk moved slightly more violently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0368a0f",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: Ugh...[p/] What does Miriam want now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01693fc",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valerie: She's asking for roasted peacock."
}

{
  "id": "line:0203021",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: ...For breakfast?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f4c4a",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valerie: She also wants...[p/] \"honey-lacquered brioche bread topped with Arcurian whipped cream and Ixian strawberries\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0392c93",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: And it gets even better!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4a86",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Just grab me the normal stuff from the pantry when you can."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9dc1",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: You [i]know[/i] that spoiled brat can't tell the difference."
}

{
  "id": "line:01411b2",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: Here.[p/] Stir these eggs for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28f2d",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina handed her sister the pot of scrambled eggs.[p/] Valerie's shoulders tensed."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a4be4",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "She was great with a knife,[p/] but her forays with the stove never ended well."
}

{
  "id": "line:082a1f3",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valerie: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0672f16",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: The stove's on low heat.[p/] Just keep stirring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0499616",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valerie: O-[p/][s/]Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26b7a",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina's mind was already on the next task.[p/] She entered the freezer and dragged out the butchered peacock."
}

{
  "id": "line:01daf78",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Luckily,[p/] they'd just received the meat shipment that morning.[p/] It hadn't fully frozen yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b0fe3",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "She quickly tossed it onto the counter and began weaving cooking twine around its legs."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f9e0",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina: Scaled Lord...[p/] These kids have no idea how good they have it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0572d2b",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Valentina Ianus was the Imperial Academy's head chef...[p/] and pâtissière,[p/] brewer,[p/] butcher,[p/] and saucier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9e7ef",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "The staff that used to fulfill each of those roles were let go one by one—[p/]the work of Professor Bellwether and her disdain for the commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edd531",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "At first,[p/] the twins had welcomed the chance to cook for the children of nobles.[p/] The pay was astounding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2543a",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "...But it wasn't long before they discovered why this kitchen had seen such a rapid turnover."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a70858",
  "node": "Startb",
  "text": "Jan: Hey, you two...[p/] How's breakfast going?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd212",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "The academy's custodian trudged into the kitchen.[p/] His posture was heavy,[p/] and his eyes were half-dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f984f",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Same as usual, Jan.[p/] How about you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a4331",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Jan: Same as usual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2f3ec",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: ...Yeah?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4b8a5",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina recalled the many times she caught Jan napping in the pantry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0301b4e",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: Oh, Jan.[p/] I packed some of last night's risotto on the counter."
}

{
  "id": "line:06269a9",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Val![p/][s/] The eggs!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d128f",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: O-[p/][s/]Oh, right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039dee6",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina grimaced as she looked over the pot of eggs.[p/] The liquid was no longer emulsified."
}

{
  "id": "line:055d62d",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "It was still edible,[p/] but it wasn't perfect—[p/]something below the Imperial Academy's self-imposed standards."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f69d95",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Val, come on![p/] I have to start over now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018ff30",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: I only left them for a second..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0341",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Jan: You two look busy...[p/] I'll just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0021b6e",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0616b26",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina pressed her hands together,[p/] closed her eyes,[p/] and took a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0852acc",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: ...It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:09011f9",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Just help me prep the next batch while I grab the ingredients for Miriam's food."
}

{
  "id": "line:0331e6a",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: Okay...[p/] I'll—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c05d68",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: Oh, gods..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a913b",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina saw her sister tense up.[p/] What was it [i]now[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ba634",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valerie: Catherine is coming...[p/] She doesn't look happy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:064cc4b",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Are you serious?[p/][s/] What does that prissy little—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00070f5",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Hello, Ms. Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0459de7",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: [i]Professor[/i] Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee49cf",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: ...What can I do for you today, Professor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6e72c",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: Care to explain what [i]this[/i] is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c03725",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "The \"professor\" PRESENTED Valentina with the Eggs Benedict that she'd personally prepared earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc77fc",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "It looked perfect.[p/] It was exactly what she asked for, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0393e72",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: ...I'm sorry.[p/] Is there something wrong with your breakfast?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c9ff0",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: These eggs are mushy and undercooked.[p/] There's no crisp to them at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650ccc",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: ...Those are poached eggs, Professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0517776",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: \"Poached\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6c9df",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: You know...[p/] It's when you boil eggs in a pot of simmering water,[p/] and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f81b7",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: \"Boiled\"?![p/][s/] Do you think this is whatever shelter Redmond plucked you out of?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018c1ea",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: I won't swallow another piece of this rustic grime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d097d1",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Catherine: I expect a meal befitting of the Imperial Academy.[p/] Do it right this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0050919",
  "node": "Start1",
  "text": "Valentina: Right away, Professor."
}

{
  "id": "line:05638a6",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Valentina thought of slapping that snooty attitude right off her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a91e0",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "It would be easy.[p/] She could have done it right at that moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed8273",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "What did she have to lose?[p/] They were already planning on firing her anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0857c9d",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "But she took a breath.[p/] Nothing was worth drawing the ire of Bellwether's friends on the school board."
}

{
  "id": "line:0406cfd",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Valentina: Some \"professor\"...[p/] Who doesn't know what Eggs Benedict is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ccbc5",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Valentina: These stupid mages wouldn't know good food if it walked up to them and jumped down their throats."
}

{
  "id": "line:0709180",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m sorry, Celeste,[p/] but there's nowhere left to go..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03096e6",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait,[p/] I think I have something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0776838",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste's eyes darted around the chess board,[p/] scanning for a way to escape my attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9409",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "I could see her measuring every angle of retreat,[p/] but I'd been in this endgame plenty of times before.[p/] It was already over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a4bc",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] just surrender."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4cf14",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "She didn't respond.[p/] Her eyes continued to search for the exact piece she needed to move."
}

{
  "id": "line:076c985",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: There![p/][s/] What about that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d77c8",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "I immediately moved my knight to respond."
}

{
  "id": "line:037c2fe",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b6224",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09905c6",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: Can I get a do-over?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f275a",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Professionals don't get do-overs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4a54a",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Ruby: Would you two keep it down?[p/] We're in a library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4aa1d",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "My mentor's eyes were fixed on the chessboard between Celeste and me.[p/] Soon,[p/] they went straight to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dd179",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]We were just taking a break."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fe428",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: A pretty short break, from the looks of it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:095f1ac",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, so it's going to be like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3d41d",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose it's going to be like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c961",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "The Imperial Library was supposedly one of the largest in Wyverngarde.[p/] I'd never seen so many books."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5261f",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "I honestly felt quite at home here.[p/] There was no noise,[p/] and everyone kept to themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0723551",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Aside from a few dirty looks from nearly everyone here,[p/] I was free to do my research in peace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb818a",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "...Something strange had happened during Celeste's trial last week.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e95984",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "That final moment with Pierce had awakened something new in me.[p/] I used the Eye of Horus in a way I'd never had before."
}

{
  "id": "line:090d355",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "I wasn't a mage.[p/] Ms. Tymora and I had confirmed as much when I failed to attune to a blank Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:08021b3",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Which meant I couldn't learn arcane magic,[p/] but my ability must have been closely related to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:039d952",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "The Imperial Academy was a school for the most talented mages in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a88c8a",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "The library on campus supposedly held the kingdom’s entire knowledge on magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2daf5",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "...But with all the books I'd read,[p/] I still couldn't find a single mention of anything [i]like[/i] the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8e932",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "There weren't any arcane spells that could affect the mind,[p/] and everything I'd read today had just confirmed that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0062997",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Ruby: With all its resources,[p/] the kingdom [i]has[/i] to have seen something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0245f4d",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Ruby: Are they hiding that information—[p/]even from the nobility?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3a52f",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you sure you can’t tell me what you’re looking for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50c66",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: I’ve seen a lot when I was travelling outside Wyverngarde.[p/] Maybe I can help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdb2e9",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste had a point,[p/] but Ms. Tymora didn't completely get along with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7ef3",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "I'm sure she'd have objections,[p/] and even if she didn't,[p/] my mentor had always been wary about letting people know about my Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4a31b",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "It was a magical ability that didn't follow the rules of arcane magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2d33f",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "The biggest advantage of the Eye of Horus was that no one ever knew about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0546f5e",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry,[p/] I can't..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c584be",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4347",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Aren't [i]you[/i] supposed to be researching new spells?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023ffad",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh,[p/] I'm almost finished."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f06e0",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Ruby: Already...?[p/] You should really challenge yourself more, McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0741f93",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Whatever, Ruby."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fbc24",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Now, why don't [i]you[/i] tell me what [i]you're[/i] looking for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0817076",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Eris: They must be researching non-arcane magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01063cf",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Celeste: OH MY GOD! [h=\"We're under attack!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0618e88",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "We nearly jumped out of our chairs as that girl appeared next to us.[p/] I even saw Celeste's hand twitch towards her sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cc066",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "This girl must've been a student at the academy,[p/] but she didn't dress like the aristocrats here."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d9e4a",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Her expression was kind but also blank in a way.[p/] It was impossible to read."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bb65b",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "There was something ethereal to her demeanor.[p/] It felt like I was speaking with a ghost."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1a87f",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "How long had she been standing there?[p/] I hadn't noticed her at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0932e07",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "She looked oddly familiar too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c0267",
  "node": "Start_1",
  "text": "Eris: I should apologize,[p/] but I overheard your conversation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb6b61",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "As she approached our table,[p/] another student followed behind her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be6195",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "His eyes darted to each person at the table,[p/] like a rodent appraising every threat in the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:08be6ae",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "In contrast to the girl,[p/] he was as tightly wound as a violin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0323a85",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "It looked like even the slightest sign of danger would send him scurrying away."
}

{
  "id": "line:048d167",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Wallace: E-[p/][s/]Eris![p/][s/] You really shouldn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:064ad60",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Wallace: I-[p/][s/]I’m so sorry! [h=\"Maybe if I apologize,|they won't have us executed!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d41df",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: It’s fine, Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce3cfa",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Who [i]are[/i] you two?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9cd3",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Ah,[p/] that was incredibly rude of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed9cc",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Most everyone calls me Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:015388d",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: This is Wallace Nightgrave.[p/] We’re both students here."
}

{
  "id": "line:074a678",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Wallace: H-[p/]Hi..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b822b",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: That was a private conversation, by the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f98e3",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5286",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Researching unconventional forms of magic is actually a hobby of mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb410d",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: I might be able to help you with your research, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a31e6c",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: And what makes you so sure that [i]is[/i] what we were researching...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f64be",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Your protégé has a bad habit of muttering to himself when he thinks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ba38",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: I assumed that his research had [i]something[/i] to do with divine magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:002861a",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: I assumed that his research had [i]something[/i] to do with magic that was unlike the arcane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0812671",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "I felt a piercing side glance from Ms. Tymora.[p/] I just pretended not to notice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0032e70",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/]But anyways,[p/] I'd really appreciate your help.[p/] Do you mind if I ask you a few questions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07761f7",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Eris: Of course.[p/] I’d be happy to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0699d5f",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Wait[p/][p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f62de",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Fine...[p/] I suppose it wouldn't hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fbde3",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Ruby: Just be more careful, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84ac9",
  "node": "Start_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bcc24",
  "node": "Intro_Main",
  "text": "EXAMINE"
}

{
  "id": "line:0553cab",
  "node": "Intro_Main",
  "text": "TALK"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd32d6",
  "node": "Intro_Main",
  "text": "MOVE"
}

{
  "id": "line:0648117",
  "node": "Intro_Main",
  "text": "PRESENT"
}

{
  "id": "line:0913146",
  "node": "Intro_Main",
  "text": "MENUS"
}

{
  "id": "line:009a105",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "The library was full of books.[p/] I'd been reading through them all morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff5153",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Player: Holy Text"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b39844",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "It was a holy text of some sort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0726895",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "It must've been related to the Church of Bahamut."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efc1fd",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "There was a table for students to sit at."
}

{
  "id": "line:03842de",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "I'd been here with Celeste all morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:020064c",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Player: Globe"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c962da",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a globe of the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:0102d14",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's amazing how many other nations there are aside from Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ee706",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: I've been to most of these places."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b15ab",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: You should come with me next time, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:005ee4b",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "That was a nice thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0caeb",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Maybe I could find some time to travel with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9754",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "Player: Notice"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6de0",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "There was a newsletter taped to one of the shelves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b25d3c",
  "node": "Intro_Examine_Library",
  "text": "\"Due to several instances of crude misuse,[p/] Arcane Construct voice lines can now only be set by Headmaster Redmond.\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01243c0",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Player: Eris and Wallace"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab73cf",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "TYRION: Are you two students at the Imperial Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0397c49",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "ERIS: I’m currently taking classes here for the [b]illusion[/b] program."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a44f0",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "CELESTE: Illusions...[p/] That’s the kind of magic that lets you turn invisible, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb3324",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "ERIS: Technically,[p/] yes,[p/] but few mages ever reach that level."
}

{
  "id": "line:01484b7",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "ERIS: I’m a bit sad to admit that I'm not able to cast that arcane spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c89d25",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "CELESTE: That’s still pretty cool![p/] What about you, Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0396e89",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "WALLACE: I-[p/]I—[p/] U-[p/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4ef7d",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "ERIS: Wallace has a [i]unique[/i] field of study.[p/] Please don't ask him about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a270d6",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh...[p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0056027",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion and Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1a6f5",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Rumors about you two have been floating around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b775",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e37532",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Many recognize you from the news articles about Ms. McCoy's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3df60",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015f7de",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: The students were surprised to see you two on the academy grounds this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:037a5e0",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "That made sense.[p/] In some ways,[p/] this school was a cornerstone of the nobility's power."
}

{
  "id": "line:01aba41",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "This was the last place anyone would expect us to take an interest in,[p/] much less be permitted to enter."
}

{
  "id": "line:058d877",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Luckily,[p/] Ms. Tymora had a lot of connections she could pull on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91c94",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: I'm particularly surprised that [i]you're[/i] still in Wyverngarde, Ms. McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fa2c1",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: I'd figured the \"Crimson Demon\" would be off on another violent escapade."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af7759",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh gods...[p/] The papers found out about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e27fce",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Crimson Demon\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7c396",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't ask..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3015c",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Anyways,[p/] I'm working as Tyrion’s personal mercenary now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0187af1",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "WALLACE: M-[p/][s/]Mercenary?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e87b4",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'd prefer the term \"bodyguard\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0097493",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "I'd successfully indicted Pierce in her trial,[p/] but that invited a lot of unwanted attention."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ef2f7",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "It wasn't long before I found armed thugs suspiciously looming around my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adb375",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "After what happened to Flinhart,[p/] Celeste wanted to stay closer to her mother.[p/] Steelwind even kept the teleportation circle from the investigation active for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d5e44",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora saw an opportunity to hire her as my bodyguard.[p/] I [i]did[/i] get along really well with her after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2df6e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "It was nice to have someone to talk to while I was getting acquainted with being an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0449ae7",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "...It was also nice to have someone who could toss an armed thug with one arm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0523d56",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Player: Unconventional Magic"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5bd76",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: “Unconventional Magic”..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e2681",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: One might wonder why you're researching such a thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf5c14",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: I want to know that too!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f138d",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I’m sorry,[p/] but I can’t really say..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9cb70",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: There are many spells in this world,[p/] and new ones are always being developed."
}

{
  "id": "line:070934e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: What makes you so certain that this magic isn't arcane?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fad280",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: The magic I'm looking into doesn’t follow the conventions of arcane magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0834bc8",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Oh?[p/] How so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d9576",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c402b3",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "I needed to tread carefully.[p/] Ms. Tymora's glare agreed."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e861e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It was cast by someone who's not a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae2f90",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, really?[p/] That implies that it was cast by a person,[p/] and it wasn't something like artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0220eea",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "I flashed an apologetic look to my mentor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dad30d",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Hm...[p/] That [i]does[/i] remind me of a story."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2f173",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: A...[p/] story?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093b39e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Are you familiar with the legends about how Wyverngade was created?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05984c5",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mean the story about the ancient dragons?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f7b5a",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Dragons?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072a0ff",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Hm...[p/] I knew you'd find it interesting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbfc76",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Player: The Ancient Dragons"
}

{
  "id": "line:056fc7a",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you talking about those stories told by the Church of Bahamut?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0928159",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: Technically,[p/] there's only ever mention of [i]one[/i] ancient dragon:[p/] Rathallion, the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c831c8",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] the first mages were created centuries ago by him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc09c6",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] I never knew that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a1571",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: In the year 10 BSB,[p/] Wyverngarde was a small kingdom caught between two warring nations:[p/] Ixia to the east,[p/] and Lumina to the west."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ff9f6",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: With no way to protect themselves,[p/] this kingdom was on the brink of destruction."
}

{
  "id": "line:075fc85",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: Its people prayed to Bahamut:[p/] the God of Dragons,[p/] for salvation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00743a0",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: And almost as if to answer their prayers,[p/] Rathallion—[p/]the last of the ancient dragons—[p/]appeared before them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0251292",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: He took pity on their plight and granted them the gift of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:06280b8",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was a weapon our greatest warriors wielded without equal."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d0c0e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: With arcane magic in hand,[p/] these warriors laid devastation upon our enemies."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7a1f",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: They didn't just stop the war.[p/] They joined the battle and singlehandedly won it,[p/] taking large swathes of territory for themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdb7bc",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: With our nation protected and our power made known,[p/] these warriors went on to form the noble houses of today."
}

{
  "id": "line:085b8de",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Ruby: Hmph...[p/] What a load of nonsense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569bc9",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Ruby: That story is nothing but religious propaganda created to prop up the noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f387b1",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "ERIS: Regardless,[p/] the significance of this legend is in the Scaled Lord himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba6b3",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "TYRION: Rathallion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0d07",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: He bestowed the power to become a mage on several individuals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0888946",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: And to this day,[p/] that power can only be passed through bloodlines."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4d041",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Can you think of an arcane spell that could reproduce something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c2b91",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] I suppose not."
}

{
  "id": "line:064ea58",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Rathallion had powers that weren’t bound by the conventions of the Arcane Arts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c0e2",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: In other words,[p/] he could use magic that was distinct from the magic of today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847b3e",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Ruby: Please,[p/] do you honestly expect us to believe a story like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a4b60",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Ruby: It’s completely unrealistic."
}

{
  "id": "line:036e73a",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "Eris: ...As unrealistic as a non-mage using magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a41fea",
  "node": "Intro_Talk_Library",
  "text": "She had a point...[p/] It was the closest thing I had to a lead right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fb5fe",
  "node": "Intro_Present_Library",
  "text": "Eris: You're already resorting to PRESENTING me things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0409958",
  "node": "Intro_Present_Library",
  "text": "Eris: We've only just started.[p/] I really think you're overthinking things."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0827",
  "node": "Intro_Present_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Or do you simply want to see all the unique things that I have to say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05882e3",
  "node": "Intro_Present_Library",
  "text": "Eris: I'm sorry to disappoint you,[p/] but I'm not some script for you to toy around with."
}

{
  "id": "line:06181fa",
  "node": "Intro_Present_Library",
  "text": "Eris: Feel free to try again later, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0117a0f",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "Catherine: Ah...[p/] Of course, it's [i]you[/i] lot making all of this noise."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb570",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "One of the instructors of the Academy approached us disdainfully."
}

{
  "id": "line:029e8bd",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "She looked like a woman of the aristocracy.[p/] Every bit of her demeanor carried that—[p/]from the stiffness of her posture to the condescending grimace on her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c560c",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "She glared at each of us like we were the most disgusting things she'd ever seen in her life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0843743",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "WALLACE: P-[p/][s/]P-[p/][s/]Professor Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff69c2",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "CATHERINE: That is [s/][i]Professor[/i][p/] Bellwether to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0180ceb",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "Celeste: But he just called you—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa77be",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "CATHERINE: I knew letting you rabble into our walls would lead to nothing but trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6f214",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "CATHERINE: ...You’ve even started associating with our malcontents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdd0be",
  "node": "LookTBooks",
  "text": "CATHERINE: Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfd0e4",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "WALLACE: Y-[p/]y-[p/]y-[p/]y-[p/]yes?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f21222",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "CATHERINE: How am I supposed to understand you when you’re stuttering?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec077",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "WALLACE: Y-[p/][s/]Yes,[p/][s/] Professor Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:043b68a",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "CATHERINE: Straighten out your uniform and fix that [i]awful[/i] hair."
}

{
  "id": "line:091be65",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "CATHERINE: I know it’s unreasonable to expect anything more from you,[p/] but try not to look like such a street urchin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0332e36",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "Wallace shrank away from the professor.[p/] He reacted like a scared and beaten animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:048944e",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "I could see Celeste's fist start to clench.[p/] She looked like she was about to toss the professor across the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1dc9a",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "I flashed her a look.[p/] Any trouble we caused would just make things worse for Eris and Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c819e",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "Catherine: As for the rest of you,[p/] your rowdy behavior is disrupting the other students."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b67ec",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "Catherine: Leave.[p/] Now."
}

{
  "id": "line:019260f",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "RUBY: Oh, please.[p/] The headmaster gave us express permission to be here."
}

{
  "id": "line:097ec81",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "Catherine: That may be,[p/] but the school board has placed the Imperial Library under my jurisdiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:07eddc8",
  "node": "LookTBooksB",
  "text": "Catherine: I can remove anyone who disrupts the studies of our prized students."
}

{
  "id": "line:013f6bc",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Ruby: Why would [i]you[/i] have authority over the library?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8ed7",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Tyrion: My apologies, Professor.[p/] We'll try to keep our volume lower."
}

{
  "id": "line:029c10e",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Catherine: I don't believe I was talking to you,[p/][s/] [i]boy[/i].[p/] Know your place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0779b4a",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, Tyrion.[p/] [i]Please[/i] tell me you feel threatened so I can \"defend\" you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d89ceb",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "I wanted to avoid a confrontation,[p/] but a part of me really wanted to see that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f5708",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Catherine: If you refuse to leave,[p/] I'll have no choice but to remove you myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:047efed",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Catherine: I'll have you know that I'm the most accomplished mage at this academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ffa45",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Celeste: Trust me.[p/] You'll find spellcasting difficult while something's hitting you in the face. [h=\"Come at me, bitch.|I'll wear you like a sweater.\" e=\"ha\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02369",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "...I definitely caught hints of Flinhart in her thoughts every so often."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c6774",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "CATHERINE: H-[p/][s/]Hmph...[p/] I don't have to stand for this. [h=\"That girl is like a rabid dog...|It'd be best to keep my distance.\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0923ee7",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Catherine: I was just on my way to speak with the headmaster.[p/] He [i]will[/i] be hearing of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:073012e",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh,[p/][s/] you're going to tell on us?[p/][s/] I'm [i]so[/i] scared!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a95f0",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "WALLACE: ...Celeste,[p/] you're a little scary."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cfe7d",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Celeste: Aw...[p/] Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0f9b",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "ERIS: Anyways,[p/] Wallace.[p/] You’ve finished this week’s assignment, haven’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe8a6",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "Eris: Would you mind entertaining Celeste while I aid Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb583f",
  "node": "LookTBooksC",
  "text": "WALLACE: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] I don’t know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d19dba",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "CELESTE: Now that you mention it...[p/] I could really use some help learning a new spell formula."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ee2ea",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "CELESTE: You know your way around here.[p/] Right, Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce2d78",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "WALLACE: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] O-[p/][s/]okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:011cb98",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "RUBY: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:019f01b",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "TYRION: I’ll be discreet, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:01517e4",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "RUBY: ...Please do."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1a43",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "RUBY: I still have some business to take care of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:03835dc",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "Ruby: I'll leave you to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0114b62",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "She was about to leave,[p/] but she stared at Eris warily."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c87c7",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "Eris: ...Is something wrong, Ruby?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f80509",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "Ruby: No.[p/] Not at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f960",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "I spent the next few hours searching through the library’s books with Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f8688",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "I hadn’t thought to look into the ancient dragons.[p/] The library had religious texts about them in abundance."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1af6",
  "node": "LookTBooksD",
  "text": "There was one problem, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0485beb",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "TYRION: These texts read more like myths than real historical documents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0798d8e",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "ERIS: It can’t be helped.[p/] The Church of Bahamut has far too much influence in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0d7a8",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "Eris: To them,[p/] history is a narrative to be embellished rather than something to be preserved."
}

{
  "id": "line:015f201",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "Eris: The bones of dragons are displayed in Wyverngarde's museums.[p/] Without those,[p/] most would have no evidence that they even existed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dc735",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "TYRION: Except for Rathallion, possibly..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a7634",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to these legends,[p/] dragons can't die of old age.[p/] Presumably,[p/] he'd still be alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:087ce77",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "ERIS: I wouldn’t be surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f6fff",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "Eris: Despite everything,[p/] the kingdom includes him in our constitution."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b20b5",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "TYRION: Wait...[p/] Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0226",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "ERIS: As the savior of our kingdom,[p/] he and his kin were given an honorary position in our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0add678",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "ERIS: The Scaled Lord made Wyverngarde what it is today.[p/] He was given authority that befits such a legacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fad7b",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "TYRION: How have I never heard of this before?[p/] I've memorized all of Wyverngarde's laws."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5aaae",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "Eris: Practically speaking,[p/] it's never been invoked.[p/] It's merely a law spun of reverent words to praise the Scaled Lord and appease the Church."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0b55b",
  "node": "LookTBooksE",
  "text": "TYRION: [s/]A-[p/]Ah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0772874",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "I was so stuck in my own thoughts that I'd accidentally walked face-first into a bookshelf."
}

{
  "id": "line:0262fb8",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "The shelf slowly began to tip,[p/] and I had to catch it before it knocked over the other shelves like a set of dominoes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd84b2",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Several books fell out of it as I slowly set the shelf back in place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f3f4",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "They hit the ground with a cacophony of thuds.[p/] Some students glanced over at me,[p/] annoyed by the noise."
}

{
  "id": "line:091295f",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "I really hoped Bellwether wasn't still around to see that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a4324",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "I wasn't sure where the voice was coming from,[p/] but it sounded annoyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa06a0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Eris giggled to herself as she watched me flounder around."
}

{
  "id": "line:06976f3",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hey,[p/] are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ba6cb",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Wallace: We heard a loud noise and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f656e",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Wallace: ...Oh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c75189",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "The two of them scanned over the pile of fallen books around me."
}

{
  "id": "line:062cf41",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Pfft...[p/] What did you do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04feae4",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "TYRION: T-[p/][s/]That's not important...[p/] Can you help me clean this up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d00e5",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "ERIS: Ah...[p/] There’s no need for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0809ce0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Eris: Wallace,[p/] can you call over the Construct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef4c7d",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Wallace: Ugh...[p/] Why do you always make [i]me[/i] do it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049e2fc",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Eris: Please?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f973a0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1",
  "text": "Wallace: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Construct.[p/][s/] I require assistance."
}

{
  "id": "line:049be47",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Construct: ACKNOWLEDGED!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70c7c",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "CELESTE: Agh![p/][s/] W-[p/][s/]What is that—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d4866",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Upon Wallace's command,[p/] one of the nearby suits of armor suddenly sprang to life and marched towards us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c57271",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "The voice coming from it sounded like a woman's,[p/] but it lacked any emotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:03389c8",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "I could have sworn that I'd heard its voice before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0922dbb",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, I thought those things were just decorative."
}

{
  "id": "line:063c234",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "ERIS: This is an Arcane Construct.[p/] It's a suit of armor brought to life using artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f2b52",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "ERIS: They’re designed to carry out various tasks on campus."
}

{
  "id": "line:063f520",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "CELESTE: Really?[p/] I didn’t know artificery had come that far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa429f",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "ERIS: They’re still experimental.[p/] They aren’t available to the public yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f6d35",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Eris: House von Sanctus is using the Academy as a testing ground for them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08198b4",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Wallace: Construct,[p/] can you please put these books back where they belong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a22ed",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Eris: You're so polite to them.[p/] You know they're just machines, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6580e",
  "node": "LookTBooks_1B",
  "text": "Wallace: They're really helpful...[p/] It just feels wrong to be rude to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa8056",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "The Construct jumped straight into its task,[p/] its metallic hands moving with a quick yet delicate precision."
}

{
  "id": "line:001056c",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "It wasn't long before all the books were back exactly where they belonged."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e5d29",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wow![p/] So, they do whatever you tell them to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b350c4",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "Wallace: There [i]are[/i] some limits to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce18c6",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Construct![p/][s/] Tell me that I’m the fairest maiden you’ve ever seen!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afce85",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "Construct: COMMAND REJECTED."
}

{
  "id": "line:063c578",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Aw...[p/] What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01beb60",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "TYRION: I guess they’re not able to lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b45041",
  "node": "LookTBooks_2",
  "text": "Celeste: Watch it, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:040d593",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "TYRION: I've heard of artificery recording audio,[p/] but to think they could process and respond to what I'm saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f109b",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "TYRION: I’ve never seen anything like it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f65e30",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: But you just said that they're experimental, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29e92",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe I can find a way to trick it into doing what I want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d741bb",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Eris: I'd advise against that.[p/] We've had several instances of students using them to play pranks."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d6a2c",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Eris: Even if your commands are rejected,[p/] they're still stored in the Construct's logs."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f233b",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "ERIS: And weren't you researching spells with Wallace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d03c4c",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, that?[p/] I'm already done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8182",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: I've just been reading [i]Death at Daggerfall[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9f96",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Did you know they have the unpublished manuscript of the newest book?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79c77",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Those books were apparently her favorite series of murder mysteries.[p/] She'd been recommending them to me for the entire week."
}

{
  "id": "line:01680f0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "And by \"recommending\",[p/] I meant she'd been leaving those books around my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa93b6",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "I think at one point,[p/] she'd somehow snuck them into Ms. Tymora's office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0091d0f",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "...I really got an earful from my mentor about that one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffc401",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's no possible way you're already done learning those new spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a09bd",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We've only been here a few hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a0e16",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah?[p/] You wanna bet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e4ed",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sure.[p/] Show me your Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d2e9b",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] No! [h=\"I can't tell him yet.|I want it to be a surprise.\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7732",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "I didn't catch any lies through the Eye of Horus.[p/] Was she really telling the truth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0556a8d",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "I never actually knew the process for learning new spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bfb79",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "I just knew that it involved becoming familiar with unique spell formulas."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e23fb6",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "She was fidgeting a lot when we were reading together this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bfbb9",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "She basically forced me into taking a break to play chess with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bca36",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you were in the fiction section,[p/] did you get a chance to read [i]Wraithbound[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049a51a",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: This again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5f8cf",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a great series, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db211c",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "The best series I've ever read.[p/] Even after nearly a century,[p/] those books had aged like fine wine."
}

{
  "id": "line:078f824",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Look, Tyrion.[p/] I'm sorry,[p/] but I just can't get into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:006a308",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: The whole thing just feels so hammy and unrealistic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb20bf",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Come on![p/] It's a classic story of good vs evil.[p/] Corrin Bloomveil is a literary genius."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a0f45",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "...Maybe I needed to start leaving my copies of [i]Wraithbound[/i] in the McCoy Tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b70c0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Look,[p/] I'm just not into the fantasy genre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c01410",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Wallace: ... [h=\"Good...|Those books are terrible anyways.\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0231f8d",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3204",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Wallace: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] I should get back to work! [h=\"Scaled Lord,|did I say that out loud?!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0390f04",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Wallace: Let's go, Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0befa22",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0903ec5",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Let's keep going, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cb8c0",
  "node": "LookTBooks_3",
  "text": "I had no intentions of letting Celeste get ahead of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b734d2",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "I read more and more about the ancient dragons."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a440a",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "I looked at anything I could get my hands on—[p/]historical accounts,[p/] religious texts,[p/] even folk tales."
}

{
  "id": "line:01483e9",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "But after finding the twelfth embelished story about a dragon fighting a knight,[p/] I was starting to lose hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:040bd93",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "This most recent story was the worst.[p/] It read like the fantasy novels I usually read,[p/] but even [i]I[/i] had a limit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbb44c",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "At this point,[p/] I felt like one of those Arcane Constructs,[p/] hollowly reading out the words of yet another myth to myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b797d6",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"The dragon awoke with a rumble,[p/] hot steam pouring from its mouth.\"[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0053ace",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"The knight responded in kind,[p/] drawing his steel and charging forward.[/i]\""
}

{
  "id": "line:05aa868",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"But the dragon had his own weapon.[p/] He used his Eye of Bahamut to—\"[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c275f",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "My dull rhythmic dictation broke when I read that line."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a4683",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "I straightened out in my chair,[p/] and inspected each subsequent line carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4c152",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"He used his Eye of Bahamut to call upon the power of Radiance to pierce through the knight's soul.\"[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:070841a",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"Naught a single thought was concealed from his gaze.\"[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04aefda",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]\"The knight's thoughts—[p/]even his emotions—[p/]were laid bare before the scaled giant.\"[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bda41",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "That description sounded eerily familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:009acb4",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "I'd named my ability the \"Eye of Horus\" when I was a child.[p/] At the time,[p/] I was just copying one of my childhood friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4da19",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "But was I actually using this \"Eye of Bahamut\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba6277",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Honestly,[p/] \"Eye of Horus\" fits better."
}

{
  "id": "line:046d45c",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: Ah, [p/] the Eye of Bahamut."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d9ca0",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Agh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:047715d",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "I jumped out of my seat again.[p/] How did she always sneak up on me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054021f",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: D-[p/][s/]Do you know about this \"Eye of Bahamut\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0574427",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is the first time I've seen it mentioned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5de79",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: Ah...[p/] Legends say that the Eye of Bahamut holds the power to mimic the radiance of the celestial gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727ed6",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: The \"[i]celestial[/i] gods\"?[p/] Are they anything like the Scaled Lord?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd8d32",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: ...Not quite,[p/] and I doubt you'd find anything about them here."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b102f",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Eye of Bahamut mimics the \"radiance\" of the gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea7fa6",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does that mean the dragon in this story is mimicking magic related to these \"celestials\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5fd82",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: Unfortunately,[p/] knowledge of them is quite scarce in Wyvergarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a491fc",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: Even mentioning the celestials could very well tie a noose around your neck."
}

{
  "id": "line:000fab9",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Eris: It's forbidden to possess any texts that even whisper their names."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b13f4",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] The kingdom must've been suppressing knowledge of religions other than the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:047a628",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "No wonder I couldn't find any information here.[p/] Was this whole morning a colossal waste of time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c075da",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "...No.[p/] This was still a lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c54260",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "If I couldn't read about the celestial gods here,[p/] I'd just have to look somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b2682",
  "node": "MurderReveal",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora had a lot of connections.[p/] I'm not sure if she'd condone the risk of buying illegal books, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:057778f",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "Suddenly,[p/] a low-pitched thrum thundered across the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18223",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "It was unnaturally loud.[p/] It must've been produced by some sort of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4325f",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/][s/] What [i]is[/i] that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0446a4c",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "TYRION: Were you messing around with the Arcane Constructs...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b5066",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "CELESTE: What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bef9bd",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I mean—[p/]only a little.[p/] I didn't expect that to trip anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feb1a1",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "Celeste: It finally stopped..."
}

{
  "id": "line:061e1b5",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "WALLACE: E-[p/]Eris...[p/][s/] Wasn’t that the lockdown?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9ca5",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "ERIS: Yes.[p/] I believe so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1f6a",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "TYRION: “Lockdown”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f967f",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "ERIS: The academy is outfitted with a large artificery system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6675b",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "ERIS: In a state of emergency,[p/] it will erect magical barriers throughout the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e4573",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "CELESTE: “State of emergency”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6120",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "CELESTE: Should we be worried?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07eac8d",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "ERIS: Don’t worry.[p/] The lockdown is designed to keep everyone sequestered."
}

{
  "id": "line:07825c5",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "ERIS: We’re safe from most threats as long as those barriers stay up."
}

{
  "id": "line:002a224",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "But...[p/] Ms. Tymora.[p/][s/] Wasn't she still on campus?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0254763",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "Theodore: I-[p/][s/]I’m terribly sorry!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06332b3",
  "node": "MurderRevealB",
  "text": "A disembodied voice cut through the anxious murmurs of the students in the library."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2ffe3",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: Students and faculty![p/][s/] Please remain calm!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ea570",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: T-[p/]There’s...[p/][s/] There’s been an attack in one of the lecture halls!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2719",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: Please stay where you are and wait for the City Watch to arrive!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01abb27",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "TYRION: ...We have to get out of here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074aae6",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/][s/] Tyrion, no.[p/] That's the last thing we should do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0779562",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "I ran towards the library entrance.[p/] My body crashed into the door.[p/] It didn't budge at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0794bca",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "I desperately pushed and pulled at the handle,[p/] trying to wrench the door open."
}

{
  "id": "line:049ad5d",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion, stop that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:028ddf2",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "TYRION: B-[p/]But...[p/][s/] Ms. Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a7a00",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: I know that you’re worried about her,[p/] but it's not safe out there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09697e0",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Look,[p/] the best thing we can do right now is stay here and wait until the lockdown is over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de8631",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "I knew she was right,[p/] but I couldn't just stand here and do nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d628a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "I began kicking the door handle,[p/] but my foot was repelled by the low hum of magical energy.[p/] It didn't move at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:082a1fc",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Celeste’s hand rested on the hilt of her sword.[p/] Her eyes slowly scanned our surroundings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0493253",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "The other students watched her fearfully.[p/] No one dared to come near us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc20f6",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "WALLACE: Celeste...[p/] I think you can calm down.[p/] They said the attack was in the lecture halls."
}

{
  "id": "line:0950861",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "She answered him without breaking her glare."
}

{
  "id": "line:0589286",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Celeste: We don't know what's happening,[p/] and it's my job to keep Tyrion safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:083fcc4",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "...She also calmed me down earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7e231",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "It was easy to forget sometimes,[p/] but she was really vigilant when it counted."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b79af",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: Students and faculty.[p/] Thank you for your patience."
}

{
  "id": "line:034184b",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: The knights have secured the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:097b80f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Theodore: The lockdown has been lifted.[p/] However,[p/] please remain in the building until—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00630dc",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "He was barely finished with his announcement before I was out the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0824e2c",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ee2e",
  "node": "MurderReveal_1",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey![p/][s/] Don’t go off on your own!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0450403",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "I desperately ran through the academy hallways."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b2e76",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0620fad",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:058269f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora![p/][s/] Where are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:028d21f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "I was running blindly.[p/] My breath was haggard.[p/] My heart was racing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d34367",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Dread was creeping inside me with each passing moment.[p/] I didn't even know where I was going."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422053",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: ...Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:097aab8",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: What’s wrong?[p/] Why are you shouting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:029af25",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "TYRION: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:016a580",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: Are you okay?[p/] You're breathing—"
}

{
  "id": "line:047645a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Relief washed away my anxiety.[p/] I just embraced my mentor tightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:08565d6",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "She'd always demanded I keep a professional distance from her,[p/] but despite myself,[p/] I was just relieved she was safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183457",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion![p/][s/] There you are!"
}

{
  "id": "line:051beb2",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: And...[p/] you're crying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044a56a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: C-[p/][s/]Cuthbert...[p/] You're hurting me."
}

{
  "id": "line:098fe9f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e129",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "I let go of her and tried to stifle my tears."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e2e9",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "CELESTE: We heard the announcement.[p/] Are you okay, Ruby?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083125f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: I am,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0249182",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora glanced at Wallace.[p/] She slowly put herself between us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f583c9",
  "node": "MurderReveal_2",
  "text": "RUBY: For now,[p/] I think we should head to the foyer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b96fd0",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "We arrived at the foyer.[p/] The Academy was swarmed with a legion of familiar knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:069266c",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "TYRION: The Inquisition?[p/] Don’t tell me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce2a51",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: They mentioned that there was an attack on campus..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a6d5d",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: They must have used magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa8ac",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "ORYM: Hey![p/][s/] You, there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65c8a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "As we came into the foyer,[p/] the Commander marched towards us."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb951",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "...But his attention wasn’t focused on Celeste this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d10df7",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "WALLACE: H-[p/][s/]Huh?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6a2dc",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "ORYM: Wallace Nightgrave![p/] By the authority of the Wyverngarde Crown,[p/][s/] I’m placing you under arrest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcf2d7",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "Before Wallace could react,[p/] Orym grabbed him by the wrist and began dragging him away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0716486",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hey,[p/][s/] what are you doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6fd9e",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "ORYM: You three...?[p/] The hell are [i]you[/i] doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:066bf2f",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said he was under arrest?[p/] On what charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3d9ee",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "ORYM: The charge of first-degree murder![p/][s/] This damned mage killed Catherine Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0348833",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "Celeste grabbed the commander's arm and wrenched him off of Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0865f92",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "Orym showed no resistance,[p/] clearly remembering what happened during [i]her[/i] arrest last week."
}

{
  "id": "line:054906a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Like hell you’re arresting him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0480b59",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: He was with us in the library the entire morning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:017fab7",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s no way he could have murdered her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f832e",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "RUBY: Step aside, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a57b76",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "CELESTE: But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04da407",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "TYRION: No,[p/] Ms. Tymora is right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d32caf",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Wallace is a suspect,[p/] we can’t legally stop the Inquisition from arresting him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc86c",
  "node": "MurderReveal_3",
  "text": "TYRION: It'd be best for you to go with them, Wallace.[p/] I'm sure we can get all of this sorted out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9c85e",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "I could only watch as the Inquisition dragged him away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c27b10",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "ERIS: My apologies.[p/] I’m going to accompany him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3721",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6d525",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "TYRION: They arrested him,[p/] even though he was in a different room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0831e7c",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Ruby: This school is filled with plenty of mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dbca9",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Ruby: There [i]has[/i] to be a longer list of suspects."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed6a65",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "CELESTE: What do we do now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032080a",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Let's head to the Lecture Halls.[p/] That's where the murder must've taken place."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e55b",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "RUBY: Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb942",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Y-[p/][s/]yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e2973",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "RUBY: He hasn’t accepted you as his attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce6dc",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "RUBY: You don’t even know if you’ll be working this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0126701",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I [i]know[/i] that he’s innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69cc0",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "She looked like she was about to reprimand me,[p/] but she just let out a defeated sigh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0430c48",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "RUBY: Just remember that being an attorney is your [i]job[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:039b2a8",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Ruby: Our law firm isn't a charity.[p/] If you overextend yourself,[p/] I'm not going to pay your rent for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6838",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "RUBY: I have another appointment in the city.[p/] Can you two take it from here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b17528",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Y-[p/]Yes.[p/][s/] Of course!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06de4c4",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "TYRION: Alright.[p/] Let’s go, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:05559e0",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh![p/] I've been waiting for our first case!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064766b",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] Wallace was just arrested.[p/] Be respectful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0518197",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...R-[p/][s/]Right.[p/] Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c527e",
  "node": "MurderReveal_4",
  "text": "I was reluctant to admit that I was just as excited as she was."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b0705",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: Celeste,[p/] this room was close to the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c96cb",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: Could you cast [b]Detect Magic[/b] and scan for magical traces?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a8c85",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:099eca1",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...! [h=\"Did he just say,|[i]scan for magical traces[/i]?!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3aaf5",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "VALENTINA: O-[p/]Oh![p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I’ll just get out of your way, then!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0808649",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Before we could even acknowledge her,[p/] Valentina broke out into a sprint and fled from the kitchen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a740ad",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow...[p/] She can run pretty fast."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee03f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "What was [i]that[/i] about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030390c",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Spoons"
}

{
  "id": "line:085f0f3",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "There was a rack of cooking implements hanging from the wall."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e92e7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Ingredients"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a6bba",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Several commonly used ingredients were close to the cooking area."
}

{
  "id": "line:0161db1",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Barrels"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee460a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a barrel full of some sort of drink."
}

{
  "id": "line:09940f4",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07954c9",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's probably not Lotus Juice, Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd437e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Bread"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0a2d7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/] it's a plate of bread."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8a64f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: They probably serve these as sides to the entrees."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d666f7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Don't get any ideas, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:00593b5",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Remember when we went to that fancy restaurant?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0245a83",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: You just [i]kept[/i] ordering breadsticks and butter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc76e6",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: The bread is [i]free[/i]![p/][s/] I might as well take advantage of it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc8cd",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: You know,[p/] eating that many carbs isn't good for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:077a433",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not as if I'm gaining any weight."
}

{
  "id": "line:044c477",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Weird,[p/] I've never had that problem either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5343",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Station"
}

{
  "id": "line:0383eba",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "There was a large cooking station here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0546e7d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "They must've prepared the meals in bulk here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e04a4",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Pots"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ab58a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "There was a set of pots for cooking soups and the like."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a82a7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Plates"
}

{
  "id": "line:0481777",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "They must've served the students' meals on these plates."
}

{
  "id": "line:05125de",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "It was a shame they had to close the kitchen due to the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2dde0",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Stuff"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1a791",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "There was a large sack of produce in the corner."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e5d14",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "There was some wine there, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0135f12",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "It must be for cooking...[p/] Or the professors."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f4933",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "I wanted to take a look around the kitchen,[p/] but Valentina seemed a little anxious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccadcf",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "Snooping around might've scared her off."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c760e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Examine",
  "text": "I needed to TALK to her before EXAMINING the kitchen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b809d8",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Necromancy on you"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8a08e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Magic on the body"
}

{
  "id": "line:02394f7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus,[p/] there appears to be traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on Bellwether’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7b9c9",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: T-[p/][s/]That’s because that necromancer killed her, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f52743",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: That’s the thing.[p/] If [i]that[/i] were true,[p/] a lot of the evidence we found doesn't make sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:038205f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I think someone [i]else[/i] cast a spell on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0159f09",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0981661",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "She became even more tense than before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3d394",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Is it possible that you saw someone use magic on Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8db47",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Definitely, not! [h=\"Calm down!|There’s no way they know!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5eb87",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Her thoughts were an open book now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efe287",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "If I beat her in an ARGUMENT,[p/] her thoughts might show me what she’s hiding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0070315",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Did you see something? (ARGUMENT)"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd75bb",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Could you tell us what happened when you and your sister discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057e228",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:008e216",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: My sister and I were heading to the west exit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0627c36",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: We saw the professor in a nearby classroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0848cfc",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Valentina: ...She was lying on the floor in a pool of blood. [h=\"It really scared me|seeing her like that...\" e=\"fsa\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7fa51",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I used an emergency communication device to call for help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0318275",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: While I was doing that,[p/] my sister tried to wake her up. [h=\"That <i>is</i> what happened...\" e=\"fs\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b08e43",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Was the professor still alive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fb62f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I don't know...[p/] But she wasn’t breathing,[p/] and she didn’t have a pulse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb9b0a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "She was less tense,[p/] which might imply that she was telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a62e92",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "It's possible the attack happened well before they discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0669e29",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Keeping your jobs"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ee66a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Did you ever feel like your job was at risk because of Bellwether?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d43c5",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] Why would you say that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0722dba",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It was just a hunch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0971dc3",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Valentina: Yeah?![p/][s/] W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] you're wrong!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e76ad",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "Valentina: [i]I[/i], for one, plan to work here until the day I die![p/][s/] Haha!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0791da7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Talk",
  "text": "She was clearly lying,[p/] but maybe it would be best to keep that to myself for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:023d657",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "TYRION: What do you know about the suspect in this case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04833d6",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "TYRION: His name is Wallace Nightgrave.[p/] He’s a student here."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fea6a",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...H-[p/][s/]He’s that scary necromancer, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f9d34",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: The one that makes zombies?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08232e4",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Those are just rumors.[p/] He wants to be a doctor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0229fb1",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: B-[p/][s/]But he studies [b]necromancy[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc581b",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you ever actually gotten to know him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a310f",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: No...[p/][s/] But I’ve heard the rumors![p/] He’s always hanging around the cemetery."
}

{
  "id": "line:061da42",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I’m sure he’s just biding his time...[p/] waiting for his chance to raise an army."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49720",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "It couldn't be helped that people thought of him that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:05834ef",
  "node": "ValWallTalk",
  "text": "[i]I[/i] still wasn't sure what to make of all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcabdd",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ... [h=\"Nothing good,|if that's what you're looking for...\" e=\"as\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03431d5",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Yet another set of negative emotions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0167aec",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Celeste: Just tell us the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a7cfb",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think we've talked to anyone who had anything nice to say about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3fc5e",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Yeah...[p/] She was a horrible person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babc37",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Valentina: She was really terrible to everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4b37e",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "TYRION: Did that include the academy staff?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05af398",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: She always treated us like her personal servants."
}

{
  "id": "line:0077b95",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Sometimes she’d make messes on purpose,[p/] just so she could order us to clean it up."
}

{
  "id": "line:038ea5f",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Valentina: I thought the kids from the noble houses were bad,[p/] but she was something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:057f9ed",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Valentina: She acted like she owned the place,[p/] but she wasn't even from a noble family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418b36",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Valentina: The only reason why she had [i]any[/i] power was because of her friends on the school board. [h=\"I just hope|we can still keep our jobs...\" e=\"sf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad0c2c",
  "node": "ValCathTalk",
  "text": "Interesting...[p/] Why would she be worried about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af00df",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: Scaled Lord, he's got a thing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0492ff7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:036ad8c",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: \"Pictures\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ecdc3",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: I do [i]not[/i] consent to having my picture taken.[p/] You are [i]legally[/i] not allowed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0716bda",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I wasn't planning to..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08de56d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] just put it away."
}

{
  "id": "line:079e157",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion|Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0999f64",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: So...[p/] Are you two like private investigators,[p/] or supermodels..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fae51",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"Supermodels\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:078f7ab",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "I'm not sure what gave her that idea,[p/] but it'd be best not to tell her that I planned on being Wallace's attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0025a18",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know Eris Illmater?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d55aa0",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: A-[p/]Ah,[p/][s/] she's even scarier than that necromancer!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0165d33",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: I've heard rumors about her, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ddbec",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: People who start talking to her end up missing or [i]worse[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02703e9",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: I feel it every time I'm around her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04df9a3",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: Something about her that fills me with dread..."
}

{
  "id": "line:099cb0b",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Have you actually spoken to her before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0326c54",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's a nice person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0386b7d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: N-[p/]No, thanks...[p/] I'm good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9c32f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about the headmaster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2a0f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: Oh.[p/] He's a really nice person."
}

{
  "id": "line:064d515",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: We would have never gotten a job here if it weren't for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaebf7",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f039e9",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: Yeah,[p/] he has connections with the local community center."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e5f33",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: He hires people from the commonfolk there to work at the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0739ed2",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Ms. Ianus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0732823",
  "node": "Kitchen_Present",
  "text": "Valentina: S-[p/]Sorry...[p/] I don't have much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:063a140",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hello?[p/] Is anyone there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b2cb6",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Be right there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:095c95d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Sorry,[p/] but the cafeteria is closed right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6c915",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Actually,[p/] we’re here to investigate what happened to Catherine Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3d5a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: We heard that two members of the kitchen staff discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:082ca85",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Her posture tensed at the mention of Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a9271",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Valentina: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] That would be me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:006cc9a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm Valentina."
}

{
  "id": "line:091854f",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "[i]She[/i] was the head chef of the kitchen?[p/] She was close to my age..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11d5c",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "I knew how picky nobles were,[p/] and I'd imagined that their children would be worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8621e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "If her cooking fit their standards,[p/] that was impressive in and of itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff58dd",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: How about your sister?[p/] Do you know where she is right now?[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5c93d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd like to get her statement, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f11e61",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] She’s somewhere else on campus right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0e72",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] If you’re with those knights,[p/] we’ve already told them everything we know."
}

{
  "id": "line:030f603",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Actually,[p/] we’re investigating separately from them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f39193",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I wanted to ask you some questions about what you saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af13de",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Sure... [h=\"I’m going to have to remember.|There were so many details.\" e=\"saf\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:007de6a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "What was that just now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c948b",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hello...?[p/] Is anyone there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010c47a",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It looks like there's no one here right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c905",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe we should check somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0987c30",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Those two are finally gone..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0326c36",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I can finally get some cleaning done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7a8aa",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "We approached the kitchen from afar,[p/] making sure that Valentina wouldn't spot us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fbb5e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "We were pretty far away,[p/] but Celeste had the eyes of a hawk.[p/] It must've been a skill she picked up from her days as a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0150c42",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: There she is, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeb36c",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7468",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Just...[p/] don’t shout that incantation like you always do."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9878",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I-[p/][s/]I know that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0704dfa",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: [i]Reperio Arcanum[/i]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:061bbce",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: What the...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0020236",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2bbf3",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s a trace of magic on her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2af36",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: I knew it...[p/] Which school of magic is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0913a8c",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: I-[p/]It’s...[p/][s/] [b]necromancy[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067308e",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: There’s a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0170085",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "CELESTE: Is she going to be okay?![p/][s/] What if the real killer cursed her or something?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:097d9e2",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "I still wasn't sure how this fit with everything,[p/] but if she was in danger,[p/] we were obligated to tell her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0319ee2",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: ...For now,[p/] let’s talk to her and see if she saw who cast that spell on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f14179",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: If all else fails,[p/] we can confront her with the evidence we have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd13ff",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "VALENTINA: O-[p/][s/]Oh?![p/][s/] It’s you two again! [h=\"They’re back?!\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:023ff6d",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Valentina: ... [h=\"Okay... Just relax.|I just need to repeat what I told them.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa6a52",
  "node": "Kitchen_Check",
  "text": "Unfortunately for her,[p/] she had far more troubling matters to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:03860d1",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "VALENTINA: T-[p/][s/]This is crazy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:073b6b3",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Why is there a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfdd85",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Did that guy curse me?![p/][s/] Am I going to become a zombie?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf43e5",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "That was strange...[p/] She seemed genuinely worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:05acda0",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "Was she really unaware that a spell was cast on her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f37d28",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "...No.[p/] She ran away when Celeste was going to scan the crime scene for magical traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ab04",
  "node": "ValDeduce",
  "text": "She knew that someone used magic on her,[p/] but she didn't know that the spell cast on her was [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:092b085",
  "node": "ValDeduceb",
  "text": "No...[p/] Valentina should have noticed someone casting a spell on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0635d26",
  "node": "ValDeduceb",
  "text": "She knows about the spell.[p/] She just didn’t know that it was [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f206a",
  "node": "ValDeduceb",
  "text": "What kind of magic would cause her to think that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c81fc",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/]Calm down, Ms. Ianus..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dbe43",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not all [b]necromancy[/b] spells relate to the undead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebdf04",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Healing spells are also from the school of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e75832",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "VALENTINA: \"Healing spells\"...? [h=\"Oh!|It was from that time she healed that cut!\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:066ecd7",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Someone healed a cut on her?[p/] Was that mage a student here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050cf61",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "VALENTINA: S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/][s/] I just remembered that there’s...[p/][s/] something else I have to do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0969175",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I-[p/][s/]I’ll be right back!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d9d0e",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Before we could say anything,[p/] she quickly walked out of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3c706",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "She seemed to really want to avoid talking about that mage,[p/] but why was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e626e",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "CELESTE: H-[p/][s/]Hey![p/][s/] We're not done talking to you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0285f3c",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Do you want me to just catch her?[p/] I'm pretty sure she can't outrun me."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fbb76",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "TYRION: The Inquisition is still patrolling the surrounding areas."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c6104",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They’d probably intervene if we started chasing one of the witnesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d58eb",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/] But we weren’t able to learn anything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0dde4",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "TYRION: Actually,[p/] I [i]did[/i] learn one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4baa8",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She has a friend who cast a healing spell on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df2597",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?![p/][s/] How did you figure that out?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2878c",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Good deductive reasoning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb6830",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, healing magic is also a form of [b]necromancy[/b], right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e6cc8",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: I guess that explains why there are magical traces on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d3e58",
  "node": "ValDeduce2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's a good thing a necromancer isn't actually trying to kill her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1558f",
  "node": "ValDeduce2b",
  "text": "000"
}

{
  "id": "line:0603083",
  "node": "ValDeduce2b",
  "text": "No...[p/] Valentina had traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfcad8",
  "node": "ValDeduce2b",
  "text": "That made her think she'd been secretly attacked,[p/] but someone had just healed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd0d2",
  "node": "ValDeduce2b",
  "text": "I'd considered that possibility until now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab187",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f9e8d",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: This whole time,[p/][s/] we’ve been wondering why there were traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on the body!"
}

{
  "id": "line:002e3b8",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: It wasn't because someone [i]attacked[/i] Bellwether with a [b]necromancy[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ffeb1",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: It was because someone used a [b]necromancy[/b] spell to try to [i]heal[/i] her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ddd66",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh...[p/] I get it.[p/] It doesn’t matter what type of [b]necromancy[/b] spell someone uses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0481023",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Traces from the same school of magic look exactly the same to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f538f7",
  "node": "ValDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s not just that.[p/] The body clearly bled at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a46b0",
  "node": "ValDeduce3b",
  "text": "No...[p/] There's no rule saying that healing spells require the target to be alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a54a2",
  "node": "ValDeduce3b",
  "text": "If a healing spell were used on a wounded person,[p/] what would happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c449e",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: What would happen if someone used a healing spell on an injured corpse?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d6df8",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "Celeste: It would close all of the body's wounds!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ccd43",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: In other words,[p/] it would remove any cuts or bruises!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05499ca",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "Celeste: So [i]that's[/i] why they couldn't find any wounds on her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0355445",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "CELESTE: Well,[p/] interrogating Valentina may have been a dead end,[p/] but at least it helped you figure that out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77e49",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: ...I’m not so sure that was a dead end."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f886f",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "CELESTE: What makes you say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6c9b",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: Why would she go to so much trouble to hide those traces on her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086243d",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s too coincidental.[p/] The wounds on the body were healed by an unknown person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7cd1f",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: And the person who [i]found[/i] the body is hiding the identity of a healing spell cast on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0124f9e",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "TYRION: What if they're the same person?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0833e11",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I doubt she'll give us the opportunity to find out for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed50ae",
  "node": "ValDeduce3c",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] she's definitely onto us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d74854",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "We'd done everything we could for now,[p/] and we had plenty of evidence to poke holes in the prosecution’s case."
}

{
  "id": "line:054f05d",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "And if that didn’t work,[p/] we'd just have to drag Valentina onto the stand and pull the truth out of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:001e212",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "She clearly knew more than she was letting on,[p/] and she wouldn't be able to run in a courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:015276e",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm telling you![p/][s/] That girl used magic to \"[i]scan[/i]\" me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc68b3",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: Calm down...[p/] We don't even know who they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d091d",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: Didn't you see them, Val?![p/][s/] Those two were unreasonably attractive!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08727af",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Okay?[p/] But what does that mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09721ff",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: They have to be nobles or [i]something[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3fe8f",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: Commoners don't look that good!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d6bcf",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: Tina,[p/] calm down..."
}

{
  "id": "line:032eb87",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina:  What if they find out what you did?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0442879",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: They can't prove anything.[p/] The Inquisition already has our alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7eb6",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Jan: Alibi?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8608b",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071de10",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: Oh,[p/] it's just you, Jan."
}

{
  "id": "line:04450e1",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Jan: What are you two talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0781ff4",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: W-[p/][s/]We were just talking about those two investigators!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0479ba2",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valentina: They're so weird, right?![p/][s/] Like why are they so attractive?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038bfca",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Why do you keep mentioning that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094dee7",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Jan: Investigators?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03832ea",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Jan: Oh, you mean that blond kid and the girl with the sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2392",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Valerie: They talked to you, didn't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080fecf",
  "node": "ValDeduce4",
  "text": "Jan: Yeah,[p/] they asked me a bunch of questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0107114",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: I think they're investigating Bellwether's murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2c0c2",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: ...W-[p/][s/]What did you tell them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0149",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: Oh, not much."
}

{
  "id": "line:037579d",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: I saw Bellwether a bit before you two found the body.[p/] So they wanted to know if I saw anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:040a813",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: [i]Did[/i] you see anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0015e3c",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: No idea...[p/] I just told them about how she shoved me before you two discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6ac95",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: After that,[p/] the guy just kept going on and on about \"getting to the truth\" and \"finding the other suspects\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0615886",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: Scaled Lord,[p/] I think I'm going to be sick......"
}

{
  "id": "line:05861e8",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: He seemed really interested when I told them Bellwether was going to fire us."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c607c",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: What?![p/][s/] Why would you tell them about that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0159309",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] It's not as if it makes any difference,[p/] right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088b65c",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: With Bellwether gone,[p/] I'm pretty sure we'll see a few more paychecks before they fire us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ed08",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina cursed under her breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0462e10",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: Damn it all...[p/] That's probably what [i]they're[/i] thinking too!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e01188",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: Are you okay?[p/] You don't look so good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd98e",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: Just go away, Jan![p/][s/] Don't you have work to do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef1c0",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: Ugh...[p/] Don't remind me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c31f01",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valerie: By the way, I made you lunch.[p/] It's on the front counter in the kitchen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f332a2",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Jan: Thanks...[p/] You're a lifesaver, Valerie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8460e",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
