{
  "id": "line:0400229",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: They have our motive,[p/] and they're going to find out what we did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9e1bb",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valerie: You don't know that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0107151",
  "node": "ValDeduce5",
  "text": "Valentina: Why did Jan have to go blabbing about Bellwether's plan to those two?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9d58f",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: And why do you keep making meals for him?![p/][s/] He doesn't even do anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adaa5e",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm just going to come out and say it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a1bba",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: I have to run a two-person kitchen every meal to feed these pampered kids!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e0448",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: He just lazes around and complains about his job!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0317d",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: Tina, he's overworked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d98fd4",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: Like hell, he's overworked![p/][s/] Every time I see him,[p/] he's either napping or barely working!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee5f29",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: Have you been around the campus?[p/] Have you ever seen it dirty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b51dc4",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/][s/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a824c1",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: He's the only custodian on staff,[p/] and the school board won't let the headmaster hire more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f18d",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: He barely has enough time to sleep.[p/] Why do you think he's so tired all of the time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03266ab",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: I-[p/][s/]I'm really sorry,[p/] I just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b17f",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: Are we really going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0467f9b",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: Everything is going to be fine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:095c3c2",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: We just need to do our best and keep our stories straight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1349",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: Have you been able to get into the library lately?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da899e",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] The knights are patrolling around it."
}

{
  "id": "line:027c7fc",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valentina: I was really hoping we could get one last study session for you before they fire us."
}

{
  "id": "line:025ebad",
  "node": "ValDeduce6",
  "text": "Valerie: Yeah...[p/] It's too bad."
}

{
  "id": "line:03faa2e",
  "node": "ValArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Valentina: L-[p/]Look...[p/]I [i]really[/i] don't know what you're talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:098f108",
  "node": "ValArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Valentina: I didn't see anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe22d0",
  "node": "ValArgument_Fail",
  "text": "I would have to do a better job of ARGUING against her points."
}

{
  "id": "line:0980e6c",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "Valentina clearly knew more than she was letting on."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac213",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "She found the body alongside her sister,[p/] and she reacted strangely when I mentioned someone may have used magic on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ce0a",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "What was she hiding?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1bfe6",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "Yes"
}

{
  "id": "line:0450047",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "No"
}

{
  "id": "line:076dd84",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus.[p/] From the very beginning,[p/] I’ve felt like you’ve been hiding something from us."
}

{
  "id": "line:040fca6",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "TYRION: There's something that you’re not telling us about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0368f58",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What are you talking about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d24f71",
  "node": "Val_Argument",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I’ve told you and the knights everything I know.[p/][s/] I’ve got nothing to hide! [h=\"My testimony was fine...\" e=\"af\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0774282",
  "node": "Val_Argument2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Ianus,[p/] it’s clear to anyone how nervous you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a84c",
  "node": "Val_Argument2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can practically [i]see[/i] the fear you’re emanating right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c12708",
  "node": "Val_Argument2",
  "text": "Valentina: U-[p/][s/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ed214",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "TYRION: Ms. Ianus.[p/][s/] What you’re saying and what you’re thinking are clearly different!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e0152",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "VALENTINA: ...What does that even mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0607544",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "TYRION: ...O[p/][s/]-Oh,[p/][s/] w-[p/][s/]well-"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0919a",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I don’t really know what you’re talking about,[p/] b-[p/][s/]but I’m telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:004fb7a",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "I needed to use the Eye of Horus to look at her thoughts and emotions."
}

{
  "id": "line:054bd12",
  "node": "Val_Argument2Fail",
  "text": "After I identified what exactly was inconsistent with the claim,[p/] I would need to choose the correct approach."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adaadc",
  "node": "Val_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: It's clear that you're hiding something from us.[p/] Just tell us the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c7224",
  "node": "Val_Argument3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Let’s say I [i]were[/i] hiding something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94040",
  "node": "Val_Argument3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Which I’m [i]not[/i],[p/][s/] by the way!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c9f66",
  "node": "Val_Argument3",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Why should I tell you anything?![p/][s/] You're not even with those knights!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d6ee0",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"You’ve already given your statement to the Inquisition. If the truth comes out, what do you think they’ll do when they realize you lied to them?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0daf414",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"My client is innocent. By withholding your testimony, you’re condemning him to a wrongful conviction.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:053eedf",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "TYRION: My client is innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff581d",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "TYRION: By withholding your testimony,[p/] you’re condemning him to a wrongful conviction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a954",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah![p/][s/] So, what?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3e9e2",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Why should I care about what happens to that necromancer?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f738f",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "She clearly didn't empathize with Wallace's situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:014b956",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"You have nothing to lose by telling us what happened. I know that you’re not the murderer, and I’ll make sure you’re protected.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bf8ea",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "TYRION: You have nothing to lose by telling us what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:075f5dc",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "TYRION: I know that you’re not the murderer,[p/] and I’ll make sure that you’re protected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0356f6a",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: You [i]say[/i] that,[p/] but what reason do I have to trust you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fc1ca",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I barely even know you two!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9f43",
  "node": "Val_Argument4",
  "text": "She [i]was[/i] right.[p/] She had very little reason to trust us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701d7d",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "TYRION: You’ve already given your statements to the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:031473d",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "TYRION: If the truth comes out,[p/] what do you think they’ll do when they realize you lied to them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092f4e7",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "TYRION: So,[p/] who are you protecting, Ms. Ianus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bae1a5",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: Y-[p/][s/]You talk a big game,[p/] but I bet you can’t actually [i]prove[/i] anything,[p/][s/] can you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0601739",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: You keep trying to say that I’m lying to protect someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee3baf",
  "node": "Val_Argument5",
  "text": "VALENTINA: I don’t even [i]know[/i] any mages,[p/] and I definitely didn’t see anyone use magic on the body!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d779f",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "ValTrace"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b381e5",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "TYRION: You can’t hide the truth from us, Ms. Ianus."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e8140",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "VALENTINA: W-[p/][s/]What...? [h=\"How do they know?!\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4a9ad",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "TYRION: You said that you’ve never even [i]seen[/i] a [b]necromancy[/b] spell before."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aec40",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "TYRION: If that were true,[p/][s/] why is there a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] [i]on[/i] you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bb78a",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "VALENTINA: What?![p/][s/] There’s a trace a [b]necromancy[/b] [i]on[/i] me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9c6aa",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "...What?[p/] She seemed to be genuinely surprised about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c57668",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "Was she unaware that a spell was cast on her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1893",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "No...[p/] If she didn’t know,[p/] she wouldn’t have avoided Celeste back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:093f58d",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "There had to be an explanation for that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea638f",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Ianus.[p/] You [i]know[/i] someone capable of casting magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4fee",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]this[/i] proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08dc9",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "Valentina: That doesn't prove anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0552080",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "Valentina: You're bluffing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79167",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "That wasn't the right piece of evidence to PRESENT."
}

{
  "id": "line:09be96f",
  "node": "Val_Argument6",
  "text": "I had definitive proof that she knows a mage.[p/] I needed to show it to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:037373b",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: The library is full of books for educational purposes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9a61d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: And books for recreational purposes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e41d8",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: You know...[p/] I never got to [i]finish[/i] that book."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8c650",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Since we're here—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e445e",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] Absolutely, not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb4998",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on!"
}

{
  "id": "line:072b270",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Back me up, Aria!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bb79e",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: I'm afraid I must agree with Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f104a",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: You tend to get very immersed in those books..."
}

{
  "id": "line:011620f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, that's rich coming from you.[p/] I bet you're sneaking peeks at it too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f057c6",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Nonsense.[p/] I would never do such a thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4a5d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...I already have my own copy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0720693",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/] And you're not sharing it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:099db6d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...You're very demanding sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d93a2",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tell me about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e3675",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/][s/] [i]Please[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bc8a0",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: You can even recommend some of [i]your[/i] favorite books to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c91d80",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: O-[p/][s/]Oh... [h=\"I mostly read teen romance,|but I can't let [i]her[/i] know that.\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03eed9f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "...I guess we all had different tastes."
}

{
  "id": "line:029029f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a holy text from the Church of Bahamut."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3a093",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I read some of these with Eris earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eee2aa",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: I've been meaning to ask.[p/] Do you guys worship dragons in Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7379",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never really been the religious type,[p/] but I've seen some devout worshippers in the capital."
}

{
  "id": "line:0405afc",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: It's the most prominent religion here."
}

{
  "id": "line:080c3c8",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: The Scaled Lord Rathallion is said to be the source of all arcane magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2932c",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: It's no wonder that he's such a large part of our culture."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b924d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Yet,[p/] worship of the celestial gods is forbidden..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0471f7b",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "I would need to find a way to learn more about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c77ec3",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are tables for students to sit at while they study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0888c16",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I don't think I could handle studying here day after day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4b14f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...Isn't traveling through the border heavily restricted?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03337a8",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Don't worry.[p/] I won't report you."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f73d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...I can't exactly [i]blame[/i] you for wanting to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca73f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Due to constant misuse of the Arcane Constructs' voice systems,[p/] voice lines can now only be set by Headmaster Redmond.\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8649a",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Is [i]that[/i] why I can't make the Constructs say what I want?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51ea2",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: The Constructs speak using Professor Bellwether's voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afce36",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: Unfortunately,[p/] that was an [i]open[/i] invitation to many of the students."
}

{
  "id": "line:021eefa",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: It wasn't long before the Constructs began speaking several obscenities using her voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f8a4f",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] that's kind of funny."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ccfec",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: It is,[p/] but this is a place of learning,[p/] not one of childish chicanery."
}

{
  "id": "line:0601979",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: But why is Headmaster Redmond the only person allowed to set the voice lines?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084c529",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Aria: ...There were also rumors that several [i]faculty[/i] members were partaking in these pranks."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c0300",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: That's also pretty funny."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c40b27",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "The library was full of books for educational purposes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09396a8",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "I'd spent all of yesterday morning combing through them for information about the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0786b54",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "The story I'd read about the \"Eye of Bahamut\" was in this book."
}

{
  "id": "line:008b66b",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "It was a table for students to sit at."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72023",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "I was studying here with Celeste yesterday morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0163104",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "Maybe I could travel with her when I was ready to take a break from this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3c9d",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "There's some sort of notice taped to one of the shelves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0871750",
  "node": "Library_Examine",
  "text": "\"Due to constant misuse of the Arcane Constructs' voice systems,[p/] voice lines can now only be set by Headmaster Redmond.\"."
}

