  "text": "ARIA: Just so we're clear,[p/] I wasn't acting to protect the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:086f953",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: But I’ll admit that Miriam Frega [i]was[/i] the other witness that saw Bellwether that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067e0f",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I see...[p/] I had some suspicions but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03954d6",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: There’s also another matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed4ce",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Steelwind tensed once again.[p/] She was still hesitant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d308dc",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...When I was investigating the body,[p/] I found this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eec260",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What the...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70601",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: It looks like Miriam's been cheating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea6ed7",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: But why would Bellwether have something like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7bc2",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: From the way it’s arranged in this folder,[p/] I think it might have been blackmail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe84e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Miriam Frega is considered a prodigy in the practice of [b]conjuration[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfbec4",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: She’s won a litany of awards,[p/] and she will most definitely graduate with honors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1dbf9",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: If these files were to reach the public,[p/] it would absolutely ruin her reputation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f013c0",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Do you think that the professor was trying to threaten her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bada9",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: It appears so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c02b78",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: When I discovered this,[p/] several elements of the case were still unknown."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c45fb",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: That's when I found [i]this[/i] in Wallace Nightgrave's locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:037bcf1",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: This is...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a813c",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: It’s very likely that [i]this[/i] was the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad71a",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: This rapier is a valuable family heirloom for House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9c7e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: And a few weeks ago,[p/] Miriam reported that the rapier was stolen from her room."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ccaf6",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: But why was it found in Wallace’s locker...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e814e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Not that I’m complaining,[p/] but why didn’t you PRESENT this in court?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d52f2",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: To be honest,[p/] I’d like to avoid involving House Frega by any means necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:095e1a7",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: I knew it![p/][s/] You’re just protecting her, aren’t you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:055cf87",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Ms. McCoy.[p/] Do you recall how Wyverngarde's justice system works?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9594b",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: To acquit a defendant,[p/] you need to unequivocally prove that they didn’t commit the crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ad65",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: To do that,[p/] they either need a solid alibi-"
}

{
  "id": "line:021dcdb",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Or we need to prove that someone [i]else[/i] committed the crime..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdadd8",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: What do you suppose will happen if you bring Miriam Frega onto the stand?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f82307",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: House Frega won’t allow one of its members to be indicted in a court of law."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cedd0",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: They’ll plant and forge evidence to implicate your defendant,[p/] and they’ll use the Inquisition to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0514be0",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Even [i]I[/i] wouldn't be able to stop them,[p/] should it come to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a3d29",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: So [i]that’s[/i] why you’ve been keeping them away from the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9d55",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Can’t [i]you[/i] do anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f44563",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: I thought the Steelwinds were powerful, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7de8e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I don’t have the support of my House."
}

{
  "id": "line:09eabc7",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Aria: Right now,[p/] I'm just a prosecutor,[p/] nothing more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f85dc2",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Steelwind.[p/] You [i]know[/i] that this isn’t fair for us."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9221",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Just do nothing.[p/][s/] Do nothing and let us win!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e56d72",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e6789",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: If we can't go after Miriam,[p/][s/] then you can at least help us save Wallace!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087e361",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I’m [i]not[/i] going to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2dca",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Why?![p/][s/] What if Miriam Frega is the real killer?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4379",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Her sword is the murder weapon [i]and[/i] Bellwether was trying to blackmail her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0261d43",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I seem to recall [i]another[/i] case where an innocent person’s sword was used to frame them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b74dc",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: T-[p/][s/]That’s...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e1125",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: As a prosecutor,[p/] it is [i]not[/i] my place to decide who’s guilty and who’s not."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad154",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I won’t engage in corruption,[p/] even if it’s to counter corruption from another noble house."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c2307",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...I’m sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e134b9",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Do you know where Miriam is right now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c97c0e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Did you not hear what I just said?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f317f",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: You can’t let her think that there’s even the [i]slightest[/i] possibility you’ll indict her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2e5d",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: She’ll bring the entire wrath of House Frega down on you.[p/] I won't be able to protect you if that happens."
}

{
  "id": "line:067fcc0",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: I don't need your protection,[p/] and I can’t do anything for Wallace unless I know everything that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc01e4",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Frega has the last piece I need to put everything together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0090546",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Well, I suppose I don’t have much of a choice, do I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9af91",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Her dormitory is room 107.[p/] I imagine that she’ll be there,[p/] considering that classes are suspended."
}

{
  "id": "line:02914fa",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Thank you, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c52925",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: If I don’t tell you,[p/] I’m sure you’ll probably just find out using some other means..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecc0fe",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: But please, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] exercise caution."
}

{
  "id": "line:04358bb",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Any Leads?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042fa7d",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Have you had any luck finding the scene of the crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e72e4",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Unfortunately,[p/] I haven’t."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79ecf",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: From the witness’ testimonies,[p/] we have a rough idea of the route Bellwether took."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3766b",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: But none of the rooms we’ve checked have any sign of a struggle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0876845",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Why are you so sure that a struggle happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069b1f0",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I'm mainly basing that off of the Ianus sisters’ testimonies."
}

{
  "id": "line:064676d",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Valerie,[p/] in particular,[p/] noticed that the bleeding came from a wound in her chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0991129",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Regrettably,[p/] the body’s wounds were mended."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4d3ae",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: So, we can’t determine what kind of weapon the murderer used."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a27958",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Other Witness"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd0a5c",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: During the trial,[p/] you mentioned that another witness saw Bellwether walking around yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0675d83",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Who is this person,[p/] and why haven't they been called to testify?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09019c5",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...I’m sorry,[p/] but I can’t tell you that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e56f91",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Steelwind's posture tightened.[p/] Something was making her uneasy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bb3dc",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You've been pretty transparent with your investigation so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b8c0e",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I have no obligation to justify myself to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d33c07",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: Nor do I have an obligation to help the opposition."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3888",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Didn’t we have a deal?[p/] Hiding information doesn’t exactly seem fair to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3cbb6",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I believe I’ve given you plenty of information already."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2dc83",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ...So regardless of what I said before,[p/] the answer is still “no”. [h=\"Her family is dangerous.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bffff",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus caught a stray thought from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb916",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "“[i]Her[/i] family is dangerous”?[p/] What did she mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:087cfd2",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Is there something about this witness’s family that you’re worried about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26ef8",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: ... [h=\"No...|This could be a feint.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c48a3",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "ARIA: I’m sorry,[p/] but you’ll have to try harder than that if you want to bluff me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a77a3",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Why would she go to such lengths to hide one witness's identity?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed336f",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "She was perfectly fine with revealing elements of the investigation yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:095a681",
  "node": "Library_Talk",
  "text": "Maybe I needed to try looking somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf48c7",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: Oh.[p/] It’s you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:09868fb",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind?[p/] What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8ac74",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "I once again came across Steelwind.[p/] Like yesterday,[p/] she was the only one in the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0ecd",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "But was she seriously carrying out the investigation alone here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044e8e3",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "Searching the classroom was one thing,[p/] but searching this entire library seemed a little ridiculous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abbae6",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: After what happened at the trial yesterday,[p/] I decided it would be best to start my investigation here."
}

{
  "id": "line:042a4a9",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "Wallace [i]was[/i] in the library for the entire morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:042a6d7",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "If she was insistent that he did it,[p/] this would probably be the best place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d40c97",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: Actually,[p/] since I have you here,[p/] have you seen Eris Illmater anywhere?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0145f35",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: It’s my understanding that you're both acquainted with each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d669e7",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Eris?[p/] What do you want with her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c311de",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: It’s not for anything serious, mind you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec610b",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: It’s just that oaf of a commander lost her [b]Spell Compendium[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02702b6",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: Now we need her to produce another one for our records."
}

{
  "id": "line:0322723",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: If you see her,[p/] please let her know that we’d like to speak to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2d0d9",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: We saw her earlier in the cemetery nearby,[p/] but I have no idea where she is now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e2fa",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: Ugh...[p/] Once again,[p/] I have to compensate for that idiot’s mistakes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e69253",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: ...Anyways,[p/] I was wondering if I could ask you some questions about the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef742",
  "node": "Library_Check",
  "text": "ARIA: ...Very well.[p/] I suppose I still need to honor our deal from earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d7938",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should have enough information now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067389",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's have a talk with the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bedc72",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Valerie: Please just tell me what's wrong![p/][s/] Are you mad at me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0215d6f",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm not mad, okay?![p/][s/] Can we just get to work?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:029e47a",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "The twins' voices rang out from the kitchen.[p/] They sounded like they were in an argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a758bc",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think they're okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0874166",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Celeste: It sounds private.[p/] We shouldn't get involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:006a312",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c9326",
  "node": "IanusScene",
  "text": "I slowly closed the door to the library and kept my mind on the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0110773",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: Fine.[p/][s/] You want to know what I think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1fa2",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: You don't get to say that you hate magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3a4c",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: Look at how many problems it's causing for us."
}

{
  "id": "line:07733fe",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: Yeah...[p/][s/] For this dumb job![p/] [i]None[/i] of this even matters for you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:098d5b0",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: Those people from the Church always say that \"mages are chosen by divine right\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d33090",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: And they're right![p/][s/] You don't get to complain about being better than me, Val!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064a160",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: I'm not [i]better[/i] than you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06eb10f",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: Yes, you are,[p/][s/] and I'm so sick of pretending you're not!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c50af8",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: You were helping Jan while I was jealous of how easy I [i]thought[/i] his job was!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a086ae",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: You outed yourself as a mage trying to save Catherine [i]bloody[/i] Bellwether!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aff8f5",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: Tina,[p/] that's not—"
}

{
  "id": "line:028e764",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: ...I hate how much I'm holding you back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0909530",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: I know you![p/][s/] I know how hard you've been working in the library!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0962bf1",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: You're destined for great things!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6c80",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: Tina,[p/] I haven't learned anything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec729c",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: Come on![p/][s/] Don't give me that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ee20",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: You've been heading straight to the library after work for years!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf580b",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: Yeah,[p/] and I [i]still[/i] haven't learned anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:060cd1b",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valentina: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8e485",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: I can't wrap my head around how it all works.[p/][s/] I've been trying to for years..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff9e1e",
  "node": "IanusScene2",
  "text": "Valerie: I don't understand \"aether\".[p/] I don't understand \"spell formulas\".[p/] It's like they're speaking another language."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b465a8",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: I can do magic,[p/] but I'm nothing like the students here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3e550",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: But you know healing magic..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3c2c",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: It's the most basic spell.[p/] Children in the theurgy program learn that in their first class."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f82d49",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: It took me years to even figure [i]that[/i] out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0558a73",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: ...Why didn't you ever tell me about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0106c55",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: Because magic is the only thing I have.[p/] You're better than me at [i]everything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0770b8b",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: What?[p/] [i]I'm[/i] not—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cec7f9",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: I'm always making mistakes and forcing you to clean up after me."
}

{
  "id": "line:023b610",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: We only have this job because you begged the headmaster to hire me with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bda77c",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: You're amazing...[p/] The students here are spoiled aristocrats and they [i]love[/i] your food."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a517d4",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: I can't even fry an egg right.[p/] [i]You're[/i] not the one holding us back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0319f64",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: ...Do you really think my cooking is that good?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ecf4",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: I don't think I could live without eating your food every day."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f35e8",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: Remember when I was just learning to cook at the orphanage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfa736",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: We were just a pair of dumb kids,[p/] but you were there with me every step of the way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0538b5b",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: You were there for me.[p/] I would've never gotten this good if you weren't always with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:053d225",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: Tina..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd85c2",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm sorry I never told you this sooner.[p/] I could never do this without you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0641fca",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: ...Neither could I."
}

{
  "id": "line:012d802",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: I'm sorry for being so stupid before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0460ba4",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: It's okay...[p/] I was also being—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07491d3",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valerie: We should get started on that soup."
}

{
  "id": "line:075de59",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "Valentina: Right.[p/] Can you help me grab all the leftover meat from the freezer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028b080",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "ARIA: Oh?[p/] You’re back."
}

{
  "id": "line:091f0ee",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "TYRION: We’ve uncovered a few things during our investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d71dd",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind...[p/] Are you acquainted with a student named Miriam Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6a9b",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "She shifted slightly.[p/] It was subtle,[p/] but I could see her discomfort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7e95b",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "ARIA: ... [h=\"Hmph...|I underestimated him...\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5d5f6",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "ARIA: ...I said it before, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I won’t fall for such an obvious bluff."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3aea1",
  "node": "IanusScene3",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s not a bluff, Steelwind,[p/] and I’ll prove it using the evidence we’ve gathered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0116955",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Aria: It doesn't matter how many accusations you make."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b9fa",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Aria: I'm under no obligation to share those details with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b54fb",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] She still wasn't budging..."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f7d1",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "Steelwind was paranoid,[p/] and for whatever reason,[p/] it was due to the involvement of Miriam Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b3d5e",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "If I could convince her to reveal why she’s being so secretive,[p/] she might give me more information."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed95d4",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ve been behaving strangely, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fe915",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even the knights of the Inquisition have noticed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a154e7",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just tell me the truth.[p/] Why are you being so paranoid?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2df31",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "ARIA: I’m not sure what you’re trying to imply, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ae121",
  "node": "Aria_Argument",
  "text": "ARIA: I’ve prosecuted the defendant the same way I've always have."
}

{
  "id": "line:082d5e1",
  "node": "Aria_Argument2",
  "text": "SteelOrd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3efd",
  "node": "Aria_Argument2",
  "text": "Aria: ...And what is this supposed to be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a4797",
  "node": "Aria_Argument2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear evidence that your behavior has changed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d3cb3",
  "node": "Aria_Argument2",
  "text": "ARIA: Please.[p/] What kind of fool do you take me for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01946ea",
  "node": "Aria_Argument2",
  "text": "ARIA: I’ve already told you.[p/] Your bluffs won’t work on me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bccaf",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: You’ve ordered the knights to stay away from the crime scene,[p/] and you’ve even taken it upon yourself to conduct the investigation yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cfaf6",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: That is [i]not[/i] normal behavior for a prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b5ec3",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "ARIA: I took those actions because the Inquisition is incompetent."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b7e54",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "ARIA: How could I possibly trust them with anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18da6",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: The knights [i]are[/i] incompetent,[p/] but even you can see the value of delegation."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dd9ab",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: During Celeste’s case,[p/] you still delegated tasks to the Inquisition.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f3de0",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You could have easily investigated the McCoy Tavern yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0839b75",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "TYRION: This academy is huge.[p/] You wouldn’t conduct your investigation this way unless you had a good reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7bbd5",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "Aria: Then why don’t you enlighten me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51a9c",
  "node": "Aria_Argument3",
  "text": "Aria: What would cause me to behave so \"strangely\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091561c",
  "node": "Aria_Argument4",
  "text": "Miriam|Four"
}

{
  "id": "line:005be20",
  "node": "Aria_Argument4",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]This[/i] is the reason why you've been acting so strangely, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff41de",
  "node": "Aria_Argument4",
  "text": "Aria: What kind of weak-willed person do you think I am?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e262e1",
  "node": "Aria_Argument4",
  "text": "ARIA: Something like [i]that[/i] would hardly cause me to change my behavior."
}

{
  "id": "line:020360f",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know that the Inquisition is corrupt and will bend to the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:09232f9",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, what would happen if a powerful noble were publicly involved in this case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9cfed",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: With that noble’s influence,[p/] they’d probably order the Inquisition to conceal their involvement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0363e17",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: A high-profile noble is involved in this case, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b469d7",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I believe that noble is Miriam Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:010401e",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Aria: Again with this.[p/] Do you think you can bluff me by throwing out the names of random nobles?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0910dea",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Aria: Not every noble is a malevolent criminal like Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfefed",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Aria: I’ve said it before,[p/] and I’ll say it again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c436b5",
  "node": "Aria_Argument5",
  "text": "Aria: Nothing about this case has anything to do with House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:071831a",
  "node": "Aria_Argument6",
  "text": "LockerBlood2|LockerBlood"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b7182",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then how do you explain this, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037a957",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The commander told us that you were following a lead in the locker room yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b03529",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: We investigated the lockers of students from the Four Pillar families."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b523b0",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: And we found stains of blood in a locker with [i]Miriam Frega’s[/i] id number,[p/] and it was presumably left by a bloody object."
}

{
  "id": "line:098db00",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The bloody object must have been taken by someone,[p/] and you became extremely paranoid after you found something in the locker room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b84fde",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I had to guess,[p/] I’d say that [i]you[/i] took the bloody object as evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:075eb00",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "ARIA: ...And what evidence do you have to support these outrageous claims?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52c54",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "TYRION: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7b4f",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "ARIA: The only thing you have is evidence of a bloodstain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9b9f1",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "ARIA: There is a myriad of explanations for that.[p/] Everything else you mentioned is pure speculation."
}

{
  "id": "line:087a1e9",
  "node": "Aria_Argument7",
  "text": "Aria: I could have found any number of things in that room.[p/] Or possibly nothing at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0639f22",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"If you don’t present what you found to the court, I’ll have no choice but to pull the “owner” of that locker onto the stand.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db0866",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You found an object in the locker with Miriam Frega’s nameplate on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0087b37",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you don’t present what you found to the court,[p/] I’ll have no choice but to pull the “owner” of that locker onto the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e92f8",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: That’s ridiculous.[p/][s/] We both know that the locker in question belongs to Wallace Nightgrave."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0972",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can [i]you[/i] unequivocally prove that, Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd2111",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because the way I see it,[p/] there’s a lot of room for doubt there."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9f43",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Enough doubt for me to pull Lady Frega onto the witness stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a072ff",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ebfbc",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if I had more context,[p/] maybe I wouldn’t have to resort to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06077a9",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Her brow furrowed for a bit.[p/] She was searching for a counterargument."
}

{
  "id": "line:056fe9c",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "But she just exhaled in resignation.[p/] I'd finally gotten her."
}

{
  "id": "line:064dd12",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "ARIA: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] ...Well played, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b8c90",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "ARIA: I suppose I don’t have a choice, do I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bed0b",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"You’re hiding evidence, Ms. Steelwind?! Do you not see how wrong that is?!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b6ed5",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’re hiding evidence, Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7479f",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you not see how wrong that is?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0300a8b",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: You don't have any proof to support your accusations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faad39",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: Show me hard evidence instead of making baseless claims."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b20b4",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Logic [c=\"Let’s not be coy, Ms. Steelwind. Anyone can tell that the bloodstain is the most notable thing in that room.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:091df82",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let’s not be coy, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8c38c",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyone can tell that the bloodstain is the most notable thing in that room."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c4a52",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: How are you so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad7145",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: You weren’t there with me during my investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e120f2",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Aria: As I’ve said,[p/] any number of things could have happened to change my behavior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a027c4",
  "node": "Aria_Argument8",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] She was playing devil’s advocate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a174",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh.[p/] There's an Arcane Construct in the back here."
}

{
  "id": "line:06666dd",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's probably here to aid the students."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a1303",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] I don't think it's relevant to our investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa4b0e",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Just in case,[p/] I made a note of it in my Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed06a5",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I used the legend that the commander gave me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c549e",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I looked carefully across the list to find the names of some notable students."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8426",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Wallace Nightgrave"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cc7ee",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I opened the locker with Wallace’s ID number."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aca0fc",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Inside,[p/] I found a bottle of fragrant liquid and something that looks like a makeup kit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b60584",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Huh...[p/] Why does Wallace have this stuff?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d774b5",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "It [i]did[/i] seem strange,[p/] but it wasn't my place to judge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5a3bc",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I should take a look through the other lockers."
}

{
  "id": "line:02579a8",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Miriam Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:0860b61",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I opened the locker with Miriam Frega’s ID number."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d87de8",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Inside,[p/] I found several stacks of worn-out textbooks and notebooks."
}

{
  "id": "line:05148f3",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: Wait a minute...[p/] These notebooks all have Wallace’s name on them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d828d0",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I opened the notebook and quickly scanned through its pages."
}

{
  "id": "line:040657f",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "It appeared to be notes on the art of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d731ad",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: These are Wallace’s notebooks."
}

{
  "id": "line:059368d",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: But why are they in Miriam Frega’s locker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050469e",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Did she steal his things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0901b",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "What was going on here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cedf4",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I began taking all of the textbooks and notebooks,[p/] one after another."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ce108",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "The locker was really cramped,[p/] but then I noticed a stain near the back of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ea361",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I quickly took everything out to get a better look at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07521c8",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ce16",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: I think this is dried blood..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e993c",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Celeste scan it for traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:09adb95",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: No,[p/] there aren't any traces on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ebe13",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Jaiden von Sanctus"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b09f2",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I opened the locker with Jaiden von Sanctus’s ID number."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d7206",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Inside,[p/] I found several bottles of some kind of transparent lotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe1ad",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: ...There’s nothing but lotion in here,[p/] and also a distinct smell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0137f9d",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a53865",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: I wonder why a student would need this much lotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:09474ae",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I took one of the bottles to inspect it more closely."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e055d",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: W-[p/][s/]Wait, Tyrion![p/][s/] Don’t touch those with your hands!"
}

{
  "id": "line:044230b",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: From the label,[p/] it appears to be some kind of sanitizing liquid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea7a76",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s a little strange,[p/] but it doesn’t seem to be related to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0381524",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Warren Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:0beeb93",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I opened the locker with Warren Sibyl’s ID number."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5e787",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "Inside,[p/] I found some textbooks and a neatly stacked deck of tarot cards."
}

{
  "id": "line:053fa1f",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh.[p/] It’s like those cards that fortune tellers use."
}

{
  "id": "line:021a3e2",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: I wonder if this student studies [b]divination[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a90e3",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "TYRION: But anyways,[p/] I don’t think this is related to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2a2cc",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "There were several lockers in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:040968f",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "It'd be a waste of time to search through them all without any leads."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09abb",
  "node": "Lockers_Examine",
  "text": "I should speak with Commander White first."
}

{
  "id": "line:03be4d3",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Headmaster"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d63f98",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What was the headmaster talking to you about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:087ea65",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: He has some items stored in one of the faculty lockers."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fe126",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: The problem is,[p/] Steelwind said no one gets in or out of this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91158",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: ...Except for her and you two, I guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:04978e9",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: She won’t even let the other knights in here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d31fb",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Really?[p/] Is that normal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ba7ac",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Nope,[p/] but things rarely are when she’s calling the shots.[p/] I just go with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e4dd",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Why would she give [i]me[/i] access to the crime scene if she wasn’t even letting the knights in?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0398687",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: I don’t know what her deal is,[p/] but she’s been acting strange lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:01deae9",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: She’s been really paranoid, that girl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0370586",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Frankly,[p/] I can't tell what’s going through her head."
}

{
  "id": "line:011c567",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Steelwind's Paranoia"
}

{
  "id": "line:0574770",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: You mentioned that the prosecutor has been paranoid lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c6ac3",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Do you think it has something to do with this case?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08831b5",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Nah,[p/] it started way before that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07997fa",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Lately,[p/] she’s been using the Inquisition to investigate a lot of non-magical homicides."
}

{
  "id": "line:0728bc3",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: What...?[p/] Wouldn’t it be easier to work with the relevant law enforcement for that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0334583",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: I don’t know why,[p/] but she’s convinced that these cases have magic involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dae8f7",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: But every time we scan one of those crime scenes,[p/] nothing turns up."
}

{
  "id": "line:043b422",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: ...I got to say, though.[p/] If it weren’t for the scans,[p/] I might actually agree with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0026021",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Why do you say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0930ea1",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Those homicides...[p/] I haven’t ever seen [i]anything[/i] like them."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ebc16",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: They’re probably some of the most screwed-up cases I’ve ever handled,[p/] and I've seen some things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183179",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: For one of those cases,[p/] we had ourselves a disgruntled spouse."
}

{
  "id": "line:011a487",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: She found out that her man was going around town with a barkeep,[p/] if you catch my meaning."
}

{
  "id": "line:057066c",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] What [i]do[/i] you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038e6e9",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: They were making the beast with two backs."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cff7e",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a90e4",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: He was two-timing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2c3e",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know this lingo, Orym."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abf670",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god![p/][s/] He was a married man having sex with another woman, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b52bd7",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...![p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa40d9",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: [i]Anyways[/i],[p/] you know what the spouse does?[p/] She stalks the poor woman."
}

{
  "id": "line:022d940",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: She started leaving threatening notes all around where she worked."
}

{
  "id": "line:084ca5a",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: The barkeep told the City Watch all about what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a587a0",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: But no matter how much they staked out the tavern,[p/] they could never catch her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0087",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Then one day,[p/] the barkeep arrived home."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a6e44",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Little did she know,[p/] the spouse was waiting there for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bbf7b",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: The poor lady never had a chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d92e00",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Then to tie the whole thing together,[p/] the spouse waits for her husband to get home."
}

{
  "id": "line:088cd02",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: She cooks him a big meat pie,[p/] using the barkeep's remains."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c62080",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Possible Explanation"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a9c84",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "CELESTE: Wow...[p/] That story is pretty..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8f8c",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0010f9d",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Steelwind thinks someone’s developed a new type of magic that can control people’s minds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad262c",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: And these homicides were some kind of sick test run."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ea017",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "...Magic that can affect people’s minds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78f5b",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wouldn't Mageblight make more sense?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099722d",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mageblight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090f8e9",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: When a mage overuses their magic,[p/] it can have pretty bad consequences on their mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0021614",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They temporarily lose grip of reality,[p/] and begin seeing things that aren't there."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f5d49",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: When a mage becomes like that,[p/] it almost never ends well.[p/] They basically become psychotic."
}

{
  "id": "line:065ad97",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They enter a frenzy and begin firing spells randomly,[p/] which only makes it worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace699",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: I've seen my fair share of Mageblight cases,[p/] and [i]this[/i] wasn’t like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03984b2",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Not all of the perps were mages,[p/] and the ones that were,[p/] didn’t even use their spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:04330f6",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: One thing was that each of the perps almost seemed to wake up after we arrested them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0192e4e",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: All of them said things like [s/]“It wasn’t me!”[p/] or [s/]“I didn't have a choice!”."
}

{
  "id": "line:037afac",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: They \"didn't have a choice\"?[p/] What could that mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76cd1",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: I doubt it \"means\" anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2727d",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Sometimes people can’t face the things they’ve done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644b11",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: It’s easier to say that you had no control than to take responsibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ea82d",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Secret Witness"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d53f8",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "I wondered if I could mislead the commander into revealing who the secret witness is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb5a48",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: During the trial,[p/] Steelwind mentioned that someone other than Jan Hughes saw Bellwether walking around."
}

{
  "id": "line:071f479",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "TYRION: Have you seen them around lately?[p/] We wanted to speak with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:081d9af",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:067848e",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Hah.[p/] Nice try, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0346e2f",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Well...[p/] It was worth a shot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a069",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: Honestly,[p/] I couldn’t tell you if I wanted to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2aa15",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: I don’t think anyone other than Steelwind knows who this witness is."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9772",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "ORYM: [i]I[/i] sure as hell don’t."
}

{
  "id": "line:0581d7e",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "What?[p/] She was even hiding it from the Inquisition Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78607",
  "node": "Lockers_Talk",
  "text": "Why was she being so secretive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c3fa0",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: ...Kid,[p/] are you going to show me this thing every time we meet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088721c",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It proves I'm an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22c8a",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:01721db",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Seriously,[p/] you're just like Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0647e5b",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...She does this, too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061578d",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I didn't expect to see you two again so soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e38d51",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering our careers,[p/] we'll probably be seeing a lot more of each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d997fb",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: ...Well, between you and Tymora,[p/] [i]you're[/i] a lot less insufferable to be around."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f7e40",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I was surprised to see [i]you[/i] again, mage girl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5a3f",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I have a name, you know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9548e",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0419963",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: So, what are you doing around the kid [i]this[/i] time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5951",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Are you two...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02450da",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm working as Tyrion's bodyguard now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0330173",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Really?[p/] With [i]your[/i] record?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0694cfe",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I figured you'd be back in the Eastern Kingdoms after your acquittal."
}

{
  "id": "line:074e2ee",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: No.[p/] I'm trying to keep my work in Wyverngarde for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa24d4",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: My mom's all alone after what happened..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8cc88",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: ...Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f423b",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Steelwind|SteelOrd"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9b13",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Man...[p/] Steelwind's really wound up today."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f35ee",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I don't know what her deal is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:045a19e",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is she not normally like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a31e7",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Not usually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfeef2",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Or at least not [i]this[/i] much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736176",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: By the way,[p/] have you two seen Eris Illmater around?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9f895",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Steelwind mentioned what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:097d741",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] She has really been on my case about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:063f29f",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I can't believe I lost her [b]Compendium[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1ff79",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: But I guess it's mostly my fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd4511",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We saw her at the cemetery earlier,[p/] but I have no idea where she is now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babed9",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Damn it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07701c4",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Player: Wallace|Catherine Autopsy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0208dd0",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Look, kid...[p/] I know you always \"believe in your clients\" and all, but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:082ee75",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I can't believe you're defending a [i]necromancer[/i] of all people."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0c28",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: There [i]has[/i] to be a limit to that “compassion” of yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:002f383",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wallace has his reasons for studying [b]necromancy[/b].[p/] I trust him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab1adb",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Even though you just met him yesterday?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033bbfd",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think that I'm a good judge of character.[p/] There's no way he killed Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f441d",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Whatever you say, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0355b52",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Player: Lockdown"
}

{
  "id": "line:0325b6e",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was there really no way for you to breach the academy during the lockdown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a2a4e",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] Those [b]abjuration[/b] barriers are top-notch."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b19a1",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: They were paid for by the nobility, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b60706",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I bet Lucio Steelwind could drop a meteor on it,[p/] and it wouldn't even make a dent."
}

{
  "id": "line:05650c3",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I’m sorry...[p/] He could drop a [i]what[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f94697",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Player: Valentina|Valerie|ValTrace"
}

{
  "id": "line:0251c0b",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Ugh...[p/] Those twins really screwed me over with what they did."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3909",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Steelwind's going to hold this over me for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cd809",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't exactly blame you for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c24b",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Twins are such a rare occurrence.[p/] I doubt even the Inquisition has dealt with that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0492fe1",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Ugh...[p/] You always know just how to piss off the right people, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0479177",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: We're [i]still[/i] trying to clean up the mess you made with House Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:081689b",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cc53a",
  "node": "Lockers_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Sorry, kid.[p/] I don't have much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0663684",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "We spent some time wandering through the academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c21d95",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "That's when we overheard a conversation from a nearby room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4c1e4",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: From what I understand,[p/] Ms. Steelwind has already moved the investigation elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb8ba0",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: How long must I wait before I can retrieve my things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b5ac6",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "ORYM: Sorry, old-timer.[p/] Orders are orders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0f7c",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "ORYM: Nothing comes in or out till this case is over and done with."
}

{
  "id": "line:086da89",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: Commander White?[p/] And the headmaster too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015578d",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: Oh...[p/] Hello, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:003c30a",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "ORYM: Hey, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b012fd",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] In any case,[p/] there are other matters I must attend to."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f40d5",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "THEODORE: Please inform me when I can reclaim my things."
}

{
  "id": "line:071ef6a",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "ORYM: Sure thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f09f9",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "It looked like Commander White was standing guard in front of this locker room."
}

{
  "id": "line:085108b",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "But it didn't look like he's conducting [i]any[/i] sort of investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dffe1d",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "Was he here on Steelwind’s orders?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0253fc0",
  "node": "Lockers_Check",
  "text": "He might be able to tell us who this secret witness was."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cda80",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "It seemed like the commander didn't know who this secret witness was, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db774f",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "CELESTE: Ugh...[p/] This isn’t getting us anywhere..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef1845",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind’s behavior [i]is[/i] strange, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:029e7eb",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "Perhaps we could try analyzing her behavior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607754",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "If I did that,[p/] I might be able to figure out why she's acting so strangely."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a1ade",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Let's take a moment to work through this."
}

{
  "id": "line:084dc8a",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind’s behavior has been strange this time around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0299e38",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: She’s hiding elements of the case,[p/] even from the commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d71a96",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Anyone can tell that she doesn’t have much faith in him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0313d2d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "ORYM: I’m...[p/] standing right here."
}

{
  "id": "line:079d1f9",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: But this is the first time I’ve seen her hide key details of a case from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0718ef8",
  "node": "LockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: There has to be a reason why she’s being so secretive."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f704d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "1"
}

{
  "id": "line:06411b8",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Steelwind might have had a habit of micromanaging the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bd7ba",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "But she had [i]always[/i] delegated tasks to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0818ae8",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "This time is different.[p/] Something was stopping her from utilizing them."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e55a1",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd8578",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] This academy was a large building."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d2688",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "No matter how competent she was,[p/] she couldn't possibly carry out a search of this scale by herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:090996d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce2",
  "text": "From a logical standpoint,[p/] it would make more sense for her to utilize the entirety of the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ecf88",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her actions must be driven by paranoia.[p/] She’s been hoarding information about the case, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f0a25",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s only one reason why she wouldn’t utilize the Inquisition like she usually does."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2c7c",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s because she doesn’t trust them."
}

{
  "id": "line:040f936",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "ORYM: I hate to say it,[p/] but that doesn’t really surprise me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5838d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "ORYM: She’s always been standoffish with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:075090d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: But there [i]is[/i] one exception."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef833",
  "node": "LockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: There are individuals whom she’s trusted more than the Inquisition during this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe628d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Steelwind had been personally investigating the crime herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:06931c3",
  "node": "LockerDeduce4",
  "text": "She wouldn't let anyone into the crime scene,[p/] not even the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:02251b6",
  "node": "LockerDeduce4",
  "text": "But there [i]were[/i] individuals that she trusted enough to give full freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b116d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: She's let [i]us[/i] investigate the crime scenes without any restrictions."
}

{
  "id": "line:043656d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce5",
  "text": "CELESTE: ...Yeah,[p/] I didn't notice that until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1c27",
  "node": "LockerDeduce5",
  "text": "CELESTE: Does she really trust us that much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05780b0",
  "node": "LockerDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: I don’t think personal trust is the reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc4de5",
  "node": "LockerDeduce5",
  "text": "TYRION: We don't usually interact with her,[p/] and she’s worked with the Inquisition on plenty of cases that we weren’t even involved in."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b23ac",
  "node": "LockerDeduce6",
  "text": "No...[p/] There was a key difference between us and the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:014710a",
  "node": "LockerDeduce6",
  "text": "We didn't answer to anyone,[p/] and we weren't subject to corruption from the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da1d98",
  "node": "LockerDeduce6",
  "text": "So why would that make Steelwind trust us this time around?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0723d83",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind doesn’t know much about us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0154b90",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she [i]does[/i] know that we aren’t prone to noble corruption."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5e73f",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right...[p/] You [i]did[/i] just indict a noble last week."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b2126",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: Meanwhile,[p/] the Inquisition usually bends to the nobility’s whims."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0145",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "ORYM: Can’t argue with you there."
}

{
  "id": "line:003691a",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: Using my[p/] intuition,[p/] I could tell that she’s worried about the witness’s family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f06482",
  "node": "LockerDeduce7",
  "text": "TYRION: And if she’s worried about corruption from the nobility,[p/] that can only mean one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0b457",
  "node": "LockerDeduce8",
  "text": "000|020"
}

{
  "id": "line:042d795",
  "node": "LockerDeduce8",
  "text": "No...[p/] We weren't controlled by the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:094a652",
  "node": "LockerDeduce8",
  "text": "There was a reason why Steelwind was so wary of us knowing who this witness is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0060ab2",
  "node": "LockerDeduce8",
  "text": "And if the witness’s family was powerful,[p/] that must mean..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca7c7",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness has to belong to a noble family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0900e20",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "Tyrion: That’s why she’s so wary of interference."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fabb6e",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "CELESTE: But [i]we’re[/i] obviously not going to do anything corrupt."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7e1d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "CELESTE: Why is she hiding the witness's identity from us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0849751",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "I remember that thought I saw through the Eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd37c",
  "node": "LockerDeduce9",
  "text": "ARIA: ...So regardless of what I said before,[p/] the answer is still “no”. [h=\"Her family is dangerous.\" e=\"f\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01aa605",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: ...She’s worried about our safety."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc31f8",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "ORYM: Yeah...[p/] I guess harassing a noble could put you in danger,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf84db",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: I’m the protégé of the “infamous Ruby Tymora”."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b6f6b",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "CELESTE: Yeah,[p/] it’s not as if we weren’t already on the nobility’s bad side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0085d35",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "CELESTE: I’m sure House Pierce still has it out for us."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d1e96",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "Celeste: They are definitely the ones sending those rogues into your house."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d9076",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "Orym: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020ac4b",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't worry about it.[p/] I've got it under control."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cbb93",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: This can only mean that the family we’re dealing with is even more powerful than House Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a0a37",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: If the prosecutor is wary of them,[p/] they must be as powerful as the Steelwinds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b207bb",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "ORYM: Wait...[p/][s/] Don’t tell me you think we’re dealing with another one of the Four Pillars?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e169d2",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "CELESTE: I have to ask about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe57c",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "Celeste: I always hear you and Ruby say it a lot,[p/] but who [i]are[/i] the “Four Pillars”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01575c1",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: It’s a name people use for the four most powerful noble houses.[p/] They're led by the Dukes and Duchesses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0325ec3",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "TYRION: House Frega,[p/] House von Sanctus,[p/] House Sibyl,[p/] and, of course, House Steelwind—[p/]the four of them stand at the top of Wyverngarde's hierarchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:084b1ef",
  "node": "LockerDeduce10",
  "text": "Celeste: So Steelwind [i]is[/i] one of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eccca2",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b11f6",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: Steelwind's paranoia all started after she investigated this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a6267",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: We were at the crime scene,[p/] and she left to follow a lead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02907c8",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: But an hour later,[p/] she came back to the lecture hall and basically booted everyone out."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b8f18",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "TYRION: Her behaviour changed [i]after[/i] investigating this room..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a841b",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "TYRION: That means that she found something here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a103fa",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "CELESTE: And that “something” must point to a family from the four pillars!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0265a2d",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "The commander shifted slightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dab64",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: You know...[p/] Steelwind’s orders say [i]I[/i] can’t snoop around here."
}

{
  "id": "line:04506ba",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "ORYM: But you two,[p/] on the other hand..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6bda6",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "TYRION: Don’t worry.[p/] Just leave it to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f0e07",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "Orym: I have some school records that say which locker belongs to which student."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cc541",
  "node": "LockerDeduce11",
  "text": "Orym: You can use it to tell whose locker you're looking at."
}

{
  "id": "line:0accfc7",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce",
  "text": "CELESTE: We found...[p/] a few things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0678454",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce",
  "text": "CELESTE: But I can’t really make sense of any of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d6d8e",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: We should look at this from the prosecutor’s perspective."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607da7",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: Steelwind found something in one of the lockers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0583f11",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce",
  "text": "TYRION: And whatever that was,[p/] it made her extremely paranoid."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cee5b",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] We found some strange things in each of the lockers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8c8a9",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce2",
  "text": "But there was something we found that was extremely suspicious,[p/] no matter how I looked at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d90af",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: We found some insanely suspicious things in Frega’s locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b54f9",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: It had Wallace’s notebooks and even some blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:066ad87",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: But that blood is certainly strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c65a4a",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It implies that something bloody was stored there.[p/] It could only be the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eac9b",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Do you think someone stole it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d62140",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: No, actually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2f218",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: I think it was Steelwind who took it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f3091",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: Oh, right.[p/] Orym mentioned that she investigated this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3abef",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "CELESTE: She must have taken the murder weapon as evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7f5d7",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "TYRION: But with that said,[p/] there’s something else that’s strange about Miriam Frega’s locker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3417e",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It had a [i]lot[/i] of Wallace’s possessions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0da82",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s possible that she really did steal these items from him,[p/] but it's more likely that this locker isn't actually hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c46c27",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Remember what Wallace told us before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a34e9",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "WALLACE: Sometimes the other students would steal the id number off my locker and switch it with another student's."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f16ec",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "CELESTE: So, someone switched the nameplates?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091addc",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "TYRION: This means that this [i]isn’t[/i] Miriam Frega’s locker.[p/] It’s Wallace’s."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e80e1",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "CELESTE: But that would mean that the bloody object came from [i]Wallace’s[/i] locker!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03497f1",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "TYRION: It appears so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e20308",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "TYRION: But if that’s true,[p/] why didn't Steelwind present the bloody item during the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f7332",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]proved[/i] that Bellwether was wounded before Valerie healed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f889bc",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wouldn’t that have been the perfect time to present what she found?"
}

{
  "id": "line:059eea4",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was a bloody item found in the [i]defendant’s[/i] locker, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dad8b",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "CELESTE: Right...[p/] That [i]is[/i] weird."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd44f6",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "There was something more to this that I wasn’t seeing,[p/] but what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00537f3",
  "node": "AfterLockerDeduce4",
  "text": "TYRION: I think we’ll just have to ask Steelwind ourselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:079e57d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Statue"
}

{
  "id": "line:03277ee",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a statue of some sort of scientist.[p/] There's some writing below it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f81a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Gillian Kemnitz:[p/] the inventor of early artificery.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0da1fb1",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: Artificery is really impressive, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a1932",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: It lets anyone use magic [i]without[/i] having noble blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5fe8a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Although the expenses of owning artificery presented their own barrier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cf291",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: This statue's kind of weird, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:082494c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Celeste: It kind of looks like he doesn't even want to be here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdb2ce",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a man with some sort of creature on his arm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4e190",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Doctor Delbit Taphoros: a mage,[p/] historian,[p/] archeologist,[p/] anthropologist,[p/] and botanist.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:06429d0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Best known for his work in studying the history of the ancient dragons.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:082575e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Through his work,[p/] great leaps were made in the study and development of the school of [b]evocation[/b].\""
}

{
  "id": "line:070b639",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"On his arm is one of the last pseudodragons,[p/] which are now extinct.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7ad2",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a professor with some kind of magical tool."
}

{
  "id": "line:0715acb",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's some text under it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cec7ce",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Doctor Paul Vuorela:[p/] also known as the Archeologist of the North.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:08bcc89",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"He spent many years studying and exploring the mountainous regions of Shardalon.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:07beabe",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"And through his investigation,[p/] he came upon one of the many lairs of the Scaled Lord.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0e863a0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"He was honored both by the Church [i]and[/i] the Wyverngarde Historical Society for this impressive discovery.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:046a1d9",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: The Investigation"
}

{
  "id": "line:05166ba",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I hope Wallace is okay...[p/] The Inquisition isn't exactly great at treating its prisoners well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69134",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Even as an attorney,[p/] there was only so much I could do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc17db",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Until I could acquit Wallace,[p/] he would be stuck in that dungeon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c23626",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ....Let's head to Lecture Hall 2-B.[p/] We need to figure out what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aeb52",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is Wallace really a necromancer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0595577",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure.[p/] He's nothing like the mad liches I've read about."
}

{
  "id": "line:04506f3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] Have actual liches appeared in Wyverngarde before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d16655",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: E-[p/][s/]Er...[p/] No,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8fffc",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...They show up a lot in the [i]Wraithbound[/i] series."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91554",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] that's a fantasy novel."
}

{
  "id": "line:01974a7",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: E-[p/][s/]Either way,[p/] I can't help but feel like Steelwind is hiding something from us."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3bc3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Is that really so weird?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b07a2a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: We [i]did[/i] make a deal with her,[p/] but she's still going to fight us in the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca3877",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Bellwether wasn't the greatest person, was she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f98c3d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so,[p/] we can't stand by while a murderer runs loose."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ddca4",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If they get away with this,[p/] Wallace could be facing the gallows."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad42f3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3e7f1",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder if we could find Valentina again."
}

{
  "id": "line:04222da",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It'd be best not to scare her more than we already have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd6331",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: For now,[p/] let's focus on the other leads we have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e918e6",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a355c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe Bellwether was going to fire [i]everyone[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d840c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Did she really hate the commoners here [i]that[/i] much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c2982",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Some people take pleasure in cruelty,[p/] and having authority just makes that worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3e1b7",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm honestly glad she's gone.[p/] I hope the commoners here can relax now."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9af3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not so sure.[p/] I'm sure this kingdom has no shortage of Bellwethers."
}

{
  "id": "line:070f85f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I never knew that healing magic was considered [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1e101",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess I just have a lot to think about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515a37",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "I grew up reading [i]Wraithbound[/i],[p/] but I never stopped to think about what kind of person Corrin Bloomveil was."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cd453",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "It was written nearly a century ago.[p/] Could Wallace be right about him...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9612",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Player: Next Lead"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebd614",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Where should we go next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063915f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The first thing we need to do is find out exactly what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0138e7c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora said that the body was found in Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e0157",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's start our investigation there."
}

{
  "id": "line:033c864",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The headmaster supposedly had a meeting with Bellwether at noon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2073e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: He might have been the last person to see her alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f3d5",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should see if he knew where she was going after the meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7cac4",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Two members of the kitchen staff discovered the body.[p/] So we should talk to them next."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c4c78",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They might have seen something that we didn't find at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe194",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The academy is probably closed for the investigation,[p/] but we might still be able to find them in the kitchen."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b147c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm a little suspicious of Valentina,[p/] but I don't think chasing her will do us any favors."
}

{
  "id": "line:068e2b6",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: She mentioned something peculiar about Bellwether firing everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0147a75",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That rumor supposedly came from a custodian named \"Jan Hughes\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:092edea",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we walk through the hallways,[p/] we might be able to find him and ask more about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:044425b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Inquisition should be finished questioning Wallace by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:077ce8d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we MOVE to the Barracks,[p/] we might finally be able to speak with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:040eb2a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Valentina has probably returned to the kitchen by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de8995",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we MOVE there,[p/] you should be able to scan her and see if she has any magical traces attached to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fec39",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d88f3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's my Attorney's Runestone, Celeste.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7315e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] you've shown this thing to me before."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fee59",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yes,[p/] it's very cool, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c505f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It's kind of fun seeing you work through everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e85d17",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] There is something satisfying about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdd802",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm so glad I got this job.[p/] It's so much less stressful than being a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0463f7f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] You've had to stop people from breaking into my house every night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0171efa",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, that's nothing.[p/] When I was a mercenary,[p/] I had to fight hordes of people and monsters at once."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7bb1c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: A few assassins are nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fca054",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "The scariest part was that I wasn't sure if she was exaggerating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4a415",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't expect Steelwind to be working this case, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:066a717",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She appears to be prosecuting all of the cases brought forth by the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5fdc0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll probably be seeing a lot more of her in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fdb4d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Before,[p/] I thought she was prosecuting me because my dad was a revolutionary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0797a8f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: But I guess she's a prosecutor full-time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0192f04",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I hope Eris is handling this well.[p/] Her friend was falsely accused of murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5986d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Really?[p/] She doesn't seem that bothered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bccc6d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: The people who show the least emotion tend to feel it most strongly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be53c7",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "I knew that better than anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26f8f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Catherina|BellRep"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bad08",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: And if they get away with this,[p/] Wallace could be facing the gallows."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a3bab",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Jan looks like he's in a constant state of being tired.[p/] I feel kind of bad for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:003576c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you sure he's not just lazy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a95769",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't be so quick to judge people, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:076938d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You never know what someone else is going through."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ca9d9",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Player: Valentina|Valerie"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e4d21",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: The more we talk to them,[p/] the more suspicious the twins look."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c6000",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] They're definitely hiding something."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a8153",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "I just had to wait for a better opportunity.[p/] The truth would show itself eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:03573f5",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: We really don't know that much about Wallace, do we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055b6df",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: We know that he has a solid alibi for the murder.[p/] There's no way that he killed Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:04096bd",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You really believe in your clients, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039f2c1",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Of course.[p/] How can I expect the courts to believe in his innocence if I don't?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e60cf9",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm glad you're confident,[p/] but what would you do if you found out your client was guilty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094c299",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd never take on a client like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3595f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus was pretty good for vetting people."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c4262",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: But is that really...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce49d5",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Nothing.[p/] I guess it's not really my place to say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd9b43",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Player: NoneComp|WallComp"
}

{
  "id": "line:091d0cd",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Spell Compendiums are really useful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210fdc",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yep![p/] They help us mages keep track of our spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650f06",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "They were also an indisputable piece of evidence in court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6221b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Player: ValTrace"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d11c0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't know that you were learning to cast [b]Detect Magic[/b] this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba53cb",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Ruby asked me to.[p/] She doesn't really trust the Inquisition, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0bc85",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "I should probably thank her for that later.[p/] Being able to see magical traces would be instrumental in my future cases."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ca78d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i], Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04eed2d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Ah...[p/] Sorry, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:080a356",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think I can help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba714",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "A few hours had passed since Wallace was arrested."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae77a0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste and I were with him during the lockdown,[p/] so the Inquisition took our statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc03d4",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "But the more they questioned me,[p/] the more I could tell that they were looking for gaps in my testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:013c78e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "We would need to do more if we wanted to establish an alibi for Wallace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe63b2",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] They definitely know how to waste a lot of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0860cc6",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "TYRION: They know who we are now.[p/] We'll have to expect more interference from them in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:03656f3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4717",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b7c6d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you okay?[p/] I'm sorry for stopping you before.[p/] I know you were just worried about Ruby."
}

{
  "id": "line:011c84f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] You were completely right.[p/] I was just being emotional."
}

{
  "id": "line:044069a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You really care about her, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c29d3",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's done a lot for me.[p/] If it weren't for her,[p/] I would've grown up on the streets."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d89846",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ba5ab",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: It's just..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6bf74",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:029912e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't you think the way she treats you is a bit...[p/] cold sometimes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff162f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's only for my benefit.[p/] I need to be the best attorney I can be if I want to acquit my clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c70469",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Still...[p/] She's your guardian, isn't she?[p/] She could be nicer to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da927d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's never been good at expressing emotions."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d6333",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think something may have happened in the past,[p/] but I've never tried to pry."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f1abf",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I know for a fact that she cares for me.[p/] I've seen it many times."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d8f95",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] I guess my dad was the same in a way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0292bcf",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I guess people show love in different ways."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e4865",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know you didn't get the best first impression of her,[p/] but I hope you can get along with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3354e",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I'll try,[p/] but only because I really like this job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2560d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah![p/][s/] You're the best client I've ever had, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed909b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I see.[p/] That's good to hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0538269",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "She was probably just saying that.[p/] I'm sure she told every one of her clients the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3e3ba",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Anyways,[p/] we should get to work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16b70",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Right.[p/] Ruby said that a bunch of knights were heading to Lecture Hall 2-B."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e686c7",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer1_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: That sounds like a good place to start."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7b21",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea0925",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:080fb0b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you still worried about Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4f5ad",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm [i]really[/i] trying not to be scared of her.[p/] But I just can't help it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6359b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: And having to talk to her in the [i]cemetery[/i] isn't helping..."
}

{
  "id": "line:021d8ec",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's still a lot we don't know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:097f2e1",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3542c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: We [i]know[/i] that Wallace didn't kill her,[p/] but did the true killer really murder her in the library?"
}

{
  "id": "line:026545f",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Right...[p/] You'll need to go there to find out more."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f478d",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I wonder why Steelwind isn't helping us this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:021086b",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: She had no problem giving us information before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:019f847",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Something must be different this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4797a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I can't stop thinking about that story the commander told us."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eae20",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure he's just exaggerating..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9fd11",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's no way someone could [i]really[/i] use magic to control people's minds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff4c68",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Although...[p/] You clearly have an ability to [i]read[/i] people's minds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78769",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "So, it's not [i]too[/i] out there..."
}

{
  "id": "line:065a323",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: In a way,[p/] Steelwind was trying to protect us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0745ab0",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I appreciate the gesture.[p/] But we need to talk with Miriam if we want to find out more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0434023",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Just be careful.[p/] Dealing with a member of a Pillar Family could be dangerous for a [i]lot[/i] of reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2d804",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think we've gotten all the information we need out of Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0757f28",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should head back to the cemetery."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2e64",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The prosecution believes that Wallace killed Bellwether in the Library."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c8afa",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We didn't really investigate that room the first time around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0a5cb",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We might be able to find some new leads there."
}

{
  "id": "line:048c658",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind isn't cooperating with us,[p/] but I don't think I have enough information to ARGUE with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:096c4ad",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should head somewhere else in the meantime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c798b2",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We found a decent amount of information with Commander White's help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0305cde",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think we finally have enough information to ARGUE with Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d7fd2",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "...You just hope she'll finally be receptive to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7164a",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind finally told us about Miriam Frega.[p/] And we even know where her dorm room is."
}

{
  "id": "line:053a89c",
  "node": "SchoolFoyer2_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should head there and TALK to her."
}
